  <para style="h">1 ImiLando</para>
  <para style="toc1">Ugwalo Lwakuqala LwemiLando</para>
  <para style="toc2">1 ImiLando</para>
  <para style="toc3">1Lan</para>
  <para style="mt2">Ugwalo Lwakuqala</para>
  <para style="mt1">LwemiLando</para>
  <para style="imt">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="imt1">Isingeniso</para>
  <para style="im">Ngesentshuri yesihlanu uKhristu engakazalwa, amaJuda amanengi ayephenduka evela ekuthunjweni afikela emkhonweni ongaseningizimu yako-Israyeli. Bahlangana lobunzima obukhulu: isigodlo lethempeli labo kwasekwabhidlizwa, abantu bezizweni basebengene edolobheni njalo basebengasabuswa yinkosi yabo. Kodwa ingwalo zemiLando, u-Ezra, kanye lolukaNehemiya zigcizelela ukuthi abantu bakaNkulunkulu bangayigcwalisa injongo yakhe. Kumele bakhe isizwe esingafani lezinye, esigxile ekukhonzeni uNkulunkulu, ethempelini elakhiwe kutsha eliseJerusalema. (Ingwalo lezi ngempela zilugwalo olulodwa olude, olukhuluma ngodaba oluqhubekayo; lokhu sikubona ngendlela isiphetho sogwalo lwesibili lwemiLando sigabhela ekuqaleni kogwalo luka-Ezra).</para>
  <para style="ip">Lolugwalo luphawula ngokugcweleyo indaba yembali yako-Israyeli, luqalisa ngokulandisa ngensendo kumbe uluhlu lwabokhokho baka-Israyeli. Kusukela ku-Adamu, lufaka abantu bako-Israyeli phakathi kwezizwe njalo lubakhumbuza ngobizo lwabo. UJuda nguye oqakathekiswayo ngoba kulapho okuvela khona umkhondo wobukhosi bukaDavida, loLevi okuvela khona umkhondo wobuphristi lezisebenzi zethempelini.</para>
  <para style="ip">Isigaba sesibili esimqoka siphawula ngamakhosi abusa eJerusalema kuze kuyefika isikhathi sokuthunjwa. Kulandiswa kakhulu ngoDavida kulamanye amakhosi, kodwa okunengi ngempilo yakhe okukhulunywa kwezinye indawo akulotshwanga kulolugwalo. Kugxilwa kakhulu emikhankasweni yakhe yezimpi kanye lamacebo akhe okwakhiwa kwethempeli eJerusalema. Isizatho sokwaliswa kukaDavida ukwakha ithempeli sisobala, kwakungenxa yokuthi wayelibutho. UNkulunkulu wayefuna indoda elokuthula ukuthi yakhe ithempeli lapho izizwe zonke ezazizazokhulekela khona. Ngakho inhlonipho leyo yawela endodaneni kaDavida uSolomoni. Kanengi kulotshwe ngaye okwedlula amanye amakhosi ngaphandle kukaDavida, kuchasiswa ngokwakhiwa kwethempeli lobucwazicwazi bombuso wakhe.</para>
  <para style="ip">Isigaba sokucina sogwalo sigxile ezehlakalweni zalabo abaphenduka bevela ekuthunjweni. Impilo ka-Ezra loNehemiya, abakhokheli besizukulwane sesibili samaJuda aphendukayo layo igoqeliwe embalini. Abakhokheli laba basiza ekwakhiweni kwesigaba esingafani lezinye ngokwalisa amaJuda ukuthathana lokwendiselana labantu abakhelane labo, njalo baba ngabaqondisi bokwakhiwa kutsha kwemiduli yeJerusalema. Lapha kulandiswa isivumelwano esikhulu somkhosi wokwakha kutsha kukhokhelwa ngu-Ezra loNehemiya.</para>
  <para style="ip">Indikimba eqakathekileyo yembali engabizwa kuhle ngokuthi, imbali yethempeli iyikuthi ukukhonza okuqotho ngokwenziwa ngentando kaNkulunkulu hatshi eyoluntu. UNkulunkulu ukhethe u-Israyeli ukwamukela izizwe enkonzweni yeqiniso. Phakathi kwezehlakalo ezihlangana lo-Israyeli, uNkulunkulu usebenzela ukugcwalisisa linjongo.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c" sid="1CH 1"/>
  <para style="s1">Kulondwa Imbali Kusukela Ku-Adamu Kusiya Ku-Abhrahama</para>
  <para style="s2">Emadodaneni KaNowa</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 1:1"/>U-Adamu, uSethi, u-Enoshi,<verse eid="1CH 1:1"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 1:2"/>uKhenani, uMahalaleli, uJaredi,<verse eid="1CH 1:2"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 1:3"/>u-Enoki, uMethuzela, uLameki,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 1:3">uNowa.<verse eid="1CH 1:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 1:4"/>Amadodana kaNowa ayeyila: uShemu, uHamu loJafethi.<verse eid="1CH 1:4"/></para>
  <para style="s2">AbakaJafethi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 1:5"/>Amadodana kaJafethi ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:5">uGomeri, uMagogi, uMadayi, uJavani, uThubhali, uMesheki loThirasi.<verse eid="1CH 1:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 1:6"/>Amadodana kaGomeri ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:6">u-Ashikhenazi, uRifathi kanye loThogarima.<verse eid="1CH 1:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 1:7"/>Amadodana kaJavani ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:7">u-Elisha, uThashishi, uKhithimi loRodanimu.<verse eid="1CH 1:7"/></para>
  <para style="s2">AbakaHamu:</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 1:8"/>Amadodana kaHamu ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:8">uKhushi, uMizirayimi, uPhuthi loKhenani.<verse eid="1CH 1:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 1:9"/>Amadodana kaKhushi ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:9">uSebha, uHavila, uSabhitha, uRahama loSabhitheka.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 1:9">Amadodana kaRahama ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:9">uShebha loDedani.<verse eid="1CH 1:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 1:10"/>UKhushi wayenguyise</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:10">kaNimrodi, owakhula waba liqhawe elilamandla emhlabeni.<verse eid="1CH 1:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 1:11"/>UMizirayimi wayenguyise</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:11">wamaLudi, ama-Anami, amaLehabhi, amaNafithuhi, <verse eid="1CH 1:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 1:12"/>amaPhathrosi, lamaKhasiluhi (okwadabuka khona amaFilistiya) lamaKhafithori.<verse eid="1CH 1:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 1:13"/>UKhenani wayenguyise</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:13">kaSidoni izibulo lakhe, amaHithi, <verse eid="1CH 1:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 1:14"/>amaJebusi, ama-Amori, amaGigashi, <verse eid="1CH 1:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 1:15"/>amaHivi, ama-Arikhi, amaSini, <verse eid="1CH 1:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 1:16"/>ama-Avadi, amaZemari kanye lamaHamathi.<verse eid="1CH 1:16"/></para>
  <para style="s2">AbakaSemi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 1:17"/>Amadodana kaShemu ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:17">u-Elamu, u-Ashuri, u-Afazadi, uLudi lo-Aramu.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 1:17">Amadodana ka-Aramu ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:17">u-Uzi, uHuli, uGetha loMesheki.<verse eid="1CH 1:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 1:18"/>U-Afazadi wayenguyise kaShela,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:18">uShela wazala u-Ebha.<verse eid="1CH 1:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 1:19"/>Amadodana amabili ayezalwa ngu-Ebha ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:19">Omunye wayenguPhelegi, ngoba ngezinsuku zakhe umhlaba wawudabuke phakathi; umfowabo kwakuthiwa nguJokithani.<verse eid="1CH 1:19"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 1:20"/>UJokithani wayenguyise</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:20">ka-Alimodadi, uShelefi, uHazarimavethi, uJera, <verse eid="1CH 1:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 1:21"/>uHadoramu, u-Uzali, uDikila, <verse eid="1CH 1:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 1:22"/>u-Obhali, u-Abhimayeli, uShebha, <verse eid="1CH 1:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 1:23"/>u-Ofiri, uHavila kanye loJobhabhi. Bonke laba babengamadodana kaJokithani.<verse eid="1CH 1:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 1:24"/>UShemu, u-Afazadi uShela,<verse eid="1CH 1:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 1:25"/>u-Ebha, uPhelegi, uRewu<verse eid="1CH 1:25"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 1:26"/>uSerugi, uNahori, uThera<verse eid="1CH 1:26"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 1:27"/>lo-Abhrama (u-Abhrahama).<verse eid="1CH 1:27"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Imuli Ka-Abhrahama</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 1:28"/>Amadodana ka-Abhrahama ayeyila: u-Isaka lo-Ishumayeli.<verse eid="1CH 1:28"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Abenzalo KaHagari</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 1:29"/>Laba babeyinzalo yabo:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:29">uNebhayothi izibulo lika-Ishumayeli, uKhedari, u-Adibheli, uMibhisamu, <verse eid="1CH 1:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 1:30"/>uMishima, uDuma, uMasa, uHadadi, uThema, <verse eid="1CH 1:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 1:31"/>uJethuri, uNafishi kanye loKhedema.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 1:31">La yiwo ayengamadodana ka-Ishumayeli.<verse eid="1CH 1:31"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Abenzalo KaKhethura</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 1:32"/>Amadodana azalwa nguKhethura, umfazi ka-Abhrahama oweceleni, ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:32">uZimirani, uJokishani, uMedani, uMidiyani, u-Ishibhaki loShuwa.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 1:32">Amadodana kaJokishani ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:32">uShebha loDedani.<verse eid="1CH 1:32"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="1CH 1:33"/>Amadodana kaMidiyani ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:33">u-Efa, u-Eferi, uHanokhi, u-Abhida lo-Elida.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 1:33">Bonke laba babeyizizukulwane zikaKhethura.<verse eid="1CH 1:33"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Abenzalo KaSara</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="1CH 1:34"/>U-Abhrahama wayenguyise ka-Isaka.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 1:34">Amadodana ka-Isaka ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:34">u-Esawu lo-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 1:34"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amadodana Ka-Esawu</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="1CH 1:35"/>Amadodana ka-Esawu ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:35">u-Elifazi, uRuweli, uJewushi, uJalamu loKhora.<verse eid="1CH 1:35"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="1CH 1:36"/>Amadodana ka-Elifazi ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:36">uThemani, u-Omari, uZefi, uGathamu loKhenazi;</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:36">ekaThimina kungu-Amaleki.<verse eid="1CH 1:36"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="1CH 1:37"/>Amadodana kaRuweli ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:37">uNahathi, uZera, uShama loMiza.<verse eid="1CH 1:37"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Abantu BeSeyiri E-Edomi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="1CH 1:38"/>Amadodana kaSeyiri ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:38">uLothani, uShobhali, uZibhiyoni, u-Ana, uDishoni, u-Ezeri loDishani.<verse eid="1CH 1:38"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="1CH 1:39"/>Amadodana kaLothani ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:39">uHori loHomami. UThimina wayengudadewabo kaLothani.<verse eid="1CH 1:39"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="1CH 1:40"/>Amadodana kaShobhali ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:40">u-Alivani, uManahathi, u-Ebhali, uShefo lo-Onami.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 1:40">Amadodana kaZibhiyoni ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:40">u-Ayiya lo-Ana.<verse eid="1CH 1:40"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="1CH 1:41"/>Indodana ka-Ana yayingu:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:41">uDishoni.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 1:41">Amadodana kaDishoni ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:41">uHemirani, u-Eshibhani, u-Ithirani loKherani.<verse eid="1CH 1:41"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="1CH 1:42"/>Amadodana ka-Ezeri ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:42">uBhilihani, uZavani lo-Akhani.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 1:42">Amadodana kaDishoni ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 1:42">u-Uzi lo-Arani.<verse eid="1CH 1:42"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Ababusi Be-Edomi</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="1CH 1:43"/>La ayengamakhosi abusa e-Edomi kungakabusi inkosi yako-Israyeli:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 1:43">uBhela indodana kaBheyori, idolobho lakhe lalibizwa ngokuthi yiDinihabha.<verse eid="1CH 1:43"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="1CH 1:44"/>UBhela esefile, uJobhabhi indodana kaZera waseBhozira wathatha umbuso waba yinkosi.<verse eid="1CH 1:44"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="1CH 1:45"/>UJobhabhi esefile, uHushamu waselizweni lamaThemani wathatha umbuso waba yinkosi.<verse eid="1CH 1:45"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="1CH 1:46"/>UHushamu esefile, uHadadi indodana kaBhedadi owanqoba uMidiyani elizweni laseMowabi, wathatha umbuso waba yinkosi. Idolobho lakhe lalibizwa ngokuthi yi-Avithi.<verse eid="1CH 1:46"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="1CH 1:47"/>UHadadi esefile, uSamila waseMasirekha wathatha umbuso waba yinkosi.<verse eid="1CH 1:47"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="1CH 1:48"/>USamila esefile, uShawuli waseRehobhothi phezu komfula wathatha umbuso waba yinkosi.<verse eid="1CH 1:48"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="1CH 1:49"/>UShawuli esefile, uBhali-Hanani indodana ka-Akhibhori wathatha umbuso waba yinkosi.<verse eid="1CH 1:49"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="1CH 1:50"/>UBhali-Hanani esefile, uHadadi wathatha umbuso waba yinkosi. Idolobho lakhe labizwa ngokuthi yiPawu, njalo ibizo lomkakhe lalinguMehethabheli indodakazi kaMathiredi, indodakazi kaMe-Zahabhi. <verse eid="1CH 1:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="1CH 1:51"/>UHadadi laye wafa.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 1:51"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 1:51">Izinduna zase-Edomi kwakuyilezi:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 1:51">uThimina, u-Aliva, uJethethi, <verse eid="1CH 1:51"/><verse number="52" style="v" sid="1CH 1:52"/>u-Oholibhama, u-Ela, uPhinoni, <verse eid="1CH 1:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="1CH 1:53"/>uKhenazi, uThemani, uMibhizari, <verse eid="1CH 1:53"/><verse number="54" style="v" sid="1CH 1:54"/>uMagidiyeli lo-Iramu.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 1:54">Lezi kwakuzinduna ze-Edomi.<verse eid="1CH 1:54"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 1"/>
  <chapter number="2" style="c" sid="1CH 2"/>
  <para style="s1">Amadodana Ka-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 2:1"/>Amadodana ka-Israyeli ayeyila: uRubheni, uSimiyoni, uLevi, uJuda, u-Isakhari, uZebhuluni, <verse eid="1CH 2:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 2:2"/>uDani, uJosefa, uBhenjamini, uNafithali, uGadi lo-Asheri.<verse eid="1CH 2:2"/></para>
  <para style="s1">AbakaJuda</para>
  <para style="s2">Emadodaneni KaHezironi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 2:3"/>Amadodana kaJuda yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:3">ngu-Eri, lo-Onani kanye loShela. Laba bobathathu wabazala lowesifazane ongumKhenani, indodakazi kaShuwa.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:3">U-Eri, izibulo likaJuda, wayeyisigangi phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>, ngalokho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wambulala.<verse eid="1CH 2:3"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 2:4"/>UThamari, umalukazana kaJuda wamzalela uPherezi loZera.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 2:4">UJuda wayelamadodana amahlanu.<verse eid="1CH 2:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 2:5"/>Amadodana kaPherezi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:5">nguHezironi loHamuli.<verse eid="1CH 2:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 2:6"/>Amadodana kaZera yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:6">nguZimri, lo-Ethani, loHemani, loKhalikholi kanye loDarida. Bonke babebahlanu.<verse eid="1CH 2:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 2:7"/>Indodana kaKhami yile:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:7">ngu-Akhari, owaletha inhlupheko ko-Israyeli ngesiphambeko asenza ngalokho okungcwelisiweyo.<verse eid="1CH 2:7"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 2:8"/>Indodana ka-Ethani yile:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:8">ngu-Azariya.<verse eid="1CH 2:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 2:9"/>Amadodana azalwa nguHezironi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:9">nguJerameli, loRamu kanye loKhalebi.<verse eid="1CH 2:9"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Kusukela KuRama Indodana KaHezironi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 2:10"/>URamu wayenguyise ka-Aminadabi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:10">njalo u-Aminadabi enguyise kaNahashoni, umkhokheli wabantu bakoJuda.<verse eid="1CH 2:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 2:11"/>UNahashoni wayenguyise kaSalimoni,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:11">uSalimoni enguyise kaBhowazi.<verse eid="1CH 2:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 2:12"/>UBhowazi enguyise ka-Obhedi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:12">u-Obhedi enguyise kaJese.<verse eid="1CH 2:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 2:13"/>UJese wayenguyise</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:13">ka-Eliyabi izibulo lakhe; indodana yesibili kungu-Abhinadabi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:13">eyesithathu kunguShimeya, <verse eid="1CH 2:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 2:14"/>eyesine kunguNethaneli,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:14">eyesihlanu kunguRadayi, <verse eid="1CH 2:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 2:15"/>eyesithupha kungu-Ozemu,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:15">eyesikhombisa kunguDavida.<verse eid="1CH 2:15"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 2:16"/>Odadewabo kwakunguZeruya lo-Abhigeli.</para>
  <para style="li3" vid="1CH 2:16">Amadodana amathathu kaZeruya kwakungu-Abhishayi, loJowabi kanye lo-Asaheli.<verse eid="1CH 2:16"/></para>
  <para style="li3">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 2:17"/>U-Abhigeli wayengunina ka-Amasa, oloyise okwakuthiwa nguJetha umÊ¼Ishumayeli.<verse eid="1CH 2:17"/></para>
  <para style="s2">UKhalebi Indodana KaHezironi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 2:18"/>UKhalebi indodana kaHezironi wayelabantwana abazala kumkakhe u-Azubha (lakuJeriyothi). Amadodana ka-Azubha ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:18">nguJesheri, loShobhabi, kanye lo-Adoni.<verse eid="1CH 2:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 2:19"/>Ekufeni kuka-Azubha, uKhalebi wathatha u-Efrathi, owamzalela uHuri.<verse eid="1CH 2:19"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 2:20"/>UHuri wayenguyise ka-Uri, njalo u-Uri enguyise kaBhezaleli.<verse eid="1CH 2:20"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 2:21"/>Muva, uHezironi wembatha lendodakazi kaMakhiri uyise kaGiliyadi (ayemthethe eseleminyaka engamatshumi ayisithupha ubudala bakhe), yena wamzalela uSegubi.<verse eid="1CH 2:21"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 2:22"/>USegubi wayenguyise kaJayiri, owayephethe imizi engamatshumi amabili lantathu eGiliyadi.<verse eid="1CH 2:22"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 2:23"/>(Kodwa uGeshuri lo-Aramu bathumba iHavothi-Jayiri, kanye leKhenathi lezindawana eziyimizana eseduzane, imizi engamatshumi ayisithupha.)</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 2:23">Bonke laba babeyisizukulwane sikaMakhiri uyise kaGiliyadi.<verse eid="1CH 2:23"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 2:24"/>Ngemva kokufa kukaHezironi eKhalebi-Efratha, u-Abhija umkaHezironi wamzalela u-Ashuri uyise kaThekhowa.<verse eid="1CH 2:24"/></para>
  <para style="s2">UJerameli Indodana KaHezironi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 2:25"/>Amadodana kaJerameli izibulo likaHezironi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:25">nguRamu izibulo lakhe, loBhuna, lo-Oreni, lo-Ozemu kanye lo-Ahija. <verse eid="1CH 2:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 2:26"/>UJerameli wayelomunye umfazi owayethiwa ngu-Athara unina ka-Onami.<verse eid="1CH 2:26"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 2:27"/>Amadodana kaRamu izibulo likaJerameli yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:27">nguMazi, loJamini kanye lo-Ekheri.<verse eid="1CH 2:27"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 2:28"/>Amadodana ka-Onami yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:28">nguShamayi loJada.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:28">Amadodana kaShamayi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:28">nguNadabi lo-Abhishuri. <verse eid="1CH 2:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 2:29"/>Umka-Abhishuri kwakungu-Abhihayili, owamzalela u-Ahibhani loMolidi.<verse eid="1CH 2:29"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 2:30"/>Amadodana kaNadabi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:30">nguSeledi lo-Aphayimi. USeledi wafa engelabantwana.<verse eid="1CH 2:30"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 2:31"/>Indodana ka-Aphayimi yile:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:31">ngu-Ishi, uyise kaSheshani. USheshani wayenguyise ka-Ahilayi.<verse eid="1CH 2:31"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 2:32"/>Amadodana kaJada, umfowabo kaShamayi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:32">nguJetha loJonathani. UJetha wafa engelabantwana.<verse eid="1CH 2:32"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="1CH 2:33"/>Amadodana kaJonathani yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:33">nguPhelethi loZaza.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 2:33">Laba babeyinzalo kaJerameli.<verse eid="1CH 2:33"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="1CH 2:34"/>USheshani wayengelawo amadodana, wayelamadodakazi wodwa.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:34">Wayelesisebenzi saseGibhithe esasithiwa nguJariha. <verse eid="1CH 2:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="1CH 2:35"/>USheshani wendisela isisebenzi sakhe lesi esinguJariha, indodakazi yakhe eyamzalela u-Athayi.<verse eid="1CH 2:35"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="1CH 2:36"/>U-Athayi wayenguyise kaNathani,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:36">uNathani enguyise kaZabhadi,<verse eid="1CH 2:36"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="1CH 2:37"/>uZabhadi enguyise ka-Efilali,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:37">u-Efilali enguyise ka-Obhedi,<verse eid="1CH 2:37"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="1CH 2:38"/>u-Obhedi enguyise kaJehu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:38">uJehu enguyise ka-Azariya,<verse eid="1CH 2:38"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="1CH 2:39"/>u-Azariya enguyise kaHelezi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:39">uHelezi enguyise ka-Eleyasa,<verse eid="1CH 2:39"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="1CH 2:40"/>u-Eleyasa enguyise kaSisimayi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:40">uSisimayi enguyise kaShalumi,<verse eid="1CH 2:40"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="1CH 2:41"/>uShalumi enguyise kaJekhamiya,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:41">uJekhamiya enguyise ka-Elishama.<verse eid="1CH 2:41"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Abosendo LukaKhalebi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="1CH 2:42"/>Amadodana kaKhalebi umfowabo kaJerameli yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:42">uMesha izibulo lakhe, onguyise kaZifi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:42">lendodana yakhe uMaresha, uyise kaHebhroni.<verse eid="1CH 2:42"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="1CH 2:43"/>Amadodana kaHebhroni yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:43">nguKhora, loThaphuwa, loRekhemu loShema.<verse eid="1CH 2:43"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="1CH 2:44"/>UShema wayenguyise kaRahama,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:44">uRahama yena enguyise kaJokheyama.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:44">URekhemu wayenguyise kaShamayi.<verse eid="1CH 2:44"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="1CH 2:45"/>Indodana kaShamayi kunguMawoni,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:45">uMawoni wayenguyise kaBhethi Zuri.<verse eid="1CH 2:45"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="1CH 2:46"/>Umfazi weceleni kaKhalebi u-Efa wayengunina</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:46">kaHarani, loMoza kanye loGazezi.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:46">UHarani wayenguyise kaGazezi.<verse eid="1CH 2:46"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="1CH 2:47"/>Amadodana kaJahidayi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:47">nguRegemi, loJothamu, loGeshani, loPhelethi, lo-Efa kanye loShafi.<verse eid="1CH 2:47"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="1CH 2:48"/>UMahakha umfazi weceleni kaKhalebi wayengunina</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:48">kaShebheri loThirihana.<verse eid="1CH 2:48"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="49" style="v" sid="1CH 2:49"/>Nguye njalo owazala uShafi uyise kaMadimana kanye</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:49">loSheva uyise kaMakhibhena loGibhiya.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:49">Indodakazi kaKhalebi kwakungu-Akhisa.<verse eid="1CH 2:49"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="1CH 2:50"/>Yibo laba abenzalo kaKhalebi.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 2:50"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 2:50">Amadodana kaHuri izibulo lika-Efrathi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:50">nguShobhali uyise kaKhiriyathi-Jeyarimi, <verse eid="1CH 2:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="1CH 2:51"/>loSalima uyise kaBhethilehema, loHarefi uyise kaBhethi-Gaderi.<verse eid="1CH 2:51"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="52" style="v" sid="1CH 2:52"/>Inzalo kaShobhali uyise kaKhiriyathi-Jeyarimi yile:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:52">nguHaro, ingxenye yamaManahathi, <verse eid="1CH 2:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="1CH 2:53"/>labosendo lukaKhiriyathi-Jeyarimi kungama-Ithira lamaPhuthi lamaShumathi lamaMishirayi. Kulapho okwakudabuka khona amaZorathi lama-Eshithawoli.<verse eid="1CH 2:53"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="54" style="v" sid="1CH 2:54"/>Abenzalo kaSalima yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 2:54">nguBhethilehema, umNethofa, u-Athirothi-Bhethi-Jowabi, ingxenye yamaManahathi, amaZori, <verse eid="1CH 2:54"/><verse number="55" style="v" sid="1CH 2:55"/>losendo lwabalobi ababehlala eJabhezi: AmaThirathi lamaShimeya lamaSukhathi. Laba babengamaKheni beyinzalo kaHamathi ukhokho wamaRekhabi.<verse eid="1CH 2:55"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 2"/>
  <chapter number="3" style="c" sid="1CH 3"/>
  <para style="s2">Amadodana KaDavida</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 3:1"/>Nanka amadodana kaDavida awazala eHebhroni:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 3:1"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:1">Izibulo lakhe lalingu-Amnoni indodana ka-Ahinowama owaseJezerili;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:1">owesibili, uDanyeli indodana ka-Abhigeli waseKhameli;<verse eid="1CH 3:1"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 3:2"/>owesithathu, ngu-Abhisalomu indodana kaMahakha indodakazi kaThalimayi inkosi yaseGeshuri;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:2">owesine, u-Adonija indodana kaHagithi;<verse eid="1CH 3:2"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 3:3"/>owesihlanu, uShefathiya indodana ka-Abhithali;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:3">owesithupha, u-Ithireyamu amzuza ku-Egila, umkakhe.<verse eid="1CH 3:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 3:4"/>Abayisithupha laba uDavida wabazalela eHebhroni, lapho abusa khona okweminyaka eyisikhombisa lezinyanga eziyisithupha.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 3:4"/>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 3:4"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 3:4">UDavida wabusa eJerusalema okweminyaka engamatshumi amathathu lemithathu, <verse eid="1CH 3:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 3:5"/>njalo la yiwo amadodana awazalela khona:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 3:5"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:5">uShamuwa, uShobabi, uNathani loSolomoni. Amadodana amane la wawazala loBhathishebha indodakazi ka-Amiyeli.<verse eid="1CH 3:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 3:6"/>Njalo kwaba lo-Ibhari, u-Elishama, u-Elifelethi, <verse eid="1CH 3:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 3:7"/>uNoga, uNefegi, uJafiya, <verse eid="1CH 3:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 3:8"/>u-Elishama, u-Eliyada kanye lo-Elifelethi, beyisificamunwemunye bonke.<verse eid="1CH 3:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 3:9"/>Bonke laba babengamadodana kaDavida, ngaphandle kwamadodana akhe awazala labafazi bakhe beceleni. Udadewabo wamadodana la wayenguThamari.<verse eid="1CH 3:9"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Amakhosi AkoJuda</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 3:10"/>Indodana kaSolomoni kwakunguRehobhowami,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:10">indodana yakhe kungu-Abhija,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:10">indodana yakhe kungu-Asa,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:10">indodana yakhe kunguJehoshafathi,<verse eid="1CH 3:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 3:11"/>indodana yakhe kunguJehoramu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:11">indodana yakhe kungu-Ahaziya,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:11">indodana yakhe kunguJowashi,<verse eid="1CH 3:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 3:12"/>indodana yakhe kungu-Amaziya,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:12">indodana yakhe kungu-Azariya,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:12">indodana yakhe kunguJothamu,<verse eid="1CH 3:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 3:13"/>indodana yakhe kungu-Ahazi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:13">indodana yakhe kunguHezekhiya,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:13">indodana yakhe kunguManase,<verse eid="1CH 3:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 3:14"/>indodana yakhe kungu-Amoni,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:14">indodana yakhe kunguJosiya.<verse eid="1CH 3:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 3:15"/>Amadodana kaJosiya yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:15">nguJohanani izibulo,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:15">uJehoyakhimi indodana yesibili,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:15">uZedekhiya eyesithathu,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:15">uShalumi eyesine.<verse eid="1CH 3:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 3:16"/>Abasala behlala esikhundleni sikaJehoyakhimi yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:16">nguJekhoniya indodana yakhe</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:16">loZedekhiya.<verse eid="1CH 3:16"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Usendo Lwesikhosini Emva Kokuthunjwa</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 3:17"/>Abosendo lukaJekhoniya owayethunjiwe yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:17">uSheyalithiyeli indodana yakhe, <verse eid="1CH 3:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 3:18"/>uMalikhiramu, loPhedaya, loShenazari, loJekhamiya, loHoshama, kanye loNedabhiya.<verse eid="1CH 3:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 3:19"/>Amadodana kaPhedaya yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:19">nguZerubhabheli loShimeyi.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 3:19">Amadodana kaZerubhabheli yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:19">nguMeshulami loHananiya. UShelomithi engudadewabo. <verse eid="1CH 3:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 3:20"/>Babekhona njalo abanye abahlanu: uHashubha, u-Oheli, uBherekhiya, uHasadiya, loJushabi-Hesedi.<verse eid="1CH 3:20"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 3:21"/>Abosendo lukaHananiya yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:21">nguPhelathiya loJeshaya, kanye lamadodana kaRefaya, ka-Anani, ka-Obhadaya kanye lokaShekhaniya.<verse eid="1CH 3:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 3:22"/>Abosendo lukaShekhaniya yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:22">nguShemaya lamadodana akhe: uHathushi, lo-Igali, loBhariya, loNeyariya kanye loShafathi, beyisithupha.<verse eid="1CH 3:22"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 3:23"/>Amadodana kaNeyariya yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:23">ngu-Eliyonayi, loHezekhiya, lo-Azirikhamu, bebathathu.<verse eid="1CH 3:23"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 3:24"/>Amadodana ka-Eliyonayi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 3:24">nguHodaviya, lo-Eliyashibi, loPhelaya, lo-Akhubi, loJohanani, loDelaya kanye lo-Anani, beyisikhombisa.<verse eid="1CH 3:24"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 3"/>
  <chapter number="4" style="c" sid="1CH 4"/>
  <para style="s2">Abanye Abosendo LukaJuda</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 4:1"/>Abosendo lukaJuda kuyilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:1">NguPherezi, loHezironi, loKhami, loHuri loShobhali.<verse eid="1CH 4:1"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 4:2"/>UReyaya indodana kaShobhali wayenguyise kaJahathi, uJahathi onguyise ka-Ahumayi kanye loLahadi. Laba babengabosendo lwamaZorathi.<verse eid="1CH 4:2"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 4:3"/>La ayengamadodana ka-Ethamu:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:3">uJezerili, lo-Ishima kanye lo-Idibhashi. Udadewabo kwakuthiwa nguHazeleliphoni. <verse eid="1CH 4:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 4:4"/>UPhenuweli wayenguyise kaGedori, lo-Ezeri uyise kaHusha.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 4:4">Laba kungabosendo lukaHuri, izibulo lika-Efrathi uyise kaBhethilehema.<verse eid="1CH 4:4"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 4:5"/>U-Ashuri uyise kaThekhowa wayelabafazi ababili, uHela loNara.<verse eid="1CH 4:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 4:6"/>UNahara wamzalela u-Ahuzami, loHeferi, loThemeni kanye loHahashithari. Laba kwakungabosendo lukaNara.<verse eid="1CH 4:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 4:7"/>Amadodana kaHela yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:7">nguZerethi, loZohari, lo-Ethinani, <verse eid="1CH 4:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 4:8"/>loKhozi owayenguyise ka-Anubi loHazobhebha kanye labosendo luka-Ahareheli indodana kaHarumi.<verse eid="1CH 4:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 4:9"/>UJabhezi wayelodumo kulabafowabo. Unina wayemuphe lelibizo lokuthi Jabhezi, ngoba esithi âNgamzala kabuhlungu.â <verse eid="1CH 4:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 4:10"/>UJabhezi wakhuleka kuNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli wathi: âSengathi ungangibusisa uqhelise ilizwe lami! Isandla sakho kasibe lami, ungivikele ebubini, ngingehlelwa yibuhlungu.â UNkulunkulu wamnika lokho ayekucela.<verse eid="1CH 4:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 4:11"/>UKhelubi, umfowabo kaShuha, wayenguyise kaMehiri, owayenguyise ka-Eshithoni. <verse eid="1CH 4:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 4:12"/>U-Eshithoni wayenguyise kaBhethi-Rafa, loPhaseya kanye loThehina uyise ka-Iri Nahashi. Laba babengabantu bakaRekha.<verse eid="1CH 4:12"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 4:13"/>Amadodana kaKhenazi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:13">ngu-Othiniyeli loSeraya.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 4:13">Amadodana ka-Othiniyeli yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:13">nguHathathi loMeyonothayi. <verse eid="1CH 4:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 4:14"/>UMeyonathayi wayenguyise ka-Ofira.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 4:14">USeraya wayenguyise kaJowabi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:14">owayengukhokho wesizwe samaGe-Harashimi. Babizwa ngalelibizo ngoba babezingcitshi.<verse eid="1CH 4:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 4:15"/>Amadodana kaKhalebi indodana kaJefune yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:15">ngu-Iru, lo-Ela kanye loNamu.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 4:15">Indodana ka-Ela yile:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:15">nguKhenazi.<verse eid="1CH 4:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 4:16"/>Amadodana kaJehaleleli yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:16">nguZifi, loZifa, loThiriya kanye lo-Asareli.<verse eid="1CH 4:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 4:17"/>Amadodana ka-Ezra yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:17">nguJetha, loMeredi, lo-Eferi kanye loJaloni.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 4:17">Omunye wabafazi bakaMeredi wazala uMiriyemu, loShamayi kanye lo-Ishibha uyise ka-Eshithemowa. <verse eid="1CH 4:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 4:18"/>Laba kwakungabantwana bakaBhithiya indodakazi kaFaro, eyayendele kuMeredi.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 4:18">Umkakhe ongumJudakazi wamzalela uJeredi uyise kaGedori, uHebheri uyise kaSokho, loJekuthiweli uyise kaZanowa.<verse eid="1CH 4:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 4:19"/>Amadodana omkaHodiya, udadewabo kaNahama,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:19">uyise kaKheyila owaseGami, lo-Eshithemowa waseMahakhathi.<verse eid="1CH 4:19"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 4:20"/>Amadodana kaShimoni yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:20">ngu-Amnoni, loRina, loBheni-Hanani kanye loThiloni.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 4:20">Abosendo luka-Ishi yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:20">nguZohethi loBheni-Zohethi.<verse eid="1CH 4:20"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 4:21"/>Amadodana kaShela indodana kaJuda yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:21">ngu-Eri uyise kaLekha, loLada uyise kaMaresha labantwana babeluki bamalembu amahle eBhethi-Ashibheya.<verse eid="1CH 4:21"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 4:22"/>UJokhimu, lamadoda aseKhozeba, uJowashi loSarafi, owabusa amaMowabi loJashubi Lehemu. (Lokhu kutholakala emibhalweni yasendulo). <verse eid="1CH 4:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 4:23"/>Laba kwakungababumbi ababehlala eNethayimi leGedera; behlala khona besebenzela inkosi.<verse eid="1CH 4:23"/></para>
  <para style="s1">USimiyoni</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 4:24"/>Abosendo lukaSimiyoni yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:24">nguNemuweli, loJamini, loJaribhi, loZera kanye loShawuli;<verse eid="1CH 4:24"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 4:25"/>uShalumi wayeyindodana kaShawuli, uMibhisamu indodana yakhe loMishima indodana yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 4:25"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 4:26"/>Abosendo lukaMishima yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 4:26">nguHamuweli indodana yakhe, loZakhuri indodana yakhe loShimeyi indodana yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 4:26"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 4:27"/>UShimeyi wayelamadodana alitshumi lesithupha lamadodakazi ayisithupha, kodwa abafowabo babengelabantwana abanengi, ngakho usendo lwabo lonke aluzanga lwande njengabantu bakaJuda. <verse eid="1CH 4:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 4:28"/>Babehlala eBherishebha, eMolada, eHazari-Shuwali, <verse eid="1CH 4:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 4:29"/>eBhiliha, e-Ezema, eTholadi, <verse eid="1CH 4:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 4:30"/>eBhethuweli, eHoma, eZikhilagi, <verse eid="1CH 4:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 4:31"/>eBhethi-Makhabhothi, eHazari Susimi, eBhethi-Bhiri laseShaharayimu. Yiyo eyayiyimizi yabo kwaze kwabusa uDavida. <verse eid="1CH 4:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 4:32"/>Imizana eyayilapho kwakuyi-Ethamu, i-Ayini, iRimoni, iThokheni le-Ashani, imizi emihlanu <verse eid="1CH 4:32"/><verse number="33" style="v" sid="1CH 4:33"/>layo yonke imizana eyayiseduzane lalimizi kuze kuyefika eBhalathi. Lezi yizo izindawo abahlaliswa khona.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 4:33"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 4:33">Bagcina imibhalo yosendo lwabo.<verse eid="1CH 4:33"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="1CH 4:34"/>UMeshobabi loJamuleki,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 4:34">loJosha indodana ka-Amaziya <verse eid="1CH 4:34"/><verse number="35" style="v" sid="1CH 4:35"/>loJoweli,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 4:35">loJehu indodana kaJoshibhiya, indodana kaSeraya, indodana ka-Asiyeli<verse eid="1CH 4:35"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="1CH 4:36"/>kanye lo-Eliyonayi, loJakhobha, loJeshohaya,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 4:36">lo-Asaya, lo-Adiyeli, loJesimiyeli, loBhenaya,<verse eid="1CH 4:36"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="1CH 4:37"/>kanye loZiza indodana kaShifi, indodana ka-Aloni, indodana kaJedaya, indodana kaShimiri, indodana kaShemaya.<verse eid="1CH 4:37"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="1CH 4:38"/>Amadoda aqanjiweyo ngamabizo ngaphezulu ayengabakhokheli bosendo lwakwabo.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 4:38"/>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 4:38">Izimuli zabo zanda kakhulu, <verse eid="1CH 4:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="1CH 4:39"/>zaqhela zayakwakha langaphandle kweGedori okuya ngempumalanga yesihotsha bedinga amadlelo emihlambi yabo. <verse eid="1CH 4:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="1CH 4:40"/>Bathola umhlaba ovundileyo olamadlelo amahle, obanzi ophilileyo njalo uthule. Kwakuke kwahlala amanye amaHamu khonapho.<verse eid="1CH 4:40"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="1CH 4:41"/>Amadoda alamabizo abhaliweyo afika ngezinsuku zikaHezekhiya inkosi yakoJuda. Bahlasela amaHamu emizini yawo kanye lamaMewuni ayelapho bawabhuqa du, njengoba kubonakala lalamuhla. Basebezihlalela besakha khonapho, ngoba kwakulamadlelo emihlambi yabo. <verse eid="1CH 4:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="1CH 4:42"/>Abangamakhulu amahlanu alaba abakaSimiyoni, bekhokhelwa nguPhelathiya, uNeyariya loRefaya lo-Uziyeli amadodana ka-Ishi, bahlasela ilizwe lamaqaqa laseSeyiri. <verse eid="1CH 4:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="1CH 4:43"/>Babulala ama-Amaleki ayephunyukile asala, njalo sebehlale kulindawo kuze kube lamuhla.<verse eid="1CH 4:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 4"/>
  <chapter number="5" style="c" sid="1CH 5"/>
  <para style="s1">URubheni</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 5:1"/>Amadodana kaRubheni izibulo lika-Israyeli (wayelizibulo, kodwa kwathi esengcolise umbheda kayise owomtshado, amalungelo akhe njengezibulo aphiwa amadodana kaJosefa indodana ka-Israyeli, ngakho kasalotshwanga emibhalweni yosendo njengelungelo lokuzalwa kwakhe, <verse eid="1CH 5:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 5:2"/>lanxa uJuda wayelamandla amakhulu kulabo bonke abafowabo njalo enguye owazala umbusi, ilungelo lobuzibulo laya kuJosefa). <verse eid="1CH 5:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 5:3"/>Amadodana kaRubheni izibulo lika-Israyeli ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 5:3"/>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 5:3">nguHanokhi, loPhalu, loHezironi kanye loKhami.<verse eid="1CH 5:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 5:4"/>Abenzalo kaJoweli yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 5:4">nguShemaya indodana yakhe, loGogi indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 5:4">loShimeyi indodana yakhe, <verse eid="1CH 5:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 5:5"/>loMikha indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 5:5">loReyaya indodana yakhe, loBhali indodana yakhe,<verse eid="1CH 5:5"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 5:6"/>kanye loBhera indodana yakhe, lowo uThigilathi-Philesa inkosi yase-Asiriya eyamthumba yamusa ezizweni. UBhera wayengumkhokheli wabakoRubheni.<verse eid="1CH 5:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 5:7"/>Izihlobo zabo ngosendo lwabo, njengokulotshwe emibhalweni yosendo yilezi:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 5:7">nguJeyiyeli induna, loZakhariya, kanye <verse eid="1CH 5:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 5:8"/>loBhela indodana ka-Azazi, indodana kaShema, indodana kaJoweli.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 5:8"/>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 5:8">Bakha bahlala emangweni osuka e-Aroweri kusiya eNebho laseBhali-Meyoni. <verse eid="1CH 5:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 5:9"/>Empumalanga babehlezi emangweni ofika emaphethelweni enkangala etshaya khonale eMfuleni uYufrathe, ngoba izifuyo zabo zasezandile eGiliyadi.<verse eid="1CH 5:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 5:10"/>Ngezinsuku zokubusa kukaSawuli balwa impi lamaHagari; bawanqoba basebehlala emizaneni yawo emangweni wonke ongempumalanga yeGiliyadi.<verse eid="1CH 5:10"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UGadi</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 5:11"/>AbakaGadi babehlala phansi kwabo eBhashani, kuze kuyefika eSalekha:<verse eid="1CH 5:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 5:12"/>UJoweli wayeyinduna, uShafamu emlandela, besekusiza uJanayi loShafathi, ngaseBhashani.<verse eid="1CH 5:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 5:13"/>Izihlobo zabo, ngokuzalana kwabo, yilezi:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 5:13">nguMikhayeli, loMeshulami, loShebha, loJorayi, loJakhani, loZiya kanye lo-Ebha, beyisikhombisa sebendawonye.<verse eid="1CH 5:13"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 5:14"/>Laba babengamadodana ka-Abhihayili indodana kaHuri, indodana kaJarowa, indodana kaGiliyadi, indodana kaMikhayeli, indodana kaJeshishayi, indodana kaJahido, indodana kaBhuzi.<verse eid="1CH 5:14"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 5:15"/>U-Ahi indodana ka-Abhidiyeli, indodana kaGuni, wayeyinhloko yemuli yakwabo.<verse eid="1CH 5:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 5:16"/>AbakaGadi babehlala eGiliyadi, eBhashani lemizaneni yakhona, kanye lasemadlelweni aseSharoni kuze kuyefika emaphethelweni awo.<verse eid="1CH 5:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 5:17"/>Bonke laba balotshwa emibhalweni yosendo ngezinsuku zokubusa kukaJothamu inkosi yakoJuda loJerobhowamu inkosi yako-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 5:17"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 5:18"/>AbakoRubheni, labakoGadi lengxenye yesizwana sakoManase babelamadoda ayeselungele ukubuthwa azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane lane lamakhulu ayisikhombisa lamatshumi ayisithupha (44,760) amadoda ayeseqwahele esenelisa ukuphatha ihawu ahlome ngenkemba, atshoke ngemitshoko, ayesevele afundela ukulwa empini. <verse eid="1CH 5:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 5:19"/>Bahlasela uHagari loJethuri loNafishi loNodabi. <verse eid="1CH 5:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 5:20"/>Bahlonyulelwa ekulweni kwabo labo, njalo uNkulunkulu wanikela uHagari labanye bakhe ezandleni zabo, ngoba bakhuleka kuNkulunkulu empini. Wayiphendula imikhuleko yabo, ngoba bamethemba. <verse eid="1CH 5:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 5:21"/>Bathumba izifuyo zakoHagiri ezibalisa amakamela azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amahlanu, izimvu eziyizinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amahlanu labobabhemi abazinkulungwane ezimbili. Bathumba njalo abantu abazinkulungwane ezilikhulu, <verse eid="1CH 5:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 5:22"/>abanye abanengi babulawa, ngoba le kwakuyimpi kaNkulunkulu. Bona bahlala kulelolizwe kwaze kwaba yisikhathi bethunjwa.<verse eid="1CH 5:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ingxenye Yesizwana SikaManase</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 5:23"/>Abantu ababeyingxenye yesizwana sikaManase babebanengi; bahlala elizweni kusukela eBhashani kusiya eBhali-Hemoni, kusitsho iSeniri (iNtaba yaseHemoni).<verse eid="1CH 5:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 5:24"/>Laba yibo ababezinhloko zezimuli: u-Eferi, lo-Ishi, lo-Eliyeli, lo-Aziriyeli, loJeremiya, loHodaviya, kanye loJahidiyeli. Babengamadoda empi alezibindi, amadoda adumileyo, njalo bezinhloko zezimuli zabo. <verse eid="1CH 5:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 5:25"/>Kodwa bona babengathembekanga kuNkulunkulu waboyise basebekhonza onkulunkulu bezizwe uNkulunkulu wabo ababhubhisa kulawomazwe bengakahlali khona. <verse eid="1CH 5:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 5:26"/>Ngakho uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli wadunga umoya kaPhuli inkosi yase-Asiriya (okuyikuthi, Thigilathi-Philesa inkosi yase-Asiriya), owathumba abakoRubheni, labakoGadi kanye lengxenye yesizwana sikaManase. Wabathatha wabasa eHala, leHabhori, leHara lasemfuleni uGozani, lapho abakhona lalamuhla.<verse eid="1CH 5:26"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 5"/>
  <chapter number="6" style="c" sid="1CH 6"/>
  <para style="s1">ULevi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 6:1"/>Amadodana kaLevi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:1">nguGeshoni, loKhohathi, kanye loMerari.<verse eid="1CH 6:1"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 6:2"/>Amadodana kaKhohathi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:2">ngu-Amramu, lo-Izihari, loHebhroni kanye lo-Uziyeli.<verse eid="1CH 6:2"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 6:3"/>Abantwana baka-Amramu yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:3">ngu-Aroni, loMosi kanye loMiriyemu.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 6:3">Amadodana ka-Aroni yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:3">nguNadabi, lo-Abhihu lo-Eliyazari lo-Ithamari.<verse eid="1CH 6:3"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 6:4"/>U-Eliyazari wayenguyise kaFinehasi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:4">uFinehasi enguyise ka-Abhishuwa,<verse eid="1CH 6:4"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 6:5"/>u-Abhishuwa enguyise kaBhukhi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:5">uBhukhi enguyise ka-Uzi,<verse eid="1CH 6:5"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 6:6"/>u-Uzi enguyise kaZerahiya,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:6">uZerahiya enguyise kaMerayothi,<verse eid="1CH 6:6"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 6:7"/>uMerayothi enguyise ka-Amariya,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:7">u-Amariya enguyise ka-Ahithubi,<verse eid="1CH 6:7"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 6:8"/>u-Ahithubi enguyise kaZadokhi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:8">uZadokhi enguyise ka-Ahimazi,<verse eid="1CH 6:8"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 6:9"/>u-Ahimazi enguyise ka-Azariya,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:9">u-Azariya enguyise kaJohanani,<verse eid="1CH 6:9"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 6:10"/>uJohanani enguyise ka-Azariya;</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:10">nguye lo owayengumphristi ethempelini elakhiwa nguSolomoni eJerusalema.<verse eid="1CH 6:10"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 6:11"/>U-Azariya enguyise ka-Amariya,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:11">u-Amariya enguyise ka-Ahithubi,<verse eid="1CH 6:11"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 6:12"/>u-Ahithubi enguyise kaZadokhi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:12">uZadokhi enguyise kaShalumi,<verse eid="1CH 6:12"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 6:13"/>uShalumi enguyise kaHilikhiya,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:13">uHilikhiya enguyise ka-Azariya,<verse eid="1CH 6:13"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 6:14"/>u-Azariya enguyise kaSeraya,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:14">uSeraya enguyise kaJozadaki.<verse eid="1CH 6:14"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 6:15"/>UJozadaki wathunjwa lapho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> athumba abakoJuda labaseJerusalema ngesandla sikaNebhukhadineza.<verse eid="1CH 6:15"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 6:16"/>Amadodana kaLevi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:16">nguGeshoni, loKhohathi kanye loMerari.<verse eid="1CH 6:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 6:17"/>Nanka amabizo amadodana kaGeshoni:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:17">nguLibhini loShimeyi.<verse eid="1CH 6:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 6:18"/>Amadodana kaKhohathi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:18">ngu-Amramu, lo-Izihari, loHebhroni kanye lo-Uziyeli.<verse eid="1CH 6:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 6:19"/>Amadodana kaMerari yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:19">nguMahili loMushi.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 6:19"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 6:19">Laba babelusendo lwabaLevi behlelwe ngoluhlu lwaboyise:<verse eid="1CH 6:19"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 6:20"/>AbakaGeshoni yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:20">nguLibhini indodana yakhe, loJahathi indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:20">loZima indodana yakhe, <verse eid="1CH 6:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 6:21"/>loJowa indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:21">lo-Ido indodana yakhe, loZera indodana yakhe kanye</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:21">loJeyatherayi indodana yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 6:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 6:22"/>Abosendo lukaKhohathi yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:22">ngu-Aminadabi indodana yakhe, loKhora indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:22">lo-Asiri indodana yakhe, <verse eid="1CH 6:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 6:23"/>lo-Elikhana</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:23">lo-Ebhiyasafi indodana yakhe lo-Asiri indodana yakhe,<verse eid="1CH 6:23"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 6:24"/>loThahathi indodana yakhe, lo-Uriyeli indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:24">lo-Uziya indodana yakhe kanye loShawuli indodana yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 6:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 6:25"/>Abosendo luka-Elikhana yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:25">ngu-Amasayi, lo-Ahimothi,<verse eid="1CH 6:25"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 6:26"/>lo-Elikhana indodana yakhe, loZofayi indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:26">loNahathi indodana yakhe, <verse eid="1CH 6:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 6:27"/>lo-Eliyabi indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:27">loJerohamu indodana yakhe, lo-Elikhana indodana yakhe kanye</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:27">loSamuyeli indodana yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 6:27"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 6:28"/>Amadodana kaSamuyeli ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:28">uVashini izibulo</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:28">lo-Abhija indodana yesibili.<verse eid="1CH 6:28"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 6:29"/>Abosendo lukaMerari yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:29">nguMahili, loLibhini indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:29">loShimeyi indodana yakhe, lo-Uza indodana yakhe,<verse eid="1CH 6:29"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 6:30"/>loShimeya indodana yakhe, loHagiya indodana yakhe kanye</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:30">lo-Asaya indodana yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 6:30"/></para>
  <para style="s2">Abahlabeleli BaseThempelini</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 6:31"/>Laba yibo abakhethwa nguDavida ukuphatha ukuhlabelela endlini <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> ngemva kokubekwa kwebhokisi lesivumelwano khona. <verse eid="1CH 6:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 6:32"/>Bakhonza ngokuhlabelela phambi kwebhokisi lesivumelwano, iThente lokuHlanganela, uSolomoni waze wakha ithempeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> eJerusalema. Benza inkonzo yabo ngendlela okwakuqoqwe ngayo.<verse eid="1CH 6:32"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="1CH 6:33"/>Bona ababekhethelwe lowomsebenzi kanye lamadodana abo yilaba:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 6:33"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 6:33">Kwabendlu kaKhohathi yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:33">nguHemani umhlabeleli,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:33">indodana kaJoweli, indodana kaSamuyeli<verse eid="1CH 6:33"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="1CH 6:34"/>indodana ka-Elikhana, indodana kaJerohamu,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:34">indodana ka-Eliyeli, indodana kaThowa,<verse eid="1CH 6:34"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="1CH 6:35"/>indodana kaZufi, indodana ka-Elikhana,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:35">indodana kaMahathi, indodana ka-Amasayi,<verse eid="1CH 6:35"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="1CH 6:36"/>indodana ka-Elikhana, indodana kaJoweli,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:36">indodana ka-Azariya, indodana kaZefaniya<verse eid="1CH 6:36"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="1CH 6:37"/>indodana kaThahathi, indodana ka-Asiri,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:37">indodana ka-Ebhiyasafi, indodana kaKhora,<verse eid="1CH 6:37"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="1CH 6:38"/>indodana ka-Izihari, indodana kaKhohathi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:38">indodana kaLevi, indodana ka-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 6:38"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="1CH 6:39"/>U-Asafi umkhula kaHemani owasebenza laye ngasesandleni sakhe sokudla:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:39">U-Asafi indodana kaBherekhiya, indodana kaShimeya,<verse eid="1CH 6:39"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="1CH 6:40"/>indodana kaMikhayeli, indodana kaBhaseya,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:40">indodana kaMalikhija, <verse eid="1CH 6:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="1CH 6:41"/>indodana ka-Ethini,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:41">indodana kaZera, indodana ka-Adaya,<verse eid="1CH 6:41"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="1CH 6:42"/>indodana ka-Ethani, indodana kaZima,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:42">indodana kaShimeyi, <verse eid="1CH 6:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="1CH 6:43"/>indodana kaJahathi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:43">indodana kaGeshoni, indodana kaLevi;<verse eid="1CH 6:43"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="1CH 6:44"/>kanti njalo kubakhula babo amaMerari kwesenxele isandla sakhe yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:44">ngu-Ethani indodana kaKhishi, indodana ka-Abhidi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:44">indodana kaMaluki, <verse eid="1CH 6:44"/><verse number="45" style="v" sid="1CH 6:45"/>indodana kaHashabhiya,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:45">indodana ka-Amaziya, indodana kaHilikhiya,<verse eid="1CH 6:45"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="1CH 6:46"/>indodana ka-Amizi, indodana kaBhani,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:46">indodana kaShemeri, <verse eid="1CH 6:46"/><verse number="47" style="v" sid="1CH 6:47"/>indodana kaMahili,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:47">indodana kaMushi, indodana kaMerari,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:47">indodana kaLevi.<verse eid="1CH 6:47"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="48" style="v" sid="1CH 6:48"/>Abafowabo kubaLevi babephiwe yonke eminye imisebenzi ethabanikeleni, endlini kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="1CH 6:48"/><verse number="49" style="v" sid="1CH 6:49"/>Kodwa u-Aroni labosendo lwakhe yibo ababesethula iminikelo yokutshiswa e-alithareni kanye lase-alithareni lempepha lakho konke okwakusenziwa eNdaweni eNgcwele kakhulu, becelela u-Israyeli umusa, njengalokhu uMosi inceku kaNkulunkulu yayitshilo.<verse eid="1CH 6:49"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="50" style="v" sid="1CH 6:50"/>Laba ngabosendo luka-Aroni:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:50">ngu-Eliyazari indodana yakhe, loFinehasi indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:50">lo-Abhishuwa indodana yakhe, <verse eid="1CH 6:50"/><verse number="51" style="v" sid="1CH 6:51"/>loBhukhi indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:51">lo-Uzi indodana yakhe, loZerahiya indodana yakhe,<verse eid="1CH 6:51"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="52" style="v" sid="1CH 6:52"/>loMerayothi indodana yakhe, lo-Amariya indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:52">lo-Ahithubi indodana yakhe, <verse eid="1CH 6:52"/><verse number="53" style="v" sid="1CH 6:53"/>loZadokhi indodana yakhe kanye</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 6:53">lo-Ahimazi indodana yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 6:53"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="54" style="v" sid="1CH 6:54"/>Imizi ababehlezi kiyo kuselizweni ababeliphiwe (yimizi eyayiphiwe abosendo luka-Aroni beyinzalo kaKhohathi, ngoba isabelo sakuqala sasingesabo) yile:<verse eid="1CH 6:54"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="55" style="v" sid="1CH 6:55"/>Babephiwe iHebhroni koJuda lamadlelo akhona. <verse eid="1CH 6:55"/><verse number="56" style="v" sid="1CH 6:56"/>Kodwa amasimu lemizana eyayiseduzane ledolobho kwaphiwa uKhalebi indodana kaJefune. <verse eid="1CH 6:56"/><verse number="57" style="v" sid="1CH 6:57"/>Ngakho abosendo luka-Aroni baphiwa iHebhroni (umuzi wokuphephela), leLibhina, leJathiri, le-Eshithemowa, <verse eid="1CH 6:57"/><verse number="58" style="v" sid="1CH 6:58"/>leHileni, leDebhiri, <verse eid="1CH 6:58"/><verse number="59" style="v" sid="1CH 6:59"/>le-Ashani, leJuta leBhethi-Shemeshi, ndawonye lamadlelo akhona.<verse eid="1CH 6:59"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="60" style="v" sid="1CH 6:60"/>Esizwaneni sikaBhenjamini baphiwa iGibhiyoni, leGebha, le-Alemethi le-Anathothi, kanye lamadlelo akhona.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 6:60">Imizi eyaphiwa amaKhohathi yayilitshumi lantathu.<verse eid="1CH 6:60"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="61" style="v" sid="1CH 6:61"/>Abaseleyo bamaKhohathi baphiwa imizi elitshumi beyingxenye yendlu yesizwana sikaManase.<verse eid="1CH 6:61"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="62" style="v" sid="1CH 6:62"/>Abosendo lukaGeshoni, indlu ngendlu, baphiwa imizi elitshumi lemithathu ezizwaneni zako-Isakhari, ko-Asheri lakoNafithali, kanye lengxenye yesizwana sikaManase esiseBhashani.<verse eid="1CH 6:62"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="63" style="v" sid="1CH 6:63"/>Abosendo lukaMerari, indlu ngendlu, baphiwa imizi elitshumi lambili esizwaneni sikaRubheni, lesikaGadi lesikaZebhuluni.<verse eid="1CH 6:63"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="64" style="v" sid="1CH 6:64"/>Ngakho yiyo imizi lamadlelo ayo eyaphiwa abaLevi ngama-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 6:64"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="65" style="v" sid="1CH 6:65"/>Esizwaneni sakoJuda, lesakoSimiyoni loBhenjamini baphiwa imizi esike yaqanjwa.<verse eid="1CH 6:65"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="66" style="v" sid="1CH 6:66"/>Amanye amaKhohathi aphiwa imizi elizweni lesizwana sika-Efrayimi.<verse eid="1CH 6:66"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="67" style="v" sid="1CH 6:67"/>Elizweni lamaqaqa lika-Efrayimi baphiwa iShekhemu (umuzi wokuphephela) leGezeri, <verse eid="1CH 6:67"/><verse number="68" style="v" sid="1CH 6:68"/>leJokhimeyamu, leBhethi-Horoni, <verse eid="1CH 6:68"/><verse number="69" style="v" sid="1CH 6:69"/>le-Ayijaloni leGathi-Rimoni, kanye lamadlelo akhona.<verse eid="1CH 6:69"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="70" style="v" sid="1CH 6:70"/>Engxenyeni yesizwana sikaManase abako-Israyeli, banika insalela yamaKhohathi, i-Aneri leBhileyamu kanye lamadlelo akhona.<verse eid="1CH 6:70"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="71" style="v" sid="1CH 6:71"/>AmaGeshoni azuza lezindawo:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 6:71">Kwabosendo lwengxenye yesizwana sikaManase bazuza iGolani eBhashani kanye le-Ashitharothi, ndawonye lamadlelo akhona;<verse eid="1CH 6:71"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="72" style="v" sid="1CH 6:72"/>esizwaneni sika-Isakhari bazuza iKhedeshi, leDabherathi, <verse eid="1CH 6:72"/><verse number="73" style="v" sid="1CH 6:73"/>leRamothi le-Anema lamadlelo akhona;<verse eid="1CH 6:73"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="74" style="v" sid="1CH 6:74"/>esizwaneni sika-Asheri bazuza iMashali, le-Abhidoni, <verse eid="1CH 6:74"/><verse number="75" style="v" sid="1CH 6:75"/>leHukhokhi leRehobhi, kanye lamadlelo akhona;<verse eid="1CH 6:75"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="76" style="v" sid="1CH 6:76"/>esizwaneni sikaNafithali bazuza iKhedeshi eGalile, leHamoni, leKhiriyathayimi kanye lamadlelo akhona.<verse eid="1CH 6:76"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="77" style="v" sid="1CH 6:77"/>AmaMerari (insalela yabaLevi) aphiwa kanje:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 6:77">esizwaneni sikaZebhuluni azuza iJokhiniyamu, iKhatha, iRimoni leThabhori, kanye lamadlelo akhona;<verse eid="1CH 6:77"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="78" style="v" sid="1CH 6:78"/>esizwaneni sikaRubheni ngaphetsheya kweJodani ngempumalanga yeJerikho azuza iBhezeri enkangala, leJahazi, <verse eid="1CH 6:78"/><verse number="79" style="v" sid="1CH 6:79"/>leKhedemothi kanye leMefahathi lamadlelo akhona;<verse eid="1CH 6:79"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="80" style="v" sid="1CH 6:80"/>lasesizwaneni sikaGadi azuza iRamothi eGiliyadi, leMahanayimi, <verse eid="1CH 6:80"/><verse number="81" style="v" sid="1CH 6:81"/>leHeshibhoni, leJazeri, kanye lamadlelo akhona.<verse eid="1CH 6:81"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 6"/>
  <chapter number="7" style="c" sid="1CH 7"/>
  <para style="s1">U-Isakhari</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 7:1"/>Amadodana ka-Isakhari yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:1">nguThola, loPhuwa, loJashubi loShimroni, bonke babebane.<verse eid="1CH 7:1"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 7:2"/>Amadodana kaThola yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:2">ngu-Uzi, loRefaya, loJeriyeli, loJahamali, lo-Ibhisamu loSamuyeli, bonke bezinhloko zezindlu zabo. Ngezinsuku uDavida esabusa, abosendo lukaThola abangamadoda aselindele impi ngoluhlu lokuzalana kwabo, babengamadoda ayezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lambili lamakhulu ayisithupha (22,600).<verse eid="1CH 7:2"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 7:3"/>Indodana ka-Uzi kungu:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:3">Izrahiya.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 7:3">Amadodana ka-Izrahiya yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:3">nguMikhayeli, lo-Obhadaya, loJoweli lo-Ishiya. Ngobuhlanu babo babezinduna. <verse eid="1CH 7:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 7:4"/>Ngoluhlu lokuzalana kwabo, babelamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu lesithupha (36,000) ayeselungele ukuthi angaphuma ayekulwa impi, ngoba babelabafazi labantwana abanengi.<verse eid="1CH 7:4"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 7:5"/>Abayizihlobo abesilisa abasebefanele ukuthi bangaya empini bengabosendo luka-Isakhari, ngoluhlu lokuzalana kwabo, sebendawonye babezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisificaminwembili lesikhombisa (87,000).<verse eid="1CH 7:5"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UBhenjamini</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 7:6"/>Amadodana kaBhenjamini amathathu yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:6">nguBhela, loBhekheri loJediyeli.<verse eid="1CH 7:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 7:7"/>Amadodana kaBhela yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:7">ngu-Ezibhoni, lo-Uzi, lo-Uziyeli, loJerimothi lo-Iri, babebahlanu bonke, bezinhloko zezindlu zabo. Bona-ke ngoluhlu losendo lwabo babelamadoda ayelungele ukulwa empini azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lambili lamatshumi amathathu lane (22,034).<verse eid="1CH 7:7"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 7:8"/>Amadodana kaBhekheri yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:8">nguZemira, loJowashi, lo-Eliyezeri, lo-Eliyonayi, lo-Omri, loJeremothi, lo-Abhija, lo-Anathothi kanye lo-Alemethi. Wonke la kwakungamadodana kaBhekheri. <verse eid="1CH 7:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 7:9"/>Imbali yoluhlu lwezimuli zababezinhloko zemindeni ibalisa ukuthi babengabantu abazinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lamakhulu amabili amadoda empi (20,200).<verse eid="1CH 7:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 7:10"/>Indodana kaJediyeli</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:10">kwakunguBhilihani.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 7:10">Amadodana kaBhilihani yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:10">nguJewushi, loBhenjamini, lo-Ehudi, loKhenana, loZethani, loThashishi kanye lo-Ahishahari. <verse eid="1CH 7:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 7:11"/>Wonke lamadodana kaJediyeli ayeyizinhloko zezindlu zawo. Kwakulamadoda ayesefanele ukubuthwa ayekulwa empini azinkulungwane ezilitshumi lesikhombisa, lamakhulu amabili (17,200).<verse eid="1CH 7:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 7:12"/>AmaShuphimu lamaHuphimu ayengawosendo luka-Iri, lamaHushimu engawosendo luka-Aheri.<verse eid="1CH 7:12"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UNafithali</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 7:13"/>Amadodana kaNafithali yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:13">nguJaziyeli, loGuni, loJezeri kanye loShalumi, abosendo lukaBhiliha.<verse eid="1CH 7:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UManase</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 7:14"/>Abosendo lukaManase yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:14">ngu-Asiriyeli amzala lomfazi weceleni ongumÊ¼Aramu. Wazala uMakhiri uyise kaGiliyadi. <verse eid="1CH 7:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 7:15"/>UMakhiri wathatha umfazi ozalwa ngamaHuphimu lamaShuphimu. Udadewabo kwakunguMahakha. Omunye owosendo kwakunguZelofehadi owazala amankazana kuphela. <verse eid="1CH 7:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 7:16"/>UmkaMakhiri uMahakha wazala indodana yathiwa nguPhereshi. Umfowabo yena wethiwa ibizo elithi Shereshi, njalo amadodana akhe kwakungu-Ulamu loRakhemu.<verse eid="1CH 7:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 7:17"/>Indodana ka-Ulamu kungu:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:17">Bhedani.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 7:17">La ngamadodana kaGiliyadi, indodana kaMakhiri, indodana kaManase.<verse eid="1CH 7:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 7:18"/>Udadewabo uHamolekhethi wazala u-Ishodi, lo-Abhiyezeri loMahila.<verse eid="1CH 7:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 7:19"/>Amadodana kaShemida yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:19">ngu-Ahiyani, loShekhemu, loLikhi kanye lo-Aniyami.<verse eid="1CH 7:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">U-Efrayimi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 7:20"/>Abosendo luka-Efrayimi yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:20">nguShuthela, loBheredi indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:20">loThahathi indodana yakhe, lo-Eleyada indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:20">loThahathi indodana yakhe, <verse eid="1CH 7:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 7:21"/>loZabhadi indodana yakhe kanye</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:21">loShuthela indodana yakhe.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:21">(U-Ezeri lo-Eliyadi babulawa ngababezalwa eGathi, baze bayethumba izifuyo zabo. <verse eid="1CH 7:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 7:22"/>Uyise u-Efrayimi wabalilela okwensuku ezinengi, izihlobo zakhe zabuya ukuzomduduza. <verse eid="1CH 7:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 7:23"/>Walala njalo lomkakhe wakhulelwa, wazala indodana ayitha ibizo elithi Bheriya, kuyikutshengisa ukuthi kwakonakele phakathi kwemuli. <verse eid="1CH 7:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 7:24"/>Indodakazi yakhe kwakunguShera owakha iBhethi-Horoni yaPhansi leyaPhezulu kanye le-Uzeni-Shera.)<verse eid="1CH 7:24"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 7:25"/>URefa wayeyindodana yakhe, loReshefi indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:25">loThela indodana yakhe, loThahani indodana yakhe,<verse eid="1CH 7:25"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 7:26"/>loLadani indodana yakhe, lo-Amihudi indodana yakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:26">lo-Elishama indodana yakhe, <verse eid="1CH 7:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 7:27"/>loNuni indodana yakhe</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:27">kanye loJoshuwa indodana yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 7:27"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 7:28"/>Amazwe lemizi yabo yayihlanganisa iBhetheli lemizana eseduzane, iNaharani empumalanga, iGezeri lemizana yayo kusiya entshonalanga, iShekhemu lemizana yayo kusiyafika e-Aya lemizana yayo. <verse eid="1CH 7:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 7:29"/>Emingceleni yakwelakoManase kuleBhethi-Shani, leThanakhi, leMegido, kanye leDori lemizana yakhona. Ababehlala kulimizi ngabosendo lukaJosefa indodana ka-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 7:29"/></para>
  <para style="s1">U-Asheri</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 7:30"/>Amadodana ka-Asheri yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:30">ngu-Imna, lo-Ishiva, lo-Ishivi kanye loBheriya. Udadewabo kunguSera.<verse eid="1CH 7:30"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 7:31"/>Amadodana kaBheriya yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:31">nguHebheri loMalikhiyeli uyise kaBhirizayithi.<verse eid="1CH 7:31"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 7:32"/>UHebheri wayenguyise kaJafilethi, loShomeri loHothamu kanye lodadewabo uShuwa.<verse eid="1CH 7:32"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="1CH 7:33"/>Amadodana kaJafilethi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:33">nguPasaki, loBhimihali kanye lo-Ashivathi.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 7:33">Laba kwakungamadodana kaJafilethi.<verse eid="1CH 7:33"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="1CH 7:34"/>Amadodana kaShomeri yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:34">ngu-Ahi, loRohiga, loHubha kanye lo-Aramu.<verse eid="1CH 7:34"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="1CH 7:35"/>Amadodana omfowabo uHelemu yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:35">nguZofa, lo-Imna, loSheleshi kanye lo-Amali.<verse eid="1CH 7:35"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="1CH 7:36"/>Amadodana kaZofa yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:36">nguSuwa, loHarineferi, loShuwali, loBheri, lo-Imra, <verse eid="1CH 7:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="1CH 7:37"/>loBhezeri, loHodi, loShama, loShilisha, lo-Ithirani kanye loBhera.<verse eid="1CH 7:37"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="1CH 7:38"/>Amadodana kaJetha yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:38">nguJefune, loPhisipha kanye lo-Ara.<verse eid="1CH 7:38"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="1CH 7:39"/>Amadodana ka-Ula yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 7:39">ngu-Ara, loHaniyeli kanye loRiziya.<verse eid="1CH 7:39"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="1CH 7:40"/>Bonke laba babengabosendo luka-Asheri bezinhloko zendlu ngendlu, amadoda akhethiweyo, amabutho alesibindi njalo bengabakhokheli abalokuhlakanipha. Inani lamadoda ayesefanele ukubuthwa aye empini, kusiya ngoluhlu losendo lwakwabo, kwakuzinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lesithupha (26,000).<verse eid="1CH 7:40"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 7"/>
  <chapter number="8" style="c" sid="1CH 8"/>
  <para style="s1">Usendo LukaSawuli UmBhenjamini</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 8:1"/>UBhenjamini wayenguyise</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 8:1">kaBhela izibulo lakhe,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 8:1">lo-Ashibheli indodana yesibili, lo-Ahara eyesithathu,<verse eid="1CH 8:1"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 8:2"/>loNoha eyesine loRafa indodana yesihlanu.<verse eid="1CH 8:2"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 8:3"/>Amadodana kaBhela ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 8:3">u-Adari, uGera, u-Abhihudi, <verse eid="1CH 8:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 8:4"/>u-Abhishuwa, uNamani, u-Ahowa, <verse eid="1CH 8:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 8:5"/>uGera, uShefufani kanye loHuramu.<verse eid="1CH 8:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 8:6"/>Laba ngabosendo luka-Ehudi, ababezinhloko zezindlu zalabo ababehlala eGebha abaxotshelwa eManahathi:<verse eid="1CH 8:6"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 8:7"/>KunguNamani, lo-Ahija, kanye loGera owabaxotshayo njalo enguyise ka-Uza, lo-Ahihudi.<verse eid="1CH 8:7"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 8:8"/>Kulamadodana azalwa nguShaharayimi eMowabi ngemva kokwehlukana labafazi bakhe oHushimi loBhara. <verse eid="1CH 8:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 8:9"/>Emfazini wakhe uHodeshi wayelabantwana laba: uJobhabhi, loZibhiya, loMesha, loMalikhami, <verse eid="1CH 8:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 8:10"/>loJewuzi, loSakhiya kanye loMirima. Yiwo amadodana akhe, ayeyizinhloko zezindlu zawo. <verse eid="1CH 8:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 8:11"/>KuHushimi wazala u-Abhithubi lo-Eliphali.<verse eid="1CH 8:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 8:12"/>Amadodana ka-Eliphali ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 8:12">u-Ebheri, uMishami, uShemedi (nguye owakha i-Ono leLodi lemizana eseduzane layo), <verse eid="1CH 8:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 8:13"/>kanye loBheriya loShema, bona bezinhloko zezindlu zalabo ababehlala e-Ayijaloni abayibo njalo abaxotsha ababehlala eGathi.<verse eid="1CH 8:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 8:14"/>U-Ahiyo, uShashaki, uJeremothi, <verse eid="1CH 8:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 8:15"/>uZebhadiya, u-Aradi, u-Ederi, <verse eid="1CH 8:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 8:16"/>uMikhayeli, u-Ishipha kanye loJoha bengamadodana kaBheriya.<verse eid="1CH 8:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 8:17"/>UZebhadiya, uMeshulami, uHizikhi, uHebheri, <verse eid="1CH 8:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 8:18"/>u-Ishimerayi, u-Iziliya, loJobhabhi kungamadodana ka-Eliphali.<verse eid="1CH 8:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 8:19"/>UJakhimi, uZikhiri, uZabhidi, <verse eid="1CH 8:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 8:20"/>u-Eliyenayi, uZilethayi, u-Eliyeli, <verse eid="1CH 8:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 8:21"/>u-Adaya, uBheraya kanye loShimirathi kungamadodana kaShimeyi.<verse eid="1CH 8:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 8:22"/>U-Ishiphani, u-Ebheri, u-Eliyeli, <verse eid="1CH 8:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 8:23"/>u-Abhidoni, uZikhiri uHanani, <verse eid="1CH 8:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 8:24"/>uHananiya, u-Elamu, u-Anithothija, <verse eid="1CH 8:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 8:25"/>u-Ifideya loPhenuweli bengamadodana kaShashaki.<verse eid="1CH 8:25"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 8:26"/>UShamisherayi, uShehariya, u-Athaliya, <verse eid="1CH 8:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 8:27"/>uJareshiya, u-Elija, kanye loZikhiri kungamadodana kaJerohamu.<verse eid="1CH 8:27"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 8:28"/>Bonke laba babezinhloko zezindlu, izinduna kusiya ngoluhlu losendo lwabo, njalo babehlala eJerusalema.<verse eid="1CH 8:28"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 8:29"/>UJeyiyeli uyise kaGibhiyoni wayehlala eGibhiyoni.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 8:29">Ibizo lomkakhe lalinguMahakha, <verse eid="1CH 8:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 8:30"/>njalo indodana yakhe elizibulo kwakungu-Abhidoni, eselanywa nguZuri, loKhishi, loBhali, loNeri, loNadabi, <verse eid="1CH 8:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 8:31"/>loGedori, lo-Ahiyo, loZekheri <verse eid="1CH 8:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 8:32"/>kanye loMikhilothi, owayenguyise kaShimeya. Laba labo babehlala eJerusalema eduze lezihlobo zabo.<verse eid="1CH 8:32"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="1CH 8:33"/>UNeri wayenguyise kaKhishi, uKhishi enguyise kaSawuli, uSawuli enguyise kaJonathani, loMalikhi-Shuwa, lo-Abhinadabi kanye lo-Eshi-Bhali.<verse eid="1CH 8:33"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="1CH 8:34"/>Indodana kaJonathani:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 8:34">kwakunguMeri-Bhali yena enguyise kaMikha.<verse eid="1CH 8:34"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="1CH 8:35"/>Amadodana kaMikha ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 8:35">uPhithoni, uMeleki, uThareya kanye lo-Ahazi.<verse eid="1CH 8:35"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="1CH 8:36"/>U-Ahazi wayenguyise kaJehoyada, uJehoyada enguyise ka-Alemethi, lo-Azimavethi loZimri, njalo uZimri enguyise kaMoza. <verse eid="1CH 8:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="1CH 8:37"/>UMoza wayenguyise kaBhineya, loRafa eyindodana yakhe, lo-Eleyasa indodana yakhe kanye lo-Azeli indodana yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 8:37"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="1CH 8:38"/>U-Azeli wayelamadodana ayisithupha, amabizo awo eyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 8:38">u-Azirikhamu, loBhokheru, lo-Ishumayeli, loSheyariya, lo-Obhadaya kanye loHanani. Wonke la ayengamadodana ka-Azeli.<verse eid="1CH 8:38"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="1CH 8:39"/>Amadodana omfowabo u-Eshekhi ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 8:39">u-Ulamu izibulo lakhe, uJewushi indodana yesibili kanye lo-Elifelethi eyesithathu. <verse eid="1CH 8:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="1CH 8:40"/>Amadodana ka-Ulamu ayengamaqhawe alezibindi ayezintshantshu zemitshoko. Babelamadodana amanengi lamadodana amadodana abo, babelikhulu elilamatshumi amahlanu sebendawonye (150).</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 8:40">Bonke laba babeyinzalo kaBhenjamini.<verse eid="1CH 8:40"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <chapter eid="1CH 8"/>
  <chapter number="9" style="c" sid="1CH 9"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 9:1"/>Bonke abako-Israyeli babelotshiwe eluhlwini logwalo lokuzalana kwabo lwamakhosi ako-Israyeli. AbakoJuda bathunjwa basiwa eBhabhiloni ngenxa yokungathembeki kwabo.<verse eid="1CH 9:1"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abantu EJerusalema</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 9:2"/>Abokuqala ukwakha kutsha elizweni labo bahlala emizini yabo babengabantu bako-Israyeli, abaphristi, abaLevi lezinceku zethempelini.<verse eid="1CH 9:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 9:3"/>AbakoJuda, abakoBhenjamini kanye labako-Efrayimi loManase ababehlala eJerusalema yilaba:<verse eid="1CH 9:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 9:4"/>Ngu-Uthayi indodana ka-Amihudi, indodana ka-Omri, indodana ka-Imri, indodana kaBhani, owosendo lukaPherezi indodana kaJuda.<verse eid="1CH 9:4"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 9:5"/>KwabakoShilo</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 9:5">ngu-Asaya izibulo lamadodana akhe.<verse eid="1CH 9:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 9:6"/>KwabakoZera:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 9:6">nguJuweli.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 9:6">Abantu bakoJuda babengamakhulu ayisithupha alamatshumi ayisificamunwemunye (690).<verse eid="1CH 9:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 9:7"/>KwabakoBhenjamini:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 9:7">nguSalu indodana kaMeshulami, indodana kaHodaviya, indodana kaHasenuwa;<verse eid="1CH 9:7"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 9:8"/>lo-Ibhineya indodana kaJerohamu;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 9:8">lo-Ela indodana ka-Uzi, indodana kaMikhiri;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 9:8">loMeshulami indodana kaShefathiya, indodana kaRuweli, indodana ka-Ibhinija.<verse eid="1CH 9:8"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 9:9"/>Abantu bakoBhenjamini, ngoluhlu lokuzalana kwabo njengokulotshiweyo, babengamakhulu ayisificamunwemunye lamatshumi amahlanu lesithupha (956). Bonke laba kwakungamadoda ayizinhloko zezindlu zawo.<verse eid="1CH 9:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 9:10"/>Abaphristi yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 9:10">nguJedaya; loJehoyaribhi; kanye loJakhini;<verse eid="1CH 9:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 9:11"/>lo-Azariya indodana kaHilikhiya, indodana kaMeshulami, indodana kaZadokhi, indodana kaMerayothi, indodana ka-Ahithubi, isikhulu esasiphethe indlu kaNkulunkulu;<verse eid="1CH 9:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 9:12"/>lo-Adaya indodana kaJerohamu, indodana kaPhashuri, indodana kaMalikhija;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 9:12">loMasayi indodana ka-Adiyeli, indodana kaJahizera, indodana kaMeshulami, indodana kaMeshilemithi, indodana ka-Imeri.<verse eid="1CH 9:12"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 9:13"/>Abaphristi ababezinhloko zezindlu zabo babeyinkulungwane eyodwa elamakhulu ayisikhombisa lamatshumi ayisithupha (1,760). Babengamadoda alolwazi, belomlandu wokuphatha umsebenzi endlini kaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="1CH 9:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 9:14"/>AbaLevi yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 9:14">nguShemaya indodana kaHashubhi, indodana ka-Azirikhamu, indodana kaHashabhiya, ongumÊ¼Merari;<verse eid="1CH 9:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 9:15"/>loBhakhibhakhari, loHereshi, loGalali kanye loMathaniya indodana kaMikha, indodana kaZikhiri, indodana ka-Asafi;<verse eid="1CH 9:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 9:16"/>lo-Obhadaya indodana kaShemaya, indodana kaGalali, indodana kaJeduthuni,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 9:16">kanye loBherekhiya indodana ka-Asa, indodana ka-Elikhana, owayehlala emizini yamaNethofa.<verse eid="1CH 9:16"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 9:17"/>Abalindi bamasango yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 9:17">nguShalumi, lo-Akhubi, loThalimoni, lo-Ahimani labafowabo loShalumi induna yabo, <verse eid="1CH 9:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 9:18"/>eyayilinda iSango leNkosi empumalanga, kuze kube lamuhla. Abalindi bamasango bakoLevi yilaba:<verse eid="1CH 9:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 9:19"/>nguShalumi indodana kaKhore, indodana ka-Ebhiyasafi, indodana kaKhora, lababelinda amasango ndawonye bengabendlunye (amaKhora) beyibo ababefanele bananzelele iminyango yeThempeli njengoba oyise babevele belinda iminyango yendlu <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>.<verse eid="1CH 9:19"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 9:20"/>Ekadeni owayephethe abalindi bamasango kwakunguFinehasi indodana ka-Eliyazari njalo <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayelaye.<verse eid="1CH 9:20"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 9:21"/>UZakhariya indodana kaMeshelemiya wayengumlindisango lokungena eThenteni lokuHlanganela.<verse eid="1CH 9:21"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 9:22"/>Sebebonke labo ababekhethiwe ukuba ngabalindimasango ezindaweni eziqakathekileyo babengamakhulu amabili aletshumi lambili (212). Babelotshwe ngoluhlu lokuzalana kwabo emizini yabo.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 9:22"/>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 9:22">Abalindi bamasango babefakwe kulezizindawo zokwethembeka nguDavida loSamuyeli umboni. <verse eid="1CH 9:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 9:23"/>Bona kanye lenzalo yabo babephethe ukugcinakala kwamasango endlu <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> indlu ethiwa iThente. <verse eid="1CH 9:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 9:24"/>Abalindimasango laba babesenhlangothini zozine: empumalanga, entshonalanga, enyakatho laseningizimu. <verse eid="1CH 9:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 9:25"/>Abafowabo ababehlezi labo emizini yabo babefanele babebelinda labo bezophisana okwensuku eziyisikhombisa ihlandla ngalinye. <verse eid="1CH 9:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 9:26"/>Abalindimasango abakhulu, abangabaLevi, ngobune babo babefanele bagcine izindlu lenotho esendlini kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="1CH 9:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 9:27"/>Babelala belindile ubusuku bonke besendlini kaNkulunkulu, ngoba babefanele bayilinde; njalo yibo ababelezihluthulelo beyivula ngokusa insuku zonke.<verse eid="1CH 9:27"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 9:28"/>Abanye babo babegcina izitsha zenkonzo ezazisetshenziswa ethempelini; babezibala zingena babuye bazibale njalo seziphuma. <verse eid="1CH 9:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 9:29"/>Abanye njalo babegcine impahla yendlini lakho konke okwakusendlini engcwele, kanye lokugcina ifulawa lewayini, lamafutha, impepha leziyoliso. <verse eid="1CH 9:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 9:30"/>Kodwa abanye abaphristi babesebenza ukuhlanganisa iziyoliso. <verse eid="1CH 9:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 9:31"/>UmLevi obizwa ngokuthi nguMathithiya, indodana elizibulo likaShalumi umKhora, wayephiwe umlandu wokubumba isinkwa somnikelo. <verse eid="1CH 9:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 9:32"/>Abanye abazalwane bamaKhohathi babephethe umsebenzi ngamaSabatha wonke owokubumba isinkwa esokubekwa etafuleni.<verse eid="1CH 9:32"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="1CH 9:33"/>Labo ababengabahlabeleli, bezinhloko zezindlu zabaLevi, babehlala ezindlini phakathi kwethempeli bengaphiwanga eminye imisebenzi ngoba babephathekile kowabo emini lebusuku.<verse eid="1CH 9:33"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="1CH 9:34"/>Bonke laba babezinhloko zezindlu zenzalo kaLevi, izinduna njengokulotshiweyo eluhlwini losendo lwabo, njalo babehlala eJerusalema.<verse eid="1CH 9:34"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Okulotshiweyo NgoLuhlu Lwendlu KaSawuli</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="1CH 9:35"/>uJeyiyeli uyise kaGibhiyoni wayehlala eGibhiyoni.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 9:35">Ibizo lomkakhe lalinguMahakha, <verse eid="1CH 9:35"/><verse number="36" style="v" sid="1CH 9:36"/>njalo indodana yakhe elizibulo kwakungu-Abhidoni eselanywa nguZuri, loKhishi, loBhali, loNeri, loNadabi, <verse eid="1CH 9:36"/><verse number="37" style="v" sid="1CH 9:37"/>loGedori, lo-Ahiyo, loZakhariya kanye loMikhilothi. <verse eid="1CH 9:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="1CH 9:38"/>UMikhilothi wayenguyise kaShimeyamu. Laba labo babehlala eJerusalema eduze lezihlobo zabo.<verse eid="1CH 9:38"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="1CH 9:39"/>UNeri wayenguyise kaKhishi, uKhishi enguyise kaSawuli, uSawuli enguyise kaJonathani, loMalikhi-Shuwa, lo-Abhinadabi kanye lo-Eshi-Bhali.<verse eid="1CH 9:39"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="1CH 9:40"/>Indodana kaJonathani kwakunguMeri-Bhali,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 9:40">yena enguyise kaMikha.<verse eid="1CH 9:40"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="1CH 9:41"/>Amadodana kaMikha ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 9:41">uPhithoni, uMeleki, uThareya kanye lo-Ahazi.<verse eid="1CH 9:41"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="1CH 9:42"/>U-Ahazi wayenguyise kaJada, uJada enguyise ka-Alemethi, lo-Azimavethi loZimri, yena uZimri enguyise kaMoza. <verse eid="1CH 9:42"/><verse number="43" style="v" sid="1CH 9:43"/>UMoza wayenguyise kaBhineya; uRefaya eyindodana yakhe, lo-Eleyasa indodana yakhe kanye lo-Azeli indodana yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 9:43"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="1CH 9:44"/>U-Azeli wayelamadodana ayisithupha, amabizo awo eyila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 9:44">u-Azirikhamu, loBhokheru, lo-Ishumayeli. LoSheyariya, lo-Obhadaya kanye loHanani. Laba babengamadodana ka-Azeli.<verse eid="1CH 9:44"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 9"/>
  <chapter number="10" style="c" sid="1CH 10"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuzibulala KukaSawuli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 10:1"/>AmaFilistiya alwa lo-Israyeli; abako-Israyeli babaleka, njalo abanengi bafela eNtabeni yase Gilibhowa. <verse eid="1CH 10:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 10:2"/>AmaFilistiya axotshana kanzima loSawuli kanye lamadodana akhe, abulala amadodana akhe uJonathani, lo-Abhinadabi kanye loMalikhi-Shuwa. <verse eid="1CH 10:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 10:3"/>Impi yatshisa macele wonke kuSawuli, njalo kwathi abatshoki bemitshoko sebemxhumile, bamlimaza.<verse eid="1CH 10:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 10:4"/>USawuli wathi kumthwali wezikhali zakhe, âHwatsha inkemba yakho ungigwaze, hlezi abantu laba abangasokanga bafike bangigwaze bangenze ihlazo.â</para>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 10:4">Kodwa umphathi wezikhali zakhe wesaba, akaze akwenza lokho, ngakho uSawuli wathatha inkemba yakhe waziwisela phezu kwayo. <verse eid="1CH 10:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 10:5"/>Kwathi umphathi wezikhali ebona ukuthi uSawuli wayesefile, laye waziwisela phezu kwenkemba yakhe, wafa. <verse eid="1CH 10:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 10:6"/>Ngakho uSawuli lamadodana akhe amathathu bafa, labo bonke abendlu yakhe bafa ndawonye.<verse eid="1CH 10:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 10:7"/>Kwathi bonke abako-Israyeli ababesesigodini bebona ukuthi ibutho lalibalekile lokuthi uSawuli kanye lamadodana akhe basebefile, batshiya imizi yabo babaleka. AmaFilistiya afika ahlala kuyo.<verse eid="1CH 10:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 10:8"/>Ngelanga elalandelayo, amaFilistiya esefikile ukuba akhuthuze abafileyo, afica uSawuli lamadodana akhe befile eNtabeni yase Gilibhowa. <verse eid="1CH 10:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 10:9"/>Bamkhuthuza baze bamquma ikhanda lakhe balithatha kanye lezikhali zakhe, basebethuma izithunywa kulolonke ilizwe lamaFilistiya ukuthi zimemezele lindaba ezithombeni zabo lebantwini bakibo. <verse eid="1CH 10:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 10:10"/>Abeka izikhali zakhe ethempelini labonkulunkulu babo kwathi ikhanda lakhe balibeka ethempelini likaDagoni.<verse eid="1CH 10:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 10:11"/>Abantu bonke baseJabheshi Giliyadi sebezwile ngokwakwenziwe ngamaFilistiya kuSawuli, <verse eid="1CH 10:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 10:12"/>wonke amaqhawe alezibindi ahamba ayathatha isidumbu sikaSawuli lezamadodana akhe aya lazo eJabheshi. Basebengcwaba amathambo abo ngaphansi kwesihlahla esikhulu eJabheshi, bazila insuku eziyisikhombisa.<verse eid="1CH 10:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 10:13"/>USawuli wafa ngoba wayengathembekanga <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>; kaligcinanga ilizwi <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> wakhe waze wayadinga ukuqondiswa yizangoma, <verse eid="1CH 10:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 10:14"/>esikhundleni sokukhuleka <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>. Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wamenza wafa wathatha ubukhosi wabunika uDavida indodana kaJese.<verse eid="1CH 10:14"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 10"/>
  <chapter number="11" style="c" sid="1CH 11"/>
  <para style="s1">UDavida Uba Yinkosi Yako-Israyeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 11:1"/>Bonke abako-Israyeli baya kuDavida eHebhroni bafika bathi: âThina siyinyama yakho legazi lakho. <verse eid="1CH 11:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 11:2"/>Esikhathini esedlulayo, lanxa uSawuli eseseyinkosi, wena nguwe owawukhokhela u-Israyeli emkhankasweni wezimpi. Njalo <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakho wathi kuwe, âWena uzakuba ngumelusi wabantu bami u-Israyeli, njalo uzakuba ngumbusi wabo.âââ<verse eid="1CH 11:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 11:3"/>Kwathi abadala bonke bako-Israyeli sebefikile enkosini uDavida eHebhroni, wenza isivumelwano labo eHebhroni phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>, basebegcoba uDavida ukuba abe yinkosi ko-Israyeli, njengesithembiso <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> asenza ngoSamuyeli.<verse eid="1CH 11:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UDavida Unqoba IJerusalema</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 11:4"/>UDavida labo bonke abako-Israyeli baya eJerusalema (kusitsho iJebusi). AmaJebusi ayehlala khona <verse eid="1CH 11:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 11:5"/>athi kuDavida, âKawuyikungena lapha.â Kodwa lanxa kunjalo, uDavida wayithumba inqaba yaseZiyoni, uMuzi kaDavida.<verse eid="1CH 11:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 11:6"/>UDavida wayethe, âOzakhokhela ekuhlaseleni amaJebusi uzakuba nguMlawuli omkhulu wempi.â UJowabi indodana kaZeruya nguye owaqala ukuya khona, ngakho wazuza ubukhokheli.<verse eid="1CH 11:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 11:7"/>UDavida wasehlala enqabeni, yikho yathiwa ibizo lokuthi nguMuzi kaDavida. <verse eid="1CH 11:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 11:8"/>Wakha idolobho inxa zonke kusukela emadundulwini kuze kuyefinyelela emidulini ehonqolozeleyo, ngalesosikhathi uJowabi esakha evuselela umuzi. <verse eid="1CH 11:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 11:9"/>UDavida waqhubeka njalo esiba lamandla, ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uSomandla wayelaye.<verse eid="1CH 11:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amaqhawe KaDavida</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 11:10"/>Lezi zinduna zamaqhawe kaDavida ezazimsekele ngokuqinileyo embusweni kanye laye wonke u-Israyeli, ukuba abe yinkosi, njengokuthembisa <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>. <verse eid="1CH 11:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 11:11"/>Lolu yiluhlu lwalawo maqhawe kaDavida:</para>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 11:11">UJashobheyamu, umHakhimoni, wayengumlawuli wezikhulu; waphakamisela amadoda angamakhulu amathathu umkhonto wakhe, ababulalayo ekuhlaseleni kunye.<verse eid="1CH 11:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 11:12"/>Yena elandelwa ngu-Eliyazari indodana kaDodo umÊ¼Ahohi omunye wamaqhawe amathathu. <verse eid="1CH 11:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 11:13"/>WayeloDavida ePhasi Damimi, ekuhlomeni kwamaFilistiya elungiselela ukudibana empini. Endaweni ethile kwakulensimu yebhali, amabutho abaleka ebalekela amaFilistiya. <verse eid="1CH 11:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 11:14"/>Kodwa bona bema bajama phakathi kwensimu. Bayivikela bawabulala amaFilistiya, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wabapha ukunqoba okukhulu.<verse eid="1CH 11:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 11:15"/>Izinduna ezintathu kwezingamatshumi amathathu zaya edwaleni kuDavida ebhalwini lwase-Adulami, ngalesosikhathi amanye amaFilistiya ayebuthene eSigodini saseRefayi. <verse eid="1CH 11:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 11:16"/>Ngalesosikhathi uDavida wayesenqabeni, iviyo lamabutho amaFilistiya laliseBhethilehema. <verse eid="1CH 11:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 11:17"/>UDavida womela amanzi wasesithi, âOh, sengathi kungaba lomuntu ongangikhela amanzi okunatha emthonjeni oseduze lesango laseBhethilehema!â <verse eid="1CH 11:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 11:18"/>Ngakho abathathu laba badabula phakathi kweviyo lamaFilistiya bayakukha amanzi eduzane lesango laseBhethilehema bayawanika uDavida. Kodwa wala ukuwanatha, wakhetha ukuwathululela phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>. <verse eid="1CH 11:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 11:19"/>Wasesithi, âUNkulunkulu kangangivumeli ukukwenza lokhu! Kufanele yini ukuthi nginathe igazi lalababantu abanikele impilo yabo engozini bewaletha?â Ngoba babeka impilo zabo engozini bewaletha, uDavida kawanathanga.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 11:19">Lezi zaziyizenzo zobuqhawe zalawomabutho womathathu.<verse eid="1CH 11:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 11:20"/>U-Abhishayi umfowabo kaJowabi wayeyinduna yabaThathu labo. Waphakamisela umkhonto wakhe phezu kwabangamakhulu amathathu, ababulalayo, ngakho waba lodumo njengabaThathu. <verse eid="1CH 11:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 11:21"/>Waba lodumo oluphindwe kabili phezu kwalaba abaThathu waze waba ngumlawuli wabo, loba engazange abe phakathi kwabo.<verse eid="1CH 11:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 11:22"/>UBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada wayeliqhawe elilesibindi laseKhabhizeli, elenza izenzo zobuqhawe obukhulu. Wabulala amaqhawe amaMowabi amabili ayezintshantshu ekulweni. Wake wangena emgodini wabulala isilwane mhla kulongqwaqwane. <verse eid="1CH 11:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 11:23"/>Wabulala umGibhithe owayemude okwezingalo eyisikhombisa njalo eqatha. Lanxa umGibhithe wayephethe umkhonto esandleni kwakungani uphethe umkhonto onjengogodo lomaluki, uBhenayiya waqondana laye ngenduku. Wahluthuna umkhonto esandleni somGibhithe wambulala ngawo umkhonto wakhe. <verse eid="1CH 11:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 11:24"/>Lezi zaziyizenzo zobuqhawe zikaBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada, laye futhi wayedume njengamaqhawe amathathu. <verse eid="1CH 11:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 11:25"/>Wayehlonitshwa kakhulu ukwedlula bonke abangamatshumi amathathu, kodwa wayengabalwa kanye labaThathu. UDavida wambeka ukuba abe ngumphathi wabalindi bakhe.<verse eid="1CH 11:25"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 11:26"/>Amaqhawe ayelamandla ayeyila:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 11:26"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:26">u-Asaheli umfowabo kaJowabi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:26">u-Elihanani indodana kaDodo waseBhethilehema,<verse eid="1CH 11:26"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 11:27"/>uShamothi umHarori,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:27">uHelezi umPheloni,<verse eid="1CH 11:27"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 11:28"/>u-Ira indodana ka-Ikheshi waseThekhowa,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:28">u-Abhiyezeri wase-Anathothi,<verse eid="1CH 11:28"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 11:29"/>uSibhekhayi umHushathi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:29">u-Ilayi umÊ¼Ahohi,<verse eid="1CH 11:29"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 11:30"/>uMaharayi umNethofathi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:30">uHeledi indodana kaBhana umNethofa,<verse eid="1CH 11:30"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 11:31"/>u-Ithayi indodana kaRibhayi owaseGibhiya koBhenjamini,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:31">uBhenaya umPhirathoni,<verse eid="1CH 11:31"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 11:32"/>uHurayi wasezindongeni zaseGashi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:32">u-Abhiyeli umÊ¼Aribhathi,<verse eid="1CH 11:32"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="1CH 11:33"/>u-Azimavethi umBhaharumi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:33">u-Eliyaba umShalibhoni,<verse eid="1CH 11:33"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="1CH 11:34"/>amadodana kaHashemi umGizoni,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:34">uJonathani indodana kaShageye umHarari,<verse eid="1CH 11:34"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="1CH 11:35"/>u-Ahiyamu indodana kaSakhari umHarari,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:35">u-Elifali indodana ka-Uri,<verse eid="1CH 11:35"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="1CH 11:36"/>uHeferi indodana kaMekherathi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:36">u-Ahija umPheloni,<verse eid="1CH 11:36"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="1CH 11:37"/>uHeziro umKhameli,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:37">uNarayi indodana ka-Ezibhayi,<verse eid="1CH 11:37"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="1CH 11:38"/>uJoweli umfowabo kaNathani,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:38">uMibhari indodana kaHagiri,<verse eid="1CH 11:38"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="1CH 11:39"/>uZelekhi umÊ¼Amoni,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:39">uNaharayi umBherothi, owayethwala izikhali zikaJowabi indodana kaZeruya,<verse eid="1CH 11:39"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="40" style="v" sid="1CH 11:40"/>u-Ira umÊ¼Ithira,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:40">uGarebhi umÊ¼Ithiri,<verse eid="1CH 11:40"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="41" style="v" sid="1CH 11:41"/>u-Uriya umHithi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:41">uZabhadi indodana ka-Ahilayi,<verse eid="1CH 11:41"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="42" style="v" sid="1CH 11:42"/>lo-Adina indodana kaShiza owakoRubheni, owayeyinduna yakoRubheni, kanye labangamatshumi amathathu ababelaye,<verse eid="1CH 11:42"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="1CH 11:43"/>loHanani indodana kaMahakha,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:43">loJoshafathi umÊ¼Mithini,<verse eid="1CH 11:43"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="44" style="v" sid="1CH 11:44"/>lo-Uziya umÊ¼Ashitherathi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:44">loShama loJeyiyeli amadodana kaHothamu umÊ¼Aroweri,<verse eid="1CH 11:44"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="45" style="v" sid="1CH 11:45"/>loJediyeli indodana kaShimiri,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:45">umfowabo uJoha umThizi,<verse eid="1CH 11:45"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="46" style="v" sid="1CH 11:46"/>lo-Eliyeli umÊ¼Mahavi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:46">loJeribhayi loJoshaviya amadodana ka-Elinamu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 11:46">lo-Ithima waseMowabi,<verse eid="1CH 11:46"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="47" style="v" sid="1CH 11:47"/>lo-Eliyeli, lo-Obhedi kanye loJasiyeli waseMezobha.<verse eid="1CH 11:47"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 11"/>
  <chapter number="12" style="c" sid="1CH 12"/>
  <para style="s1">Amabutho Alandela UDavida Egangeni</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 12:1"/>La ngamabutho ayeloDavida eZikhilagi, ngesikhathi engavunyelwa ukubonakala kuSawuli indodana kaKhishi (kwakungamaqhawe ayemhlomulele empini; <verse eid="1CH 12:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 12:2"/>ayehlome ngemitshoko, ezingcitshi ekutshokeni lokutshaya ngezavutha loba ejikijela ngesokudla loba ngesenxele; ayeyizihlobo zikaSawuli engawesizwe sikaBhenjamini):<verse eid="1CH 12:2"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 12:3"/>U-Ahiyezeri induna yawo loJowashi amadodana kaShemaha owaseGibhiya;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 12:3">loJeziyeli loPhelethi amadodana ka-Azimavethi;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 12:3">loBherakha, loJehu umÊ¼Anathothi, <verse eid="1CH 12:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 12:4"/>kanye lo-Ishimaya umGibhiyoni, indoda eyayilamandla amakhulu kwabangamatshumi amathathu, engumkhokheli wabangamatshumi amathathu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 12:4">loJeremiya, loJahaziyeli, loJohanani, loJozabhadi umGederathi, <verse eid="1CH 12:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 12:5"/>lo-Eluzayi, loJerimothi, loBheliya, loShemariya kanye loShefathiya umHarufi,<verse eid="1CH 12:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 12:6"/>lo-Elikhana, lo-Ishiya, lo-Azareli, loJowezeri loJashobheyamu amaKhora;<verse eid="1CH 12:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 12:7"/>kanye loJowela loZebhadiya amadodana kaJerohamu waseGedori.<verse eid="1CH 12:7"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 12:8"/>Abanye abakoGadi babalekela kuDavida enqabeni yakhe enkangala. Babengamabutho alezibindi, belungele ukulwa njalo bekwazi ukuphatha ihawu lomkhonto. Ubuso babo babungobezilwane, njalo belesiqubu njengamagogo ezintabeni.<verse eid="1CH 12:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 12:9"/>U-Ezeri wayeyinduna,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 12:9">u-Obhadaya engumsekeli womlawuli, u-Eliyabi engowesithathu,<verse eid="1CH 12:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 12:10"/>uMishimana engowesine, uJeremiya engowesihlanu,<verse eid="1CH 12:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 12:11"/>u-Athayi engowesithupha, u-Eliyeli engowesikhombisa,<verse eid="1CH 12:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 12:12"/>uJohanani engowesificaminwembili, u-Elizabhadi engowesificamunwemunye,<verse eid="1CH 12:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 12:13"/>uJeremiya engumsekeli wetshumi kanye loMakhabhanayi owayengowetshumi lanye.<verse eid="1CH 12:13"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 12:14"/>Amadoda akoGadi ayengabalawuli bamabutho, kuthi omncinyane wabo wayengamelana labalikhulu kodwa omkhulu wabo engamelana labayinkulungwane. <verse eid="1CH 12:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 12:15"/>Yiwo la amadoda achapha uJodani ngenyanga yakuqala umfula ugcwele uphuphuma emakhunjini awo wonke, yibo njalo abaxotsha bonke ababehlala ezihotsheni, empumalanga kanye lasentshonalanga.<verse eid="1CH 12:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 12:16"/>Amanye amadoda akoBhenjamini lamanye ayevela koJuda lawo alandela uDavida khonale enqabeni yakhe. <verse eid="1CH 12:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 12:17"/>UDavida waphuma ukuba ayewahlangabeza wathi kuwo: âNxa lingilandela ngokuthula, lizongiphathisa njengabangane, ngizimisele ukuhlanganyela kanye lani. Kodwa nxa lidinga ukunginikela ezitheni zami, mina ngimsulwa, uNkulunkulu wabokhokho kakubone lokho, alijezise.â<verse eid="1CH 12:17"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 12:18"/>Ngakho uMoya wasesehlela ku-Amasayi, umlawuli wabangamatshumi amaThathu, wathi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="1CH 12:18">âSingabakho thina, wena Davida!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 12:18">Sikanye lawe wena ndodana kaJese!</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="1CH 12:18">Impumelelo, impumelelo kuwe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 12:18">njalo impumelelo kulabo abaphathisana lawe!</para>
  <para style="q3" vid="1CH 12:18">Ngoba uNkulunkulu wakho uzakusiza.â</para>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 12:18">Ngakho uDavida wabamukela wabenza abakhokheli bamaviyo amabutho ayehlasela.<verse eid="1CH 12:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 12:19"/>Amanye amadoda akoManase abalekela kuDavida ekuhambeni kwakhe lamaFilistiya esiyahlasela uSawuli. (Yena kanye lamabutho akhe kasazange ancedise amaFilistiya, ngoba ngemva kokubuzisisana, ababusi bawo bathi kaxotshwe. Bathi bona: âUyingozi kithi, ngoba angasiphendukela abuyele enkosini yakhe uSawuli.â) <verse eid="1CH 12:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 12:20"/>UDavida wathi esiya eZikhilagi, nanka amadoda abaleka koManase amlandela: ngu-Adina, loJozabhadi, loJediyeli, loMikhayeli, loJozabhadi, lo-Elihu kanye loZilethayi ababengabalawuli benkulungwane koManase. <verse eid="1CH 12:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 12:21"/>Bancedisa uDavida ekulweni lamaviyo abahlaseli, ngoba bonke babengamabutho alezibindi, njalo basebengabalawuli phakathi kwamabutho akhe. <verse eid="1CH 12:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 12:22"/>Insuku zonke, ukusa kwamalanga, kwakutheleka abantu bezoncedisa uDavida, waze waba lebutho elikhulu, njengebutho likaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="1CH 12:22"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abanye Balandela UDavida EHebhroni</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 12:23"/>Nanka amanani amadoda ayehlomele impi eza kuDavida eHebhroni ezomncedisa ukuthatha umbuso kaSawuli, njengokutsho <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>:<verse eid="1CH 12:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 12:24"/>amadoda ayevela koJuda ehlome ngamahawu lemikhonto ayezinkulungwane eziyisithupha lamakhulu ayisificaminwembili (6,800) ehlomele ukulwa impi;<verse eid="1CH 12:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 12:25"/>abakaSimiyoni, amabutho ayelungele ukuhlasela babezinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa lekhulu (7,100),<verse eid="1CH 12:25"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 12:26"/>amadoda akoLevi ayezinkulungwane ezine lamakhulu ayisithupha (4,600), <verse eid="1CH 12:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 12:27"/>kubalwa loJehoyada, umkhokheli wabendlu ka-Aroni babezinkulungwane ezintathu lamakhulu ayisikhombisa (3,700) zamadoda <verse eid="1CH 12:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 12:28"/>kanye loZadokhi, ibutho elaliseselijaha lilesibindi, lilezikhulu zendlu yakwabo ezingamatshumi amabili lambili (22);<verse eid="1CH 12:28"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 12:29"/>amadoda akoBhenjamini, labakibo kaSawuli babezinkulungwane ezintathu (3,000), ababesele bethembekile kuSawuli kuze kufike lesisikhathi yibo ababebanengi kulelonani;<verse eid="1CH 12:29"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 12:30"/>amadoda ako-Efrayimi, amadoda ayelezibindi, edumile ezizwaneni zawo, ayezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lamakhulu ayisificaminwembili (20,800),<verse eid="1CH 12:30"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 12:31"/>amadoda ayevela kungxenye yesizwana sikaManase, ekhethwe ngamabizo awo ukuba azobeka uDavida ukuthi abe yinkosi, ayezinkulungwane ezilitshumi lesificaminwembili (18,000);<verse eid="1CH 12:31"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 12:32"/>amadoda ayevela ko-Isakhari, ayezwisisa umumo walesosikhathi njalo esazi ukuthi u-Israyeli kumele enzeni. Kwakuzinduna ezingamakhulu amabili (200) kanye lezihlobo zazo ezazingaphansi kwazo;<verse eid="1CH 12:32"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="1CH 12:33"/>amadoda ayevela koZebhuluni, amabutho ayezingwazi empini, ngezikhali zemihlobo etshiyeneyo, eza ukuzancedisa uDavida ngokuzinikela okungalakuthandabuza, ayezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amahlanu (50,000);<verse eid="1CH 12:33"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="1CH 12:34"/>amadoda ayevela koNafithali kwakuyizikhulu eziyinkulungwane eyodwa (1,000), kanye lamadoda ayephethe amahawu lemikhonto ayezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu lesikhombisa (37,000);<verse eid="1CH 12:34"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="1CH 12:35"/>amadoda ayevela koDani, ezimisele ukulwa empini, ayezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lesificaminwembili lamakhulu ayisithupha (28,600);<verse eid="1CH 12:35"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="1CH 12:36"/>amadoda ayevela ko-Asheri, amabutho ayevele ekwejayele ukulwa empini njalo ezimisele ukulwa, ayezinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane (40,000);<verse eid="1CH 12:36"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="1CH 12:37"/>njalo ngempumalanga yeJodani, amadoda akoRubheni, koGadi lakungxenye yesizwana sikaManase, ayehlome ngemihlobohlobo yezikhali, ayezinkulungwane ezilikhulu lamatshumi amabili (120,000).<verse eid="1CH 12:37"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="38" style="v" sid="1CH 12:38"/>Bonke laba babengamabutho azinikeleyo ukungena laloba yisiphi isigaba.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 12:38"/>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 12:38">Ngamabutho aya eHebhroni ezimisele ukufika abeke uDavida esihlalweni sobukhosi abe yinkosi ka-Israyeli. Abanye bonke abako-Israyeli babengqondonye befisa ukwethesa uDavida ubukhosi. <verse eid="1CH 12:38"/><verse number="39" style="v" sid="1CH 12:39"/>Wonke lamadoda athatha insuku ezintathu eloDavida, esidla njalo enatha, njengoba izimuli zawo zaziwalungisele umphako. <verse eid="1CH 12:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="1CH 12:40"/>Konke labomakhelwane babo, ababevela kude khonale ku-Isakhari, loZebhuluni lakuNafithali beza bethwele ukudla ngabobabhemi, amakamela, imbongolo langenkabi. Kwakulefulawa enengi, amakhekhe omkhiwane, amakhekhe erezini, iwayini, amafutha, inkomo lezimvu, ngoba kwakulokujabula ko-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 12:40"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 12"/>
  <chapter number="13" style="c" sid="1CH 13"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukubuyiselwa Kwebhokisi Lesivumelwano</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 13:1"/>UDavida wacebisana lezikhulu zakhe zonke, abalawuli bezinkulungwane labalawuli bamakhulu. <verse eid="1CH 13:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 13:2"/>Wasesithi kuwo wonke umbuthano wako-Israyeli: âNxa likubona kulungile njalo nxa kuyintando <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu, asithumeleni ilizwi eduze lakhatshana kubo bonke abafowethu kuwo wonke amazwe ako-Israyeli, kanye lakubaphristi labaLevi abalabo khonale emadolobheni abo lasemadlelweni abo, sibanxusa ukuthi beze bazohlanganyela kanye lathi. <verse eid="1CH 13:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 13:3"/>Asibuyiseni ibhokisi lesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu wethu kithi, ngoba asizange sibuze kulo ngesikhathi sokubusa kukaSawuli.â <verse eid="1CH 13:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 13:4"/>Bonke ababebuthene bavumelana ukukwenza lokho, ngoba bonke abantu bakubona kufanele ukukwenza lokho.<verse eid="1CH 13:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 13:5"/>Ngakho uDavida wahlanganisa ama-Israyeli wonke, kusukela eMfuleni uShihori eGibhithe kusiya eLebho Hamathi, ukuyathatha ibhokisi lesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu eKhiriyathi-Jeyarimi. <verse eid="1CH 13:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 13:6"/>UDavida labo bonke abako-Israyeli ababelaye baya eBhala yakoJuda (iKhiriyathi-Jeyarimi) ukuthi baye khonale bayebuya lebhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu, osesihlalweni sobukhosi ephahlwe ngamaKherubhi, ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> elibizwa ngaleloBizo.<verse eid="1CH 13:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 13:7"/>Balisusa ibhokisi lesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu endlini ka-Abhinadabi ngenqola entsha, eyayiqondiswa ngu-Uza lo-Ahiyo. <verse eid="1CH 13:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 13:8"/>UDavida labo bonke abako-Israyeli babejabula bezithokozisa ngamandla abo wonke phambi kukaNkulunkulu, ngezingoma betshaya lamachacho, lezingungu, lezigubhu, lamacilongo.<verse eid="1CH 13:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 13:9"/>Bathi befika esizeni sokubhulela eKhidoni, u-Uza welula isandla sakhe ezama ukuzinzisa ibhokisi lesivumelwano sikaThixo, ngoba inkabi zazikhubekile. <verse eid="1CH 13:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 13:10"/>Ulaka <char style="nd">lukaThixo</char> lwavutha ku-Uza, wamtshaya wafa ngoba wayebeke isandla sakhe phezu kwebhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>. Ngakho wahle wafa khonapho phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>.<verse eid="1CH 13:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 13:11"/>Ngakho uDavida wathukuthela ngoba ulaka <char style="nd">lukaThixo</char> lwavutha ku-Uza, njalo kuze kube lalamuhla indawo leyo ibizwa ngokuthi yiPherezi Uza.<verse eid="1CH 13:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 13:12"/>UDavida wamesaba uNkulunkulu ngalolosuku waze wabuza wathi: âPho ngingaliletha njani kimi ibhokisi lesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu?â <verse eid="1CH 13:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 13:13"/>Kasazange alithathe ibhokisi lesivumelwano ukuze libe kuye eMzini kaDavida. Kodwa-ke walisa eceleni endlini ka-Obhedi-Edomi umGithi. <verse eid="1CH 13:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 13:14"/>Ibhokisi lesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu lahlala kwabendlu ka-Obhedi-Edomi endlini yakhe okwezinyanga ezintathu, yikho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wabusisa indlu yakhe lakho konke okwakungokwakhe.<verse eid="1CH 13:14"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 13"/>
  <chapter number="14" style="c" sid="1CH 14"/>
  <para style="s1">UDavida Labendlu Yakhe</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 14:1"/>Ngalesosikhathi uHiramu inkosi yaseThire wathumela izithunywa kuDavida, ndawonye lezigodo zomsedari, ababazi bamatshe kanye lababazi ukuthi bayemakhela isigodlo. <verse eid="1CH 14:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 14:2"/>UDavida wahle wakwazi ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> usembekile ukuba abe yinkosi ka-Israyeli lokuthi umbuso wakhe uphakanyisiwe kakhulu ngenxa yabantu bakhe bako-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 14:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 14:3"/>EJerusalema uDavida wathatha abanye abafazi wazala amanye amadodana lamadodakazi. <verse eid="1CH 14:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 14:4"/>Nanka amabizo abantwana abazalelwa khona: uShamuwa, uShobabi, uNathani, uSolomoni, <verse eid="1CH 14:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 14:5"/>u-Ibhari, u-Elishuwa, u-Eliphelethi, <verse eid="1CH 14:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 14:6"/>uNoga, uNefegi, uJafiya, <verse eid="1CH 14:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 14:7"/>u-Elishama, uBheyeliyada kanye lo-Elifelethi.<verse eid="1CH 14:7"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UDavida Unqoba AmaFilistiya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 14:8"/>AmaFilistiya athi esizwa ukuthi uDavida usegcotshwe ukuba yinkosi yalo lonke elako-Israyeli, aphuma wonke ehlome ephelele esiyamzingela, kodwa uDavida wakuzwa lokho wahle waphuma yena ukuyawahlangabeza. <verse eid="1CH 14:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 14:9"/>AmaFilistiya ayesefikile njalo ukuyahlasela eSigodini saseRefayi; <verse eid="1CH 14:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 14:10"/>ngakho uDavida wabuza kuNkulunkulu wathi: âNgihambe ngiyewahlasela amaFilistiya na? Uzawanikela kimi na?â</para>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 14:10">
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wamphendula wathi, âHamba, ngizawanikela kuwe.â<verse eid="1CH 14:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 14:11"/>Ngakho uDavida lamabutho akhe aya eBhali Pherazimi lapho awehlula khona. Wathi: âNjengamanzi efohla, uNkulunkulu ufohlele ezitheni zami ngesandla sami.â Ngakho leyondawo yasibizwa ngokuthi yiBhali Pherazimi. <verse eid="1CH 14:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 14:12"/>AmaFilistiya ayebaleke atshiya onkulunkulu bawo khonale, uDavida wathi kabatshiswe ngomlilo.<verse eid="1CH 14:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 14:13"/>AmaFilistiya aphinda njalo ukuhlasela isigodi, <verse eid="1CH 14:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 14:14"/>ngakho uDavida wabuza kuNkulunkulu njalo, uNkulunkulu wamphendula wathi, âUngasuki uqonde phambili kodwa bazingeleze ubusubahlasela uvelela ezihlahleni zebhalisamu. <verse eid="1CH 14:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 14:15"/>Kuzakuthi lapho usizwa izisinde zabahambayo ezihlahleni zebhalisamu, uphume uhlasele, ngoba lokho kuzabe kusitsho ukuthi uNkulunkulu usehambe phambi kwakho ukuyanqoba amabutho amaFilistiya.â <verse eid="1CH 14:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 14:16"/>Ngakho uDavida wenza njengokulaywa kwakhe nguNkulunkulu, njalo bawacakazela phansi amaFilistiya umango wonke kusukela eGibhiyoni kusiya eGezeri.<verse eid="1CH 14:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 14:17"/>Yikho udumo lukaDavida lwanda lwafinyelela kuwo wonke amazwe, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wenza izizwe zonke zimesabe.<verse eid="1CH 14:17"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 14"/>
  <chapter number="15" style="c" sid="1CH 15"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukulethwa Kwebhokisi Lesivumelwano EJerusalema</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 15:1"/>Ngemva kokuba uDavida esakhile ezakhe izindlu eMzini kaDavida, wakha indawo yebhokisi lesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu, walimisela ithente kuleyondawo. <verse eid="1CH 15:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 15:2"/>UDavida wasesithi: âKakho ozathwala ibhokisi lesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu ngaphandle kwabaLevi ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wabakhethela ukuthwala ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> lokumkhonza kuze kube nininini.â<verse eid="1CH 15:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 15:3"/>UDavida wasehlanganisa bonke abako-Israyeli eJerusalema ukuze balethe ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> endaweni ayeyilungisele lona.<verse eid="1CH 15:3"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 15:4"/>Wahlanganisa abosendo luka-Aroni labaLevi ngezindlu zabo:<verse eid="1CH 15:4"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 15:5"/>Kwabendlu kaKhohathi,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 15:5">kwakungu-Uriyeli umkhokheli lezihlobo ezilikhulu lamatshumi amabili (120);<verse eid="1CH 15:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 15:6"/>kwabendlu kaMerari,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 15:6">kwakungu-Asaya umkhokheli lezihlobo ezingamakhulu amabili lamatshumi amabili (220);<verse eid="1CH 15:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 15:7"/>kwabendlu kaGeshoni,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 15:7">kwakunguJoweli umkhokheli lezihlobo ezilikhulu labantu abangamatshumi amathathu (130);<verse eid="1CH 15:7"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 15:8"/>kwabendlu ka-Elizafani,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 15:8">kwakunguShemaya umkhokheli lezihlobo ezingamakhulu amabili (200);<verse eid="1CH 15:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 15:9"/>kwabendlu kaHebhroni,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 15:9">kwakungu-Eliyeli umkhokheli lezihlobo ezingamatshumi ayisificaminwembili (80);<verse eid="1CH 15:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 15:10"/>kwabendlu ka-Uziyeli,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 15:10">kwakungu-Aminadabi umkhokheli lezihlobo ezilikhulu labantu abalitshumi lambili (112).<verse eid="1CH 15:10"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 15:11"/>UDavida wasenxusa abaphristi uZadokhi lo-Abhiyathari kanye lo-Uriyeli, lo-Asaya, loJoweli, loShemaya, lo-Eliyeli lo-Abhinadabi abaLevi. <verse eid="1CH 15:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 15:12"/>Wasesithi kubo, âLina lizinhloko zezindlu zabaLevi, zihlambululeni lina kanye lezihlobo zenu ukuze liyethatha ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli, lililethe endaweni engiyilungisele lona. <verse eid="1CH 15:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 15:13"/><char style="nd">UThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu wasithukuthelela ngenxa yokuthi lina abaLevi, ayisini elathwala ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> kuqala. Asizanga sibuze <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> ukuthi kwakumele senzeni njengokulaya kwakhe.â <verse eid="1CH 15:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 15:14"/>Ngakho abaphristi labaLevi bazihlambulula ukuze bathwale ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli. <verse eid="1CH 15:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 15:15"/>Yikho abaLevi bathwala ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> ngezibambo zezigodo emahlombe abo, njengokulaya kukaMosi kulandelwa ilizwi <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>.<verse eid="1CH 15:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 15:16"/>UDavida watshela abakhokheli babaLevi ukuthi bakhethe abafowabo ukuthi babe ngabahlabeleli ukuze bahlabelele izingoma ezimnandi, betshaya amachacho lezigubhu lemihubhe.<verse eid="1CH 15:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 15:17"/>AbaLevi bakhetha uHemani indodana kaJoweli; kubafowabo, u-Asafi indodana kaBherekhiya; lakubafowabo amaMerari, u-Ethani indodana kaKhushaya; <verse eid="1CH 15:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 15:18"/>kanye labafowabo ngokulandelana ngezikhundla: uZakhariya, loJahaziyeli, loShemiramothi, loJeyiyeli, lo-Uni, lo-Eliyabi, loBhenaya, loMaseya, loMathithiya, lo-Elifelehu, loMikhineya, lo-Obhedi-Edomi kanye loJehiyeli abalindi bamasango.<verse eid="1CH 15:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 15:19"/>Abahlabeleli uHemani lo-Asafi kanye lo-Ethani babezatshaya izigubhu zethusi; <verse eid="1CH 15:19"/><verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 15:20"/>loZakhariya, lo-Aziyeli, loShemiramothi, loJehiyeli, lo-Uni, lo-Eliyabi, loMaseya kanye loBhenaya babezatshaya imihubhe, ngokuhambelana <char style="tl">le-alamothi</char> <verse eid="1CH 15:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 15:21"/>loMathithiya, lo-Elifelehu, loMikhineya, lo-Obhedi-Edomi, loJeyiyeli kanye lo-Azaziya babezatshaya imiqangala, njengokuqondiswa kwabo <char style="tl">yishiminithi,</char> <verse eid="1CH 15:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 15:22"/>uKhenaniya umkhokheli kubaLevi wayengumhlabelisi; wayephethe lapha ngoba wayeligabazi.<verse eid="1CH 15:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 15:23"/>UBherekhiya lo-Elikhana babengabalindi bamasango ebhokisi lesivumelwano, <verse eid="1CH 15:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 15:24"/>loShebhaniya, loJoshafathi loNethaneli, lo-Amasayi, loZakhariya, loBhenaya kanye lo-Eliyezari bengabaphristi bokuvuthela icilongo phambi kwebhokisi lesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu. U-Obhedi-Edomi loJehiya labo babengabalindi beminyango yebhokisi lesivumelwano.<verse eid="1CH 15:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 15:25"/>Ngakho uDavida labadala bako-Israyeli labalawuli bamaxuku enkulungwane bahamba ukuyathatha ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> endlini ka-Obhedi-Edomi, bahamba ngokujabula. <verse eid="1CH 15:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 15:26"/>Ngoba uNkulunkulu wayebasizile abakoLevi ababethwele ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>, benza umhlatshelo wenkunzi eziyisikhombisa lenqama eziyisikhombisa. <verse eid="1CH 15:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 15:27"/>UDavida labo bonke abaLevi ababethwele ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> labahlabeleli loKhenaniya umkhokheli wabahlabeleli babegqoke izigqoko zelembu lelineni elihle, uDavida wayegqoke lesigqoko semahlombe selineni elihle. <verse eid="1CH 15:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 15:28"/>Ngakho abako-Israyeli ngobunengi babo baletha ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> ngomdumo omkhulu, bevuthela impondo zenqama betshaya lamacilongo, lezigubhu lamachacho lemihubhe.<verse eid="1CH 15:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 15:29"/>Ekungeneni kwebhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> eMzini kaDavida, uMikhali indodakazi kaSawuli wayebukele elunguze ngefasitela. Wathi ebona inkosi uDavida izithokozisa igida, wayeyisa ngenhliziyo yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 15:29"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 15"/>
  <chapter number="16" style="c" sid="1CH 16"/>
  <para style="s1">Ibhokisi Lesivumelwano SikaThixo Libekwa Ethenteni</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 16:1"/>Balithwala ibhokisi lesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu bayalingenisa ethenteni uDavida ayelilungiselele lona, banikela ngeminikelo yokutshiswa leyobudlelwano phambi kukaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="1CH 16:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 16:2"/>UDavida eseqedile ukunikela ngeminikelo yokutshiswa langeyobudlelwano, wabusisa abantu ngebizo <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>. <verse eid="1CH 16:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 16:3"/>Wababela bonke abako-Israyeli, abesilisa labesifazane, yilowo lalowo isinkwa, lekhekhe lezithelo kanye lekhekhe lamavini awonyisiweyo.<verse eid="1CH 16:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 16:4"/>Wakhetha abanye abaLevi ukukhonza phambi kwebhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> bedumisa <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, bebonga uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli: <verse eid="1CH 16:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 16:5"/>Induna kwakungu-Asafi, uZakhariya engumsekeli, kulandela uJeyeli, loShemiramothi, loJehiyeli, loMathithiya, lo-Eliyabi, loBhenaya, lo-Obhedi-Edomi kanye loJeyiyeli. Babezatshaya amachacho lemihubhe, u-Asafi etshaya izigubhu, <verse eid="1CH 16:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 16:6"/>abaphristi uBhenaya loJahaziyeli bengabokuvuthela amacilongo phambi kwebhokisi lesivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu.<verse eid="1CH 16:6"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ihubo Lokubonga KukaDavida</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 16:7"/>Ngalolosuku uDavida wamisa ukuba u-Asafi labanye bakhe bahlabelele lelihubo bebonga <char style="nd">uThixo</char>:<verse eid="1CH 16:7"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 16:8"/>Bongani <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, memezani ibizo lakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:8">lizazise phakathi kwabantu izenzo zakhe.<verse eid="1CH 16:8"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 16:9"/>Hlabelelani kuye, hlabelelani indumiso kuye;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:9">likhulume ngezenzo zakhe zonke ezimangalisayo.<verse eid="1CH 16:9"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 16:10"/>Jabulani ebizweni lakhe elingcwele;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:10">kazithokoze inhliziyo zabo abamdingayo <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="1CH 16:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 16:11"/>Dingani <char style="nd">uThixo</char> lamandla akhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:11">limdinge yena njalonjalo.<verse eid="1CH 16:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 16:12"/>Khumbulani izenzo zakhe ezimangalisayo azenzayo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:12">izimangaliso azenzayo, lezahlulelo azikhulumayo,<verse eid="1CH 16:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 16:13"/>lina zizukulwane zika-Israyeli inceku yakhe,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:13">lina madodana kaJakhobe, abakhethiweyo bakhe.<verse eid="1CH 16:13"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 16:14"/>Yena <char style="nd">unguThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wethu;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:14">izahlulelo zakhe zigcwele wonke umhlaba.<verse eid="1CH 16:14"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 16:15"/>Uyakhumbula isivumelwano sakhe nini lanini,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:15">ilizwi lomlayo wakhe, okwezizukulwane ezizinkulungwane,<verse eid="1CH 16:15"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 16:16"/>isivumelwano asenza lo-Abhrahama,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:16">isifungo asenza lo-Isaka,<verse eid="1CH 16:16"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 16:17"/>wasiqinisa kuJakhobe saba yisimiso,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:17">laku-Israyeli saba yisivumelwano esingapheliyo,<verse eid="1CH 16:17"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 16:18"/>wathi âNgizalinika ilizwe laseKhenani</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:18">njengesabelo selifa lenu.â<verse eid="1CH 16:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 16:19"/>Kwathi lisesebalutshwana,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:19">bebalutshwana kakhulu, beyizihambi kulo,<verse eid="1CH 16:19"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 16:20"/>bezula kuzizwe ngezizwe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:20">besuka komunye umbuso besiya komunye.<verse eid="1CH 16:20"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 16:21"/>Kavumelanga loba ngubani ukubancindezela;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:21">wawakhuza amakhosi ngenxa yabo,<verse eid="1CH 16:21"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 16:22"/>âLingabathinti abagcotshiweyo bami;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:22">lingahlukuluzi abaphrofethi bami.â<verse eid="1CH 16:22"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 16:23"/>Hlabelani <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> lina, mhlaba wonke,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:23">limemezele insindiso yakhe insuku ngezinsuku.<verse eid="1CH 16:23"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 16:24"/>Fakazani ngobukhosi bakhe ezizweni zonke,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:24">lemisebenzi yakhe emangalisayo phakathi kwabantu bonke.<verse eid="1CH 16:24"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 16:25"/>Ngoba umkhulu <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, ufanele ukudunyiswa ngokuphindiweyo;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:25">kumele esatshwe ngaphezu kwabonkulunkulu bonke.<verse eid="1CH 16:25"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 16:26"/>Ngoba bonke onkulunkulu bezizwe bayizithombe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:26">kodwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wadala amazulu.<verse eid="1CH 16:26"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 16:27"/>Inkazimulo lobukhosi kuphambi Kwakhe</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:27">Amandla lentokozo kusendaweni yakhe yokuhlala.<verse eid="1CH 16:27"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 16:28"/>Mnikeni <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, lina zizukulwane zezizwe.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:28">Mnikeni <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ubukhosi lamandla.<verse eid="1CH 16:28"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 16:29"/>Mnikeni <char style="nd">uThixo</char> udumo olufanele ibizo lakhe.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:29">Lethani umnikelo libuye phambi kwakhe.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="1CH 16:29">Mkhonzeni <char style="nd">uThixo</char> enkazimulweni yobungcwele bakhe;<verse eid="1CH 16:29"/></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 16:30"/>thuthumelani phambi kwakhe mhlaba wonke!</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:30">Umhlaba ugxilile, ngeke ugudluzwe.<verse eid="1CH 16:30"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 16:31"/>Amazulu kawathokoze, lomhlaba ujabule,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:31">kabathi phakathi kwabezizwe, â<char style="nd">UThixo</char> uyabusa.â<verse eid="1CH 16:31"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 16:32"/>Ulwandle kaluhlokome lakho konke okukulo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:32">amasimu kawathakazelele lakho konke okukuwo.<verse eid="1CH 16:32"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="1CH 16:33"/>Lapho-ke izihlahla zonke zeganga zizahlabela</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:33">ngentokozo phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:33">ngoba uyeza ukuzakwahlulela umhlaba.<verse eid="1CH 16:33"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="1CH 16:34"/>Bongani <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ngoba ulungile.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:34">Uthando lwakhe olungapheliyo lumi kokuphela.<verse eid="1CH 16:34"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="35" style="v" sid="1CH 16:35"/>Celani lithi: âSisindise, Oh Nkulunkulu Mkhululi wethu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:35">usiqoqe usikhulule phakathi kwezizwe,</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="1CH 16:35">ukuze silibonge ibizo lakho elingcwele,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:35">sijabule ekukudumiseni.â<verse eid="1CH 16:35"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="36" style="v" sid="1CH 16:36"/>Kabongwe <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 16:36">kusukela endulo kuze kube nininini.</para>
  <para style="m" vid="1CH 16:36">Bonke abantu bathi: âAmeni. Kabongwe <char style="nd">uThixo</char>!â<verse eid="1CH 16:36"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="37" style="v" sid="1CH 16:37"/>UDavida wasetshiya o-Asafi labakhula bakhe ukuba bagcine ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>, bakhonze njalo benze konke okufanele kwenziwe lapho ngezinsuku zonke. <verse eid="1CH 16:37"/><verse number="38" style="v" sid="1CH 16:38"/>Abanye abatshiya lapho ukuze bakhonze labo ngo-Obhedi-Edomi labakhula bakhe, ababengamatshumi ayisithupha lasificaminwembili. U-Obhedi-Edomi indodana kaJeduthuni, kanye loHosa babengabalindi bamasango.<verse eid="1CH 16:38"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="39" style="v" sid="1CH 16:39"/>UDavida watshiya uZadokhi umphristi kanye labanye abaphristi phambi kwethabanikeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> endaweni ephakemeyo yokukhonzela eGibhiyoni <verse eid="1CH 16:39"/><verse number="40" style="v" sid="1CH 16:40"/>ukunikela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> iminikelo yokutshiswa e-alithareni ngezikhathi zonke, ekuseni lantambama, njengokulotshiweyo eMthethweni <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>, awupha abako-Israyeli. <verse eid="1CH 16:40"/><verse number="41" style="v" sid="1CH 16:41"/>Abanye abasala labo babengoHemani loJeduthuni labanye bonke balabo ababekhethiwe beqanjwa ngamabizo ukuba badumise <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, ângoba uthando lwakhe lumi kuze kube nininini.â <verse eid="1CH 16:41"/><verse number="42" style="v" sid="1CH 16:42"/>UHemani loJeduthuni babengabokuvuthela amacilongo lokutshaya izigubhu lamanye amachacho ezingoma ezingcwele. Amadodana kaJeduthuni ayehlala esangweni.<verse eid="1CH 16:42"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="43" style="v" sid="1CH 16:43"/>Abanye bonke basuka, ngulowo lalowo waqonda emzini wakhe, uDavida wabuyela emzini wakhe ukuyabusisa abendlu yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 16:43"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 16"/>
  <chapter number="17" style="c" sid="1CH 17"/>
  <para style="s1">Isithembiso SikaNkulunkulu KuDavida</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 17:1"/>UDavida esehlezi esigodlweni sakhe wasesithi kuNathani umphrofethi, âUyabona, mina ngihlezi esigodlweni esakhiwa ngomsedari, kodwa ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> lingaphansi kwethente.â<verse eid="1CH 17:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 17:2"/>UNathani wathi kuDavida, âKonke okusengqondweni yakho, kwenze, ngoba uNkulunkulu ulawe.â<verse eid="1CH 17:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 17:3"/>Ngalobobusuku ilizwi likaNkulunkulu leza kuNathani, lisithi:<verse eid="1CH 17:3"/></para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 17:4"/>âHamba uyetshela inceku yami uDavida uthi, âNanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>: Ayisuwe ozangakhela indlu yokuhlala kuyo. <verse eid="1CH 17:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 17:5"/>Angikahlali endlini kusukela mhla ngakhulula abako-Israyeli eGibhithe kuze kube lamuhla. Sengibhode ngisuka kulelithente ngaya kuleliyana, ngisuka endaweni ethile yokuhlala ngisiya kweyinye. <verse eid="1CH 17:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 17:6"/>Konke lapho engihambe khona labako-Israyeli, kambe kukhona lapho engike ngathi kubakhokheli babo engabalaya ukuthi beluse abantu bami, âKungani lingangakhelanga indlu yemisedari na?âââ<verse eid="1CH 17:6"/></para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 17:7"/>Ngakho tshela inceku yami uDavida ukuthi, âNanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> uSomandla: Ngakuthatha emadlelweni ekweluseni izimvu, ukuze ube ngumbusi wabantu bami abako-Israyeli. <verse eid="1CH 17:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 17:8"/>Ngibe ngilawe lapho obuhamba khona, ngizinqobile zonke izitha zakho phambi kwakho. Ngalokho ibizo lakho ngizalenza libe lodumo olufana lamabizo amadoda adume kakhulu emhlabeni. <verse eid="1CH 17:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 17:9"/>Njalo ngizalungisela abantu bami bako-Israyeli indawo engeyabo ngibafake khona labo babe lekhaya labo lapho abangayikuhlutshwa khona. Abantu abagangileyo abasayikubancindezela futhi, njengalokhu abakwenza kuqala <verse eid="1CH 17:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 17:10"/>lalokhu asebephikelele ukukwenza kusukela esikhathini engamisa ngaso abakhokheli ebantwini bami u-Israyeli. Ngizazinqoba zonke izitha zakho.</para>
  <para style="pm" vid="1CH 17:10">Ngiyaqinisa kuwe ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uzakwakhela indlu: <verse eid="1CH 17:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 17:11"/>Kuzakuthi nxa insuku zakho seziphelile ususiya kubokhokho bakho, ngizakwenza inzalo yakho ithathe isikhundla sakho, omunye wamadodana akho, njalo ngizawuqinisa umbuso wakhe. <verse eid="1CH 17:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 17:12"/>Lowo nguye ozangakhela indlu yami, ngakho ngizamisa isihlalo sombuso wakhe kuze kube nininini. <verse eid="1CH 17:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 17:13"/>Ngizakuba nguyise, yena abe yindodana yami. Angiyikususa uthando lwami kuye, njengalokhu engakwenza kulowo owakwandulelayo. <verse eid="1CH 17:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 17:14"/>Ngizambeka yena endlini yami lasembusweni wami kuze kube nininini, lombuso wakhe uzakuma kokuphela.âââ<verse eid="1CH 17:14"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 17:15"/>UNathani wabikela uDavida amazwi wonke esambulelo.<verse eid="1CH 17:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umkhuleko KaDavida</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 17:16"/>Ngakho inkosi uDavida wangena wahlala phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>, wasesithi,</para>
  <para style="pm" vid="1CH 17:16">âNgingubani mina, awu <char style="nd">Thixo</char> Nkulunkulu wami, bayini abendlu yami, lokho okwenze waze wangibeka kulesi isimo? <verse eid="1CH 17:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 17:17"/>Kanti njalonje lakho kubuye kukhanye kungathi kakwenelanga emehlweni akho, Oh Nkulunkulu, usukhulume ngelizayo ngendlu yenceku yakho. Ungiphethe Nkulunkulu wami, awu <char style="nd">Thixo</char> Nkulunkulu wami, kungathi ngingomunye wabaphakemeyo kakhulu.<verse eid="1CH 17:17"/></para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 17:18"/>Kambe kuyini okunye uDavida angakutsho kuwe ngokuhlonipha okwenze encekwini yakho? Ngoba wena uyayazi inceku yakho, <verse eid="1CH 17:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 17:19"/>Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>. Ngenxa yenceku yakho, njalo langentando yakho, uyenzile into le enkulu, waziveza obala lezizithembiso ezinkulu kangaka.<verse eid="1CH 17:19"/></para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 17:20"/>Kakho ofanana lawe, Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>, njalo kakho omunye uNkulunkulu kodwa nguwe kuphela, njengoba sesizwile ngezethu indlebe. <verse eid="1CH 17:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 17:21"/>Njalo ngubani ongafanana labantu bakho bako-Israyeli esiyiso sodwa isizwe emhlabeni esiloNkulunkulu owayazikhululela abantu, lokuzenzela ibizo, lokwenza imimangaliso enzima ngokuxotsha izizwe phambi kwabantu bakho, owabakhulula eGibhithe? <verse eid="1CH 17:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 17:22"/>Wabenza abantu bakho u-Israyeli baba ngabantu bakho kuze kube nini lanini, njalo wena, <char style="nd">Thixo</char>, usunguNkulunkulu wabo.<verse eid="1CH 17:22"/></para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 17:23"/>Lakhathesi, <char style="nd">Thixo</char> akuthi lesosithembiso owasenza encekwini yakho labendlu yayo sigcwaliseke kuze kube nininini. Yenza njengokuthembisa kwakho, <verse eid="1CH 17:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 17:24"/>kuze kubonakale ukuthi ibizo lakho lizaphakanyiswa kuze kube nininini. Ngakho abantu bazakuthi, â<char style="nd">UThixo</char> uSomandla, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli, ngoka-Israyeli uNkulunkulu!â Kuthi indlu yenceku yakho imiswe phambi kwakho.<verse eid="1CH 17:24"/></para>
  <para style="pm">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 17:25"/>Wena Nkulunkulu wami ukuveze obala encekwini yakho ukuthi uzayakhela indlu. Ngalokho inceku yakho isithole isibindi sokukhuleka kuwe. <verse eid="1CH 17:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 17:26"/>Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>, unguNkulunkulu wena! Usuthembise lezizinto ezinhle encekwini yakho. <verse eid="1CH 17:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 17:27"/>Ngakho kukuthokozisile ukubusisa indlu yenceku yakho, ukuthi ibe khona phambi kwakho kuze kube nininini ebusweni bakho; ngoba wena, Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>, uyibusisile, njalo izabusiswa nini lanini.â<verse eid="1CH 17:27"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 17"/>
  <chapter number="18" style="c" sid="1CH 18"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukunqoba KukaDavida</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 18:1"/>Ngokuqhubeka kwesikhathi uDavida wahlasela amaFilistiya wawanqoba, wathumba iGathi lemizana eseduzane layo eyayiphethwe ngamaFilistiya.<verse eid="1CH 18:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 18:2"/>UDavida wanqoba njalo amaMowabi aba ngaphansi kwakhe athela kuye.<verse eid="1CH 18:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 18:3"/>Kanti njalo, uDavida walwa loHadadezeri inkosi yaseZobha, kwaze kwafika eHamathi, esiyamisa umbuso wakhe emangweni olandela uMfula iYufrathe. <verse eid="1CH 18:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 18:4"/>UDavida wathumba izinqola zakhe zokulwa eziyinkulungwane, abatshayeli bazo abazinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa lamabutho ahamba phansi azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili. Wawaquma imisila wonke amabhiza ezinqola zokulwa kwasala alikhulu kuphela.<verse eid="1CH 18:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 18:5"/>Kwathi ama-Aramu aseDamaseko ezoncedisa uHadadezeri inkosi yaseZobha, uDavida wawatshaya wawabhuqa ama-Aramu kwafa azinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amabili lambili. <verse eid="1CH 18:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 18:6"/>Wenza izinqaba e-Aramu embusweni waseDamaseko, ama-Aramu aba ngaphansi kombuso wakhe athela kuye. <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wanika uDavida ukunqoba kuzozonke izindawo ayezihlasela.<verse eid="1CH 18:6"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 18:7"/>UDavida wathatha amahawu egolide ayephethwe yizikhulu zikaHadadezeri wawathwalela eJerusalema. <verse eid="1CH 18:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 18:8"/>Kusukela eThebha laseKhuni, imizi eyayingekaHadadezeri, uDavida wathatha khona ithusi elinengi kakhulu, lelo uSolomoni enza ngalo uLwandle lwethusi, izinsika lezinye impahla ezabunjwa ngethusi.<verse eid="1CH 18:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 18:9"/>Kuthe lapho Towu inkosi yaseHamathi isizwe ukuthi uDavida usenqobe lonke ibutho likaHadadezeri inkosi yaseZobha, <verse eid="1CH 18:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 18:10"/>wathumela indodana yakhe uHadoramu enkosini uDavida ukuthi iyembingelela emenzela amhlophe ngokunqoba uHadadezeri owayekade esilwa impi loTowu. UHadoramu wayethwele imihlobohlobo yezimpahla zegolide lesiliva kanye lezethusi.<verse eid="1CH 18:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 18:11"/>Inkosi uDavida yazahlukanisela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, lezo zinto njengalokho eyayikwenze impahla zegolide lesiliva ezazithunjwe kulezozizwe zama-Edomi lamaMowabi, lama-Amoni, lamaFilistiya lama-Amaleki.<verse eid="1CH 18:11"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 18:12"/>U-Abhishayi indodana kaZeruya watshaya wabhuqa ama-Edomi azinkulungwane ezilitshumi lasificaminwembili eSigodini seTswayi. <verse eid="1CH 18:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 18:13"/>Wabeka inkamba zamabutho okulinda e-Edomi, bonke abase-Edomi babangaphansi kombuso kaDavida. <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wapha uDavida ukunqoba kuzozonke izindawo ayesiya kuzo.<verse eid="1CH 18:13"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Iziphathamandla ZikaDavida</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 18:14"/>UDavida wabusa kulolonke elako-Israyeli, esenza okuqondileyo lokulungele abantu bakhe bonke.<verse eid="1CH 18:14"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 18:15"/>UJowabi indodana kaZeruya wayephethe amabutho;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 18:15">uJehoshafathi indodana ka-Ahiludi engumlobi,<verse eid="1CH 18:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 18:16"/>uZadokhi indodana ka-Ahithubi lo-Ahimeleki indodana ka-Abhiyathari babengabaphristi;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 18:16">uShavisha wayengumabhalane;<verse eid="1CH 18:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 18:17"/>uBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada wayephethe amaKherethi lamaPhelethi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 18:17">lamadodana kaDavida ayeyizikhulu ayeseduzane lenkosi embusweni.<verse eid="1CH 18:17"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 18"/>
  <chapter number="19" style="c" sid="1CH 19"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukunqotshwa Kwama-Amoni Lama-Aramu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 19:1"/>Kwathi emva kwesikhathi, uNahashi inkosi yama-Amoni wafa, ngakho indodana yakhe yathatha isikhundla yaba yinkosi. <verse eid="1CH 19:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 19:2"/>UDavida wacabanga wathi, âNgizakuba lomusa kuHanuni indodana kaNahashi ngoba uyise wayelomusa kimi.â Ngakho uDavida wathuma izithunywa ukuyakhalela uHanuni ngoyise.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 19:2">Izithunywa zikaDavida zithe zifika kuHanuni ukuthi zimkhalele elizweni lama-Amoni, <verse eid="1CH 19:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 19:3"/>izikhulu zama-Amoni zathi kuHanuni, âWena nkosi unakana ukuthi uDavida uhlonipha uyihlo ngokuthuma izithunywa zokukukhalela na? Amadoda akhe la kawasizinhloli ezithunywe ukuzahlola umumo welizwe ukuze ahluthune umbuso na?â <verse eid="1CH 19:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 19:4"/>Ngenxa yalokho uHanuni wabamba izithunywa zikaDavida, waziphuca, waquma izigqoko zazo zafika ezibunu, wasezixotsha.<verse eid="1CH 19:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 19:5"/>Kwathi uDavida esekuzwile lokho wathuma izithunywa ukuba zihlangabeze izithunywa, njengoba zazihlukuluzwe zayangiswa kakhulu. Inkosi yathi, âLina hlalani eJerikho indevu zenu zize zikhule, libe selisiza ngapha.â<verse eid="1CH 19:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 19:6"/>Kwathi ama-Amoni esebonile ukuthi asenuka emakhaleni kaDavida, uHanuni lama-Amoni bathumela amathalenta esiliva ayinkulungwane okuqhatsha izinqola zokulwa labatshayeli bazo e-Aramu Naharayimu, le-Aramu-Mahakha laseZobha. <verse eid="1CH 19:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 19:7"/>Baqhatsha izinqola zokulwa labatshayeli bazo abazinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu lambili, banxusa lenkosi uMahakha lamabutho akhe, yona eyeza yazakanisa eMedebha labantu bayo, ama-Amoni lawo eqoqana emadolobheni awo aphuma ukuya empini.<verse eid="1CH 19:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 19:8"/>Uthe ekuzwa lokho uDavida, wathumela uJowabi kanye lamabutho akhe wonke. <verse eid="1CH 19:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 19:9"/>Ama-Amoni asondela esehlome aphelela emangenelweni edolobho lakibo, kanti amakhosi ayenxusiwe ayejamile lawo wodwa egangeni.<verse eid="1CH 19:9"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 19:10"/>UJowabi wabona ukuthi kwakulamaviyo amabutho phambi kwakhe langemva kwakhe, ngakho wakhetha amanye amaqhawe athenjiweyo ko-Israyeli wabahlela ukuba bamelane lama-Aramu. <verse eid="1CH 19:10"/><verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 19:11"/>Amanye amabutho ayesele wathi kawalawulwe ngu-Abhishayi umfowabo, wona-ke ajamelana lama-Amoni. <verse eid="1CH 19:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 19:12"/>UJowabi wasesithi, âNxa ama-Aramu ezangikhulela, wena uzangihlomulela; kanti-ke nxa ama-Amoni ezakukhulela lami ngizakuhlomulela. <verse eid="1CH 19:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 19:13"/>Qina, kasilwe ngesibindi silwela abantu bakithi lemizi kaNkulunkulu wethu. <char style="nd">UThixo</char> uzakwenza lokho okufaneleyo njengokubona kwakhe.â<verse eid="1CH 19:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 19:14"/>Ngakho uJowabi lamabutho ayelawo wasuka ukuyakulwa lama-Aramu, wona ahle abaleka phambi kwakhe. <verse eid="1CH 19:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 19:15"/>Kuthe ama-Amoni ebona ukuthi ama-Aramu ayabaleka, abaleka lawo phambi kuka-Abhishayi umfowabo kaJowabi, abuyela phakathi kwedolobho. Ngakho uJowabi wasebuyela eJerusalema.<verse eid="1CH 19:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 19:16"/>Kwathi ama-Aramu esebonile ukuthi ehlulwe ngama-Israyeli, athuma izithunywa zayaphendula ama-Aramu ayengaphetsheya koMfula, kanye loShofaki umlawuli wamabutho kaHadadezeri lamabutho ayekhokhele.<verse eid="1CH 19:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 19:17"/>Kwathi uDavida esekutsheliwe lokhu, waqoqa bonke abako-Israyeli, wachapha uJodani, wajamelana labo ngamaviyo ayeqondene laye. UDavida walungiselela amaviyo akhe ukudibana lama-Aramu empini, lakanye alwa lawo. <verse eid="1CH 19:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 19:18"/>Abaleka ebona u-Israyeli, ngakho uDavida wabulala abatshayeli bezinqola zokulwa abazinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa lamabutho ahamba ngezinyawo azinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amane. Waze wabulala loShofaki umlawuli wamabutho akhona.<verse eid="1CH 19:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 19:19"/>Kwathi izinceku zikaHadadezeri zibona ukuthi zehlulwe ngabako-Israyeli, zaxolisana loDavida, zathela kuye.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 19:19">Ngakho ama-Aramu awathandanga ukunceda ama-Amoni kusukela lapho.<verse eid="1CH 19:19"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 19"/>
  <chapter number="20" style="c" sid="1CH 20"/>
  <para style="s1">Ukuthunjwa KweRabha</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 20:1"/>Kwathi entwasa, ngesikhathi sokuphuma kwezimpi zamakhosi ukuyakulwa, uJowabi wakhokhela amabutho ayehlomile. Watshaya wabhuqa ilizwe lama-Amoni waze wayavimbezela ilizwe laseRabha, kodwa uDavida wasala eJerusalema. UJowabi wahlasela iRabha wayitshiya ingamanxiwa. <verse eid="1CH 20:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 20:2"/>UDavida wathatha umqhele owawusekhanda lenkosi yabo isisindo sawo sasilithalenta legolide, uceciswe ngamatshe aligugu, umqhele wasufakwa ekhanda likaDavida. Wathatha impango enengi kakhulu kulelodolobho, <verse eid="1CH 20:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 20:3"/>njalo abantu ababelapho wabasusa wabasa lapho ababezasebenza khona gadalala ngamasaha, ngamapiki ensimbi kanye lamahloka. Lokhu uDavida wakwenza kuwo wonke amadolobho ama-Amoni. Kwathi uDavida ngokwakhe kanye lamabutho akhe wonke babuyela eJerusalema.<verse eid="1CH 20:3"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Impi LamaFilistiya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 20:4"/>Ngokuqhubeka kwesikhathi, kwaqhamuka impi yamaFilistiya, eGezeri. Ngalesosikhathi uSibhekhayi umHushathi wabulala uSiphayi, omunye wabosendo lwamaRefayi kwaba yikwehlulwa kwamaFilistiya.<verse eid="1CH 20:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 20:5"/>Kweyinye impi lamaFilistiya, u-Elihanani indodana kaJayiri wabulala uLahimi umfowabo kaGoliyathi umGithi, owayelomkhonto ololuthi olunjengolomeluki.<verse eid="1CH 20:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 20:6"/>Kanti njalo kwenye impi, eyalwelwa eGathi, kwakulendoda enkulu kakhulu ileminwe eyisithupha esandleni ngasinye, lamazwane ayisithupha enyaweni ngalunye, sekubalwa konke ndawonye kungamatshumi amabili lane. Laye wayengowosendo lukaRafa. <verse eid="1CH 20:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 20:7"/>Ngokuchothoza kwakhe abako-Israyeli, uJonathani indodana kaShimeya, umfowabo kaDavida, wambulala.<verse eid="1CH 20:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 20:8"/>Laba ngabosendo lukaRafa eGathi, njalo bafela ezandleni zikaDavida lamabutho akhe.<verse eid="1CH 20:8"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 20"/>
  <chapter number="21" style="c" sid="1CH 21"/>
  <para style="s1">UDavida Ubala Amabutho Empi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 21:1"/>USathane wasemelana labako-Israyeli njalo wafuqela uDavida ukuba abale abantu bako-Israyeli. <verse eid="1CH 21:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 21:2"/>Ngakho uDavida wathi kuJowabi kanye labalawuli bamabutho, âHambani liyebala u-Israyeli kusukela eBherishebha kusiya koDani. Beseliphenduka lizongitshela ukuze ngazi ukuthi bangaki khonale.â<verse eid="1CH 21:2"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 21:3"/>Kodwa uJowabi waphendula wathi, âSengathi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> angandisa amabutho akhe ngokuphindwe okwedlula ikhulu. Mhlekazi wami nkosi, kambe kabasibantu benkosi yami bonke laba? Inkosi yami ifunelani ukukwenza lokhu? Kungani ithanda ukwehlisela icala phezu kwabako-Israyeli?â<verse eid="1CH 21:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 21:4"/>Loba kwakunjalo, uJowabi wakhulelwa yilizwi lenkosi, ngakho uJowabi walibhoda lonke elako-Israyeli wasebuyela eJerusalema. <verse eid="1CH 21:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 21:5"/>UJowabi wafika wabikela uDavida inani lamadoda ayengalwa empini: Kulolonke elako-Israyeli kwakulamadoda ayisigidi lezinkulungwane ezilikhulu ayelakho ukuthi angayiphatha inkemba, kubalwa labazinkulungwane ezingamakhulu amane alamatshumi ayisikhombisa koJuda.<verse eid="1CH 21:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 21:6"/>Kodwa ekubaleni kwakhe uJowabi kazange ahlanganise abaLevi labakaBhenjamini, ngoba umlayo wenkosi wawumnenga. <verse eid="1CH 21:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 21:7"/>Kanti njalo lowomlayo wawuyisono phambi kukaNkulunkulu, lakanye wamjezisa u-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 21:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 21:8"/>Ngakho uDavida wasesithi kuNkulunkulu, âNgonile kakhulu phambi kwakho ngokwenza lokhu. Ngakho, ngiyakuncenga, susa umlandu lo encekwini yakho. Ngenze ubuwula obukhulu kakhulu.â<verse eid="1CH 21:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 21:9"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wakhuluma loGadi, umboni kaDavida, wathi: <verse eid="1CH 21:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 21:10"/>âHamba uyetshela uDavida ukuthi, âNanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>: Ngikunika ukuthi ukhethe phakathi kokuthathu. Khetha okukodwa okumele ngikwehlisele khona mina.âââ<verse eid="1CH 21:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 21:11"/>Ngakho uGadi waya kuDavida wathi kuye, âNanku okutshiwo <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>: âZikhethele wena okufunayo: <verse eid="1CH 21:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 21:12"/>iminyaka emithathu yendlala, loba izinyanga ezintathu zokududulwa uxotshwa yizitha zakho, ngenkemba zazo zikukhulela, loba insuku ezintathu zokumelana lenkemba <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>, kuyikuthi kuyabe kuyisifo elizweni, ingilosi <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> iletha incithakalo kulolonke elako-Israyeli.â Ngakho, khathesi khetha ukuthi ngifike ngithini kulo ongithumileyo.â<verse eid="1CH 21:12"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 21:13"/>UDavida wathi kuGadi, âNgisosizini olukhulu kakhulu; kungangcono ngizinikele ezandleni <char style="nd">zikaThixo</char>, ngoba umusa wakhe mkhulu kakhulu; kodwa unganginikeli ezandleni zabantu.â<verse eid="1CH 21:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 21:14"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wathumela isifo ko-Israyeli, kwafa amadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisikhombisa ko-Israyeli. <verse eid="1CH 21:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 21:15"/>Njalo uNkulunkulu wasethumela ingilosi ukuba iyechitha iJerusalema. Kodwa ingilosi ithe isakwenza lokho, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wazisola ngencithakalo eyayizakwenzakala wahle wakhuza ingilosi eyayizabhubhisa abantu wathi, âKwanele! Susa isandla sakho.â Ingilosi <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> ngalesosikhathi yayisimi esizeni sika-Onani umJebusi.<verse eid="1CH 21:15"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 21:16"/>UDavida wakhangela phezulu wabona ingilosi <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> imi phakathi kwezulu lomhlaba, iphethe inkemba esandleni sayo phezu kweJerusalema. Ngakho uDavida labadala, begqoke amasaka, bawa phansi ngobuso.<verse eid="1CH 21:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 21:17"/>UDavida wathi kuNkulunkulu, âAngithi yimi engithe akubalwe amadoda okulwa na? Yimi engonileyo ngadala isono. Laba abasilutho yizimvu ezilandelayo. Benzeni? Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char> Nkulunkulu wami, isandla sakho asiwele phezu kwami labendlu yami, kodwa akuthi isifo singasali ebantwini bakho.â<verse eid="1CH 21:17"/></para>
  <para style="s1">UDavida Wakha I-Alithari</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 21:18"/>Ngakho ingilosi <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> yathuma uGadi ukuthi ayetshela uDavida ukuthi ayekwakha i-alithari <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> esizeni sika-Onani umJebusi. <verse eid="1CH 21:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 21:19"/>Lakanye uDavida walalela ilizwi elakhitshwa nguGadi ngebizo <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>.<verse eid="1CH 21:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 21:20"/>U-Onani esabhula ingqoloyi, wanyemukula wabona ingilosi; amadodana akhe amane ayelaye acatsha. <verse eid="1CH 21:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 21:21"/>Kwasekufika uDavida, kuthe u-Onani embona, watshiya ukubhula wayakhothamela uDavida elokhu ebuso bukhothamele phansi.<verse eid="1CH 21:21"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 21:22"/>UDavida wathi kuye, âAke ungivumele ngibone isiza sakho sokubhulela amabele ukuze ngakhe i-alithari <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>, ukuze isifo esisebantwini simiswe. Ngithengisela sona ngentengo yaso egcweleyo.â<verse eid="1CH 21:22"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 21:23"/>U-Onani wathi kuDavida, âSithathe! Inkosi yami kayenze lokho ebona kuyithokozisa. Khangela, mina ngizaletha inkabi zomnikelo wokutshiswa, lemibhulo yokubhula izakuba zinkuni, ingqoloyi izakuba ngumnikelo wamabele. Konke lokhu ngiyakunika.â<verse eid="1CH 21:23"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 21:24"/>Kodwa inkosi uDavida yathi ku-Onani, âHayi, ngifuna ukuthenga ngentengo egcweleyo. Angiyikuthatha okuya <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> okungokwakho, angiyikunikela umnikelo wokutshiswa engingawuthenganga.â<verse eid="1CH 21:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 21:25"/>Ngakho uDavida wanika u-Onani amashekeli egolide angamakhulu ayisithupha ethenga leyondawo. <verse eid="1CH 21:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 21:26"/>UDavida wakhela <char style="nd">uThixo</char> i-alithari kuleyondawo wanikela iminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo yobudlelwano. Wakhuleka <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wamphendula ngomlilo uvela ezulwini phezu kwe-alithari lomnikelo wokutshiswa.<verse eid="1CH 21:26"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 21:27"/>Ngakho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wakhuluma lengilosi, yona yasibuyisela inkemba yayo esikhwameni sayo. <verse eid="1CH 21:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 21:28"/>Ngalesosikhathi, uDavida esebonile ukuthi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayemphendule esizeni sika-Onani umJebusi, wanikela iminikelo kuleyondawo. <verse eid="1CH 21:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 21:29"/>Ithabanikeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>, elalakhiwe nguMosi enkangala, kanye le-alithari leminikelo yokutshiswa ngalesosikhathi kwakusendaweni ephakemeyo eGibhiyoni. <verse eid="1CH 21:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 21:30"/>Kodwa uDavida wehluleka ukuya khona ukuze abuze kuNkulunkulu ngoba wayesesaba inkemba yengilosi <char style="nd">kaThixo</char>.<verse eid="1CH 21:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 21"/>
  <chapter number="22" style="c" sid="1CH 22"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 22:1"/>UDavida wasesithi, âIndlu <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu izakuba khonapha, kanye le-alithari lomnikelo wokutshiswa ka-Israyeli.â<verse eid="1CH 22:1"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Amalungiselelo Okwakha IThempeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 22:2"/>Ngakho uDavida wakhupha ilizwi lokuthi bonke abezizweni abahlala ko-Israyeli babuthaniswe, kwathi phakathi kwabo wakhetha ababazi bamatshe ukuze balungise babaze amatshe okwakha indlu kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="1CH 22:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 22:3"/>Wabuthanisa insimbi enengi kakhulu yokwenza izipikili zezivalo lezinsimbi zokuhlanganisa, wabuthanisa lethusi elinengi elingelakulinganiswa. <verse eid="1CH 22:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 22:4"/>Wadinga lezigodo zomsedari ezinengi ezingelakubalwa, ngoba amaSidoni labaseThire baletha inani lazo elikhulu kakhulu kuDavida.<verse eid="1CH 22:4"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 22:5"/>UDavida wasesithi, âIndodana yami uSolomoni isengumntwana njalo ayikabi lolwazi, ngoba phela indlu ezakwakhelwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> kumele ibe yindlu ebukekayo kakhulu ibe lodumo lesithunzi emehlweni ezizwe zonke. Ngakho ngizalungiselela ukwakhiwa kwayo.â Yikho uDavida walungiselela ngokujulileyo esaphila.<verse eid="1CH 22:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 22:6"/>Wasebiza uSolomoni indodana yakhe, wamlaya ukuthi akhele <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli indlu. <verse eid="1CH 22:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 22:7"/>UDavida wathi kuSolomoni: âNdodana yami, ngangizimisele ukwakhela iBizo <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wami indlu. <verse eid="1CH 22:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 22:8"/>Kodwa ilizwi <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> lafika kimi lisithi: âWena uchithe igazi elinengi, walwa izimpi ezinengi. Kawuyikwakhela iBizo lami indlu, ngoba uchithe igazi elinengi kakhulu emhlabeni. <verse eid="1CH 22:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 22:9"/>Kodwa, uzazala indodana ezakuba ngumuntu othanda ukuthula; ngizayiphumuza ezitheni zayo inxa zonke. Izathiwa nguSolomoni, njalo ngizanika u-Israyeli ukuthula ensukwini zokubusa kwakhe. <verse eid="1CH 22:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 22:10"/>Nguye ozakwakhela iBizo lami indlu. Uzakuba yindodana yami, mina ngizakuba nguyise. Njalo ngizaqinisa ubukhosi bakhe ko-Israyeli kuze kube nininini.â<verse eid="1CH 22:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 22:11"/>Ndodana yami, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> kabe lawe ukuze uphumelele ukwakha indlu <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakho, njengokutsho kwakhe ngawe. <verse eid="1CH 22:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 22:12"/>Sengathi <char style="nd">uThixo</char> angakunika ukuhlakanipha lokuqedisisa, ukuze kuthi lapho ekunika amandla ko-Israyeli, uwulondoloze umlayo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wakho. <verse eid="1CH 22:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 22:13"/>Uzaphumelela nxa unanzelela ukugcina izimiso lemithetho <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ayinika u-Israyeli ngoMosi. Qina, ube lesibindi. Ungesabi utshaywe luvalo.<verse eid="1CH 22:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 22:14"/>Ngayo yonke imizamo yami ngilungisele indlu <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> amathalenta egolide azinkulungwane ezilikhulu, lamathalenta esiliva ayisigidi, lethusi kanye lensimbi okulesisindo esingelakubalwa, lezigodo kanye lamatshe. Lawe ungengezelela kulokho. <verse eid="1CH 22:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 22:15"/>Ulezisebenzi ezinengi, ababazi bamatshe, labakha ngamatshe, lababazi, lezingcitshi zemisebenzi yonke, <verse eid="1CH 22:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 22:16"/>eyegolide, isiliva, ithusi kanye lensimbi, izingcitshi ezingelakubalwa. Qalisa-ke umsebenzi, <char style="nd">uThixo</char> abe lawe.â<verse eid="1CH 22:16"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 22:17"/>UDavida waselaya bonke abakhokheli bako-Israyeli ukuba basize uSolomoni indodana yakhe. <verse eid="1CH 22:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 22:18"/>Wathi kubo, â<char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu kakho kini na? Kalinikanga ukuthula inxa zonke na? Ngoba unikele abantu belizwe esandleni sami, lelizwe libuswa <char style="nd">nguThixo</char> labantu bakhe. <verse eid="1CH 22:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 22:19"/>Ngakho nikelani inhliziyo zenu ekufuneni <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu. Qalisani ukwakha indlu <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu, ukuze ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> lezitsha <char style="nd">zikaThixo</char> ezingcwele kungeniswe ethempelini elizakwakhelwa iBizo <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>.â<verse eid="1CH 22:19"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 22"/>
  <chapter number="23" style="c" sid="1CH 23"/>
  <para style="s1">AbaLevi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 23:1"/>Kwathi uDavida esemdala eseluphele, wabeka uSolomoni indodana yakhe ukuba abe yinkosi ko-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 23:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 23:2"/>Wasehlanganisa bonke abakhokheli bako-Israyeli, labaphristi kanye labaLevi. <verse eid="1CH 23:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 23:3"/>AbaLevi abaleminyaka esukela kwengamatshumi amathathu kusiya phezulu babalwa, inani lamadoda laba zinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu lasificaminwembili. <verse eid="1CH 23:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 23:4"/>UDavida wasesithi: âPhakathi kwalaba, abazinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane bazakhangela ukuqhutshwa komsebenzi wethempeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> kuthi abazinkulungwane eziyisithupha bazakuba yizikhulu labahluleli. <verse eid="1CH 23:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 23:5"/>Abazinkulungwane ezine bazakuba ngabalindi bamasango kuthi abazinkulungwane ezine badumise <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ngamachacho lezigubhu engizigcinele lowomsebenzi.â<verse eid="1CH 23:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 23:6"/>UDavida wehlukanisa abaLevi ngamaxuku kusiya ngamadodana kaLevi: uGeshoni, loKhohathi kanye loMerari.<verse eid="1CH 23:6"/></para>
  <para style="s1">AbakaGeshoni</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 23:7"/>Exukwini labakaGeshoni yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:7">uLadani loShimeyi.<verse eid="1CH 23:7"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 23:8"/>Amadodana kaLadani yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:8">nguJehiyeli owokuqala, loZethami kanye loJoweli, bonke bebathathu.<verse eid="1CH 23:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 23:9"/>Amadodana kaShimeyi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:9">nguShelomothi, loHaziyeli kanye loHarani, bonke bebathathu.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:9">Laba babezinhloko zezindlu zenzalo kaLadani.<verse eid="1CH 23:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 23:10"/>Lamadodana kaShimeyi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:10">nguJahathi, loZiza, loJewushi kanye loBheriya.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:10">Laba kwakungamadodana kaShimeyi, bonke babebane.<verse eid="1CH 23:10"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 23:11"/>UJahathi engowakuqala loZiza engowesibili, kodwa uJewushi loBheriya abazange babelamadodana amanengi, ngakho babalwa njengemuli yinye bahle baphiwa umsebenzi bendawonye.<verse eid="1CH 23:11"/></para>
  <para style="s1">AmaKhohathi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 23:12"/>Amadodana kaKhohathi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:12">ngu-Amramu, lo-Izihari, loHebhroni kanye lo-Uziyeli, bonke babebane.<verse eid="1CH 23:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 23:13"/>Amadodana ka-Amramu yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:13">ngu-Aroni loMosi.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:13">U-Aroni wehlukaniselwa ukunikela izinto ezingcwele kakhulu <char style="nd">kuThixo</char>, ukuze yena lamadodana akhe batshise impepha phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> lokumkhonza lokubusisa ngebizo lakhe kuze kube nininini. <verse eid="1CH 23:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 23:14"/>Amadodana kaMosi inceku kaNkulunkulu abalwa ndawonye labesizwana sikaLevi.<verse eid="1CH 23:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 23:15"/>Amadodana kaMosi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:15">nguGeshomu lo-Eliyezari.<verse eid="1CH 23:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 23:16"/>Abosendo lukaGeshomu:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:16">nguShubhayeli engowakuqala.<verse eid="1CH 23:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 23:17"/>Abosendo luka-Eliyezari:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:17">nguRehabhiya engowakuqala.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:17">U-Eliyezari kazange abe lamanye amadodana kodwa amadodana kaRehabhiya ayemanengi kakhulu.<verse eid="1CH 23:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 23:18"/>Amadodana ka-Izihari yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:18">nguShelomithi engowokuqala.<verse eid="1CH 23:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 23:19"/>Amadodana kaHebhroni yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:19">nguJeriya engowokuqala, lo-Amariya engowesibili,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:19">loJahaziyeli engowesithathu kanye loJekhameyamu owesine.<verse eid="1CH 23:19"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 23:20"/>Amadodana ka-Uziyeli yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:20">nguMikha engowakuqala lo-Ishiya owesibili.<verse eid="1CH 23:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">AmaMerari</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 23:21"/>Amadodana kaMerari yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:21">nguMahili loMushi.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 23:21">Amadodana kaMahili yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:21">ngu-Eliyezari loKhishi.<verse eid="1CH 23:21"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 23:22"/>U-Eliyezari wafa engelamadodana: wayelamadodakazi wodwa. Amadodakazi endela kubafowabo, amadodana kaKhishi.<verse eid="1CH 23:22"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 23:23"/>Amadodana kaMushi yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 23:23">nguMahili, lo-Ederi kanye loJerimothi, bonke bebathathu.<verse eid="1CH 23:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 23:24"/>Laba kwakungabosendo lukaLevi ngezindlu zabo, abazinhloko zezindlu njengokulotshwa kwamabizo lokubalwa kwabo ngamunye, okutsho ukuthi, abasebenzayo abaleminyaka engamatshumi amabili kusiya phezulu ababesebenza ethempelini <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>. <verse eid="1CH 23:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 23:25"/>Ngoba uDavida wathi: âNjengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli, enike abantu bakhe ukuthula lokuthi bazahlala eJerusalema kuze kube nininini, <verse eid="1CH 23:25"/><verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 23:26"/>abaLevi akusafanele bathwale ithabanikeli loba kuyini okusetshenziswa ezinkonzweni zalo.â <verse eid="1CH 23:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 23:27"/>Njengeziyalezelo zikaDavida zokucina, abaLevi babalwa kusukela kwabaleminyaka engamatshumi amabili kusiya phezulu.<verse eid="1CH 23:27"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 23:28"/>Umsebenzi wabaLevi wawungowokuncedisa inzalo ka-Aroni emsebenzini wethempeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>: ukugcina amaguma akhona; izindlu ezisemaceleni, ukuhlambulula zonke izinto ezingcwele lokwenza yonke imisebenzi endlini kaNkulunkulu. <verse eid="1CH 23:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 23:29"/>Babephethe umsebenzi wesinkwa sokwahlukanisela ethaleni, ifulawa yomnikelo wamabele, lesinkwa esingelamvubelo, ukuxuba lokupheka isinkwa, lezilinganiso zonke zezisindo lobukhulu bakhona. <verse eid="1CH 23:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 23:30"/>Njalo babemele beme ngezinyawo ekuseni nsuku zonke ukubonga lokudumisa <char style="nd">uThixo</char>. Kwakufanele benzenjalo lantambama, <verse eid="1CH 23:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 23:31"/>lalapho kunikelwa iminikelo yokutshiswa <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> ngamaSabatha, emadilini okuThwasa kweNyanga, lakuyo yonke imikhosi emisiweyo. Babefanele bamsebenzele <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ngazozonke izikhathi ngenani elilingeneyo langendlela ababeyimiselwe.<verse eid="1CH 23:31"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 23:32"/>Ngakho abaLevi bawenza umsebenzi wabo weThenteni lokuHlanganela, laseNdaweni eNgcwele, ngaphansi kwabafowabo abayisizukulwana sika-Aroni, emsebenzini wethempeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>.<verse eid="1CH 23:32"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 23"/>
  <chapter number="24" style="c" sid="1CH 24"/>
  <para style="s1">Izigaba ZabaPhristi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 24:1"/>Lezi yizo izigaba zamadodana ka-Aroni:</para>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 24:1">Amadodana ka-Aroni nguNadabi, lo-Abhihu, lo-Eliyazari kanye lo-Ithamari. <verse eid="1CH 24:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 24:2"/>Kodwa uNadabi lo-Abhihu bafa uyise engakafi, njalo babengelamadodana; ngakho u-Eliyazari lo-Ithamari yibo ababa ngabaphristi. <verse eid="1CH 24:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 24:3"/>Ngokuphathisana loZadokhi owosendo luka-Eliyazari kanye lo-Ahimeleki owosendo luka-Ithamari, uDavida wabehlukanisa ngezigaba kusiya ngemisebenzi ababemele bayenze. <verse eid="1CH 24:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 24:4"/>Babebanengi abosendo luka-Eliyazari abakhokheli kulabosendo luka-Ithamari ngakho behlukaniswa bamiswa njengalokhu: kwakusiba ngabalitshumi lesithupha kwabosendo luka-Eliyazari abazinhloko labayisificaminwembili kusendo luka-Ithamari. <verse eid="1CH 24:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 24:5"/>Babakhetha kungelakubandlulula ngokuphosa inkatho, ngoba zazikhona izikhulu zendawo yokuphephela lezikhulu zikaNkulunkulu phakathi kwabosendo luka-Eliyazari laphakathi koluka-Ithamari.<verse eid="1CH 24:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 24:6"/>Umlobi uShemaya indodana kaNethaneli, umLevi, waloba amabizo abo phambi kwenkosi kanye lezikhulu: uZadokhi umphristi, lo-Ahimeleki indodana ka-Abhiyathari kanye lenhloko zezimuli zabaphristi labaLevi, kuthathwa imuli eyodwa ku-Eliyazari kuphinde kuthathwe imuli eyodwa ku-Ithamari.<verse eid="1CH 24:6"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 24:7"/>Inkatho yakuqala yadla uJehoyaribhi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:7">eyesibili yadla uJedaya,<verse eid="1CH 24:7"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 24:8"/>eyesithathu yadla uHarimu,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:8">eyesine yadla uSeworimi,<verse eid="1CH 24:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 24:9"/>eyesihlanu yadla uMalikhija,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:9">eyesithupha yadla uMijamini,<verse eid="1CH 24:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 24:10"/>eyesikhombisa yadla uHakhozi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:10">eyesificaminwembili yadla u-Abhija,<verse eid="1CH 24:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 24:11"/>eyesificamunwemunye yadla uJeshuwa,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:11">eyetshumi yadla uShekhaniya,<verse eid="1CH 24:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 24:12"/>eyetshumi lanye yadla u-Eliyashibi,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:12">eyetshumi lambili yadla uJakhimi,<verse eid="1CH 24:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 24:13"/>eyetshumi lantathu yadla uHupha,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:13">eyetshumi lane yadla uJeshebheyabi,<verse eid="1CH 24:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 24:14"/>eyetshumi lanhlanu yadla uBhiliga,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:14">eyetshumi lesithupha yadla u-Imeri,<verse eid="1CH 24:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 24:15"/>eyetshumi lesikhombisa yadla uHeziri,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:15">eyetshumi lasificaminwembili mibili yadla uHapizezi,<verse eid="1CH 24:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 24:16"/>eyetshumi lesificamunwemunye yadla uPhethahiya,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:16">eyamatshumi amabili yadla uHezekhiyeli,<verse eid="1CH 24:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 24:17"/>eyamatshumi amabili lanye yadla uJakhini,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:17">eyamatshumi amabili lambili yadla uGamuli,<verse eid="1CH 24:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 24:18"/>eyamatshumi amabili lantathu yadla uDelaya,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:18">eyamatshumi amabili lane yadla uMaziya.<verse eid="1CH 24:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 24:19"/>Yizo lezi izigaba ababehlukaniswe ngazo ukuze benze umsebenzi wokukhonza ekungeneni kwabo ethempelini <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>, ngezimiso ezenzelwa ukhokho wabo u-Aroni, njengokulaywa kwakhe <char style="nd">nguThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 24:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abanye AbaLevi</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 24:20"/>Kwathi-ke ababesele abosendo lukaLevi:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 24:20"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 24:20">emadodaneni ka-Amramu: uShubhayeli;</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 24:20">emadodaneni kaShubhayeli: nguJehideya.<verse eid="1CH 24:20"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 24:21"/>Kuvela kuRehabhiya, amadodana akhe yila: ngu-Ishiya engowokuqala.<verse eid="1CH 24:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 24:22"/>Kuma-Izihari: nguShelomothi;</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 24:22">emadodaneni kaShelomothi; nguJahathi.<verse eid="1CH 24:22"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 24:23"/>Amadodana kaHebhroni yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 24:23">nguJeriya owokuqala lo-Amariya owesibili, loJahaziyeli owesithathu loJekhameyamu owesine.<verse eid="1CH 24:23"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 24:24"/>Indodana ka-Uziyeli: nguMikha;</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 24:24">emadodaneni kaMikha nguShamiri.<verse eid="1CH 24:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 24:25"/>Umfowabo kaMikha: ngu-Ishiya;</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 24:25">emadodaneni ka-Ishiya: nguZakhariya.<verse eid="1CH 24:25"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 24:26"/>Amadodana kaMerari: nguMahili loMushi.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 24:26">Indodana kaJahaziya: nguBheno.<verse eid="1CH 24:26"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 24:27"/>Amadodana kaMerari:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 24:27">Kusuka kuJahaziya: nguBheno, loShohamu, loZakhuri kanye lo-Ibhiri.<verse eid="1CH 24:27"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 24:28"/>Kusuka kuMahili: ngu-Eliyezari, ongazange abe lamadodana.<verse eid="1CH 24:28"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 24:29"/>Kusukela kuKhishi: indodana kaKhishi: nguJerameli.<verse eid="1CH 24:29"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 24:30"/>Njalo lakumadodana kaMushi: nguMahili, lo-Ederi kanye loJerimothi.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 24:30"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 24:30">Laba kwakungabaLevi, ngezimuli zabo.<verse eid="1CH 24:30"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 24:31"/>Labo baphosa inkatho, njengalokhu okwenziwa ngabafowabo abosendo luka-Aroni, phambi kweNkosi uDavida loZadokhi, u-Ahimeleki, labayizinhloko zezimuli zabaphristi kanye lezabaLevi. Imuli yomfowabo omdala yaphathwa njengemuli yomfowabo omncinyane kulabo bonke.<verse eid="1CH 24:31"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 24"/>
  <chapter number="25" style="c" sid="1CH 25"/>
  <para style="s1">Abahlabeleli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 25:1"/>UDavida, elabalawuli bamabutho, wakhetha abanye bamadodana ka-Asafi, uHemani loJeduthuni emsebenzini wokuphrofetha, baphelekezelwa yimihubhe lamachacho lezigubhu. Nantu uluhlu lwamadoda ayesenza lowomsebenzi:<verse eid="1CH 25:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 25:2"/>Emadodaneni ka-Asafi:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 25:2">nguZakhuri, loJosefa, loNethaniya kanye lo-Asarela. Amadodana ka-Asafi ayesesandleni sika-Asafi, yena owayephrofetha esesandleni senkosi.<verse eid="1CH 25:2"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 25:3"/>NgakuJeduthuni, amadodana akhe yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 25:3">nguGedaliya, loZeri, loJeshaya loShimeyi, loHashabhiya kanye loMathithiya, beyisithupha ndawonye, besesandleni sikayise uJeduthuni, owayephrofetha esebenzisa umhubhe ukubonga lokudumisa <char style="nd">uThixo</char>.<verse eid="1CH 25:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 25:4"/>NgakuHemani, amadodana akhe yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 25:4">nguBhukhiya, loMathaniya, lo-Uziyeli, loShubhayeli kanye loJerimothi; uHananiya, loHanani, lo-Eliyatha, loGidalithi loRomamthi-Ezeri; loJoshibhekhasha, loMalothi, loHothiri kanye loMahaziyothi. <verse eid="1CH 25:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 25:5"/>Bonke laba kwakungamadodana kaHemani umboni wenkosi. Bona ebaphiwe ngesithembiso sikaNkulunkulu sokumphakamisa. UNkulunkulu wapha uHemani amadodana alitshumi lane lamadodakazi amathathu.<verse eid="1CH 25:5"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 25:6"/>Wonke lamadoda ayephethwe ngoyise emsebenzini wokuhlabela ethempelini <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>, ngezigubhu, amachacho lemihubhe enkonzweni endlini kaNkulunkulu.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 25:6">U-Asafi, loJeduthuni kanye loHemani babengaphansi kwenkosi. <verse eid="1CH 25:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 25:7"/>Bona kanye lezihlobo zabo zonke babewufundele umsebenzi wokuhlabelela njalo bengamagabazi okuhlabelela <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, babengamakhulu amabili lamatshumi ayisificaminwembili labantu abayisificaminwembili (288). <verse eid="1CH 25:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 25:8"/>Abatsha labadala ngokufanayo, abafundisayo lababefunda, baphosa inkatho.<verse eid="1CH 25:8"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 25:9"/>Inkatho yakuqala eyayingeka-Asafi yawela kuJosefa lamadodana akhe kanye lezihlobo zakhe, belitshumi lambili;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 25:9">eyesibili yawela kuGedaliya, yena kanye lezihlobo lamadodana akhe belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 25:10"/>eyesithathu yawela kuZakhuri, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo zakhe, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 25:11"/>eyesine yawela ku-Iziri, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo zakhe belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 25:12"/>eyesihlanu yawela kuNethaniya, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo zakhe belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 25:13"/>eyesithupha yawela kuBhukhiya, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 25:14"/>eyesikhombisa yawela kuJesarela, lamadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 25:15"/>eyesificaminwembili yawela kuJeshayiya, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 25:16"/>eyesificamunwemunye yawela kuMathaniya, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 25:17"/>eyetshumi yawela kuShimeyi, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 25:18"/>eyetshumi lanye yawela ku-Azareli, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 25:19"/>eyetshumi lambili yawela kuHashabhiya, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:19"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 25:20"/>eyetshumi lantathu yawela kuShubhayeli, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:20"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 25:21"/>eyetshumi lane yawela kuMathithiya, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 25:22"/>eyetshumi lanhlanu yawela kuJerimothi, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:22"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 25:23"/>eyetshumi lesithupha yawela kuHananiya, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:23"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 25:24"/>eyetshumi lesikhombisa yawela kuJoshibhekhasha, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:24"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 25:25"/>eyetshumi lasificaminwembili yawela kuHanani, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:25"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 25:26"/>eyetshumi lesificamunwemunye yawela kuMalothi, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:26"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 25:27"/>eyamatshumi amabili yawela ku-Eliyatha, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:27"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 25:28"/>eyamatshumi amabili lanye yawela kuHothiri, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:28"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 25:29"/>eyamatshumi amabili lambili yawela kuGidalithi, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:29"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 25:30"/>eyamatshumi amabili lantathu yawela kuMahaziyothi, lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili;<verse eid="1CH 25:30"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 25:31"/>eyamatshumi amabili lane yawela kuRomamthi-Ezeri lakumadodana akhe lezihlobo, belitshumi lambili.<verse eid="1CH 25:31"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 25"/>
  <chapter number="26" style="c" sid="1CH 26"/>
  <para style="s1">Abalindi BamaSango</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 26:1"/>Izigaba zabalindi bamasango:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 26:1"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 26:1">KwabakoKhora:</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 26:1">kunguMeshelemiya indodana kaKhora, omunye wamadodana ka-Asafi. <verse eid="1CH 26:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 26:2"/>UMeshelemiya wayelamadodana ahlanganisa</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:2">uZakhariya eyakuqala loJediyeli eyesibili,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:2">loZebhadiya eyesithathu, loJathiniyeli eyesine,<verse eid="1CH 26:2"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 26:3"/>lo-Elamu eyesihlanu, loJehohanani eyesithupha kanye</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:3">lo-Eliyehonayi eyesikhombisa.<verse eid="1CH 26:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 26:4"/>U-Obhedi-Edomi laye wayelamadodana:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:4">kunguShemaya eyakuqala, loJehozabhadi eyesibili,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:4">loJowa eyesithathu, loSakhari eyesine,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:4">loNethaneli eyesihlanu, <verse eid="1CH 26:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 26:5"/>lo-Amiyeli eyesithupha,</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:5">lo-Isakhari eyesikhombisa, kanye loPhewulethayi eyesificaminwembili.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:5">(Ngoba uNkulunkulu wayembusisile u-Obhedi-Edomi.)<verse eid="1CH 26:5"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 26:6"/>Indodana yakhe uShemaya layo yayilamadodana, ayengabakhokheli kwabendlu kayise ngoba babengamadoda enelisayo. <verse eid="1CH 26:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 26:7"/>Amadodana kaShemaya wona yila:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:7">ngu-Othini, loRafayeli, lo-Obhedi kanye lo-Elizabhadi;</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:7">izihlobo zakhe u-Elihu loSemakhiya lazo zazingamadoda ayesenelisa.<verse eid="1CH 26:7"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 26:8"/>Bonke laba babengabosendo luka-Obhedi-Edomi; bona kanye lamadodana abo lezihlobo zabo babengamadoda enelisayo belamandla okwenza umsebenzi, bengabosendo luka-Obhedi-Edomi, babengamatshumi ayisithupha lambili (62) sebendawonye.<verse eid="1CH 26:8"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 26:9"/>UMeshelemiya wayelamadodana lezihlobo, amadoda ayekhaliphile ayelitshumi lasificaminwembili (18) esendawonye.<verse eid="1CH 26:9"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 26:10"/>UHosa ongumÊ¼Merari wayelamadodana:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:10">uShimiri engowakuqala (loba wayengasuye izibulo, uyise wayembeke kulesosikhundla sokuba ngowokuqala),<verse eid="1CH 26:10"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 26:11"/>loHilikhiya engowesibili, loThabhaliya engowesithathu kanye</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:11">loZekhariya engowesine.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 26:11">Amadodana lezihlobo zikaHosa sebendawonye babelitshumi lantathu (13).<verse eid="1CH 26:11"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 26:12"/>Izigaba zabalindi bamasango, kusiya ngabakhokheli bazo, zazilomlandu wokwenza umsebenzi ethempelini <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>, njengokwakusenziwa yizihlobo zabo. <verse eid="1CH 26:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 26:13"/>Benza inkatho isango lilinye, kusiya ngemuli, abatsha labadala kufanana.<verse eid="1CH 26:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 26:14"/>Inkatho yeSango langaseMpumalanga yawela kuShelemiya.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 26:14">Basebesenzela inkatho indodana yakhe uZakhariya owayengumcebisi okhaliphileyo, inkatho yeSango langaseNyakatho yawela kuye.<verse eid="1CH 26:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 26:15"/>Inkatho yeSango langaseZansi lawela ku-Obhedi-Edomi, amadodana akhe kwathiwa kawalinde isiphala.<verse eid="1CH 26:15"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 26:16"/>Inkatho yeSango langaseNtshonalanga kanye leSango leShalekhethi emgwaqweni ongaphezulu laya kuShuphimu loHosa.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 26:16"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 26:16">Kwalinda abalindi ngabalindi:<verse eid="1CH 26:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 26:17"/>Kwakusiba labaLevi abayisithupha ngelanga empumalanga,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 26:17">abane ngelanga enyakatho,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 26:17">abane ezansi ngelanga</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 26:17">kuthi esiphaleni kube lababili lakhona ngazozonke izikhathi.<verse eid="1CH 26:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 26:18"/>Phambili ngentshonalanga, kwakulabane emgwaqweni, ababili besegumeni uqobo.<verse eid="1CH 26:18"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 26:19"/>Lezi yizigaba zabalindi bamasango ababengabosendo lukaKhora loMerari.<verse eid="1CH 26:19"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abagcinisikhwama Lezinye Izikhulu</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 26:20"/>Abanye babaLevi babephatha inotho yethempeli likaNkulunkulu leziligugu ezingcwele.<verse eid="1CH 26:20"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 26:21"/>Abosendo lukaLadani, ababe ngamaGeshoni ngoLadani njalo ababezinhloko zabakaLadani umGeshoni, kwakunguJehiyeli, <verse eid="1CH 26:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 26:22"/>amadodana kaJehiyeli, loZethami lomfowabo uJoweli. Laba yibo ababephethe inotho yethempeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>.<verse eid="1CH 26:22"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 26:23"/>Kuma-Amramu, ama-Izihari, lamaHebhroni lama-Uziyeli babemi ngalindlela:<verse eid="1CH 26:23"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 26:24"/>uShubhayeli, owosendo lukaGeshomu indodana kaMosi, wayeyisikhulu esasiphethe ezenotho. <verse eid="1CH 26:24"/><verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 26:25"/>Izihlobo zakhe ngo-Eliyezari yilezi: nguRehabhiya indodana yakhe, loJeshaya indodana yakhe, loJoramu indodana yakhe, loZikhiri indodana yakhe loShelomithi indodana yakhe.<verse eid="1CH 26:25"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 26:26"/>(UShelomithi lezihlobo zakhe babephethe zonke ezenotho ezingcwele ezazinikelwe yinkosi uDavida, labayizinhloko zezindlu ababengabalawuli bezinkulungwane labalawuli bamakhulu, langabanye abalawuli bamabutho. <verse eid="1CH 26:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 26:27"/>Eyinye impango eyayithunjwe ekulweni bayinikela ekulungisweni kwethempeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>. <verse eid="1CH 26:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 26:28"/>Lakho konke okwakunikelwe nguSamuyeli umboni loSawuli indodana kaKhishi, lo-Abhineri indodana kaNeri loJowabi indodana kaZeruya, lazozonke ezinye ezazinikelwe zazisesandleni sikaShelomithi kanye lezihlobo zakhe.)<verse eid="1CH 26:28"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 26:29"/>Kwabaka-Izihari yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:29">UKhenaniya lamadodana akhe baphiwa umsebenzi ngaphandle kwethempeli, beyizikhulu labehluleli kwabako-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 26:29"/></para>
  <para style="li2">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 26:30"/>KwabakaHebhroni yilaba:</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:30">UHashabhiya lezihlobo zakhe, amadoda enelisayo ayengamakhulu alitshumi layisikhombisa ayekhangele ingxenye ka-Israyeli entshonalanga yeJodani kuwo wonke umsebenzi <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> lokuba yizinceku zenkosi. <verse eid="1CH 26:30"/><verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 26:31"/>AmaHebhroni wona, umkhokheli wawo kwakunguJeriya kusiya ngokulotshwa koluhlu lokuzalana kwezimuli zawo.</para>
  <para style="li2" vid="1CH 26:31">Kwathi ngomnyaka wamatshumi amane wokubusa kukaDavida kwahlolisiswa kuloluluhlu lwemibhalo, kwafunyanwa ukuthi amadoda akhaliphileyo phakathi kwamaHebhroni ayeseJazeri ngaseGiliyadi. <verse eid="1CH 26:31"/><verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 26:32"/>UJeriya wayelezihlobo ezingamakhulu angamatshumi amabili lesikhombisa, ezazikhaliphile njalo zizinhloko zezimuli zazo, ngakho inkosi uDavida wazibeka ukuthi ziphathe abakoRubheni, abakoGadi lengxenye yesizwana sikaManase kukho konke okwakungokukaNkulunkulu lokuyizindaba zenkosi.<verse eid="1CH 26:32"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 26"/>
  <chapter number="27" style="c" sid="1CH 27"/>
  <para style="s1">Amaviyo Empi</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 27:1"/>Nantu uluhlu lwabako-Israyeli, inhloko zezimuli, abalawuli bezinkulungwane labalawuli bamakhulu, ababesebenzela inkosi kulokho okuqondane lamaviyo empi ayefanele ukuzophisana ngenyanga kuze kuyephela umnyaka. Iviyo lilinye lalilamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000).<verse eid="1CH 27:1"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 27:2"/>Owayephethe iviyo lakuqala, ngenyanga yakuqala, kwakunguJashobheyamu indodana kaZabhidiyeli. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000) esigabeni sakhe. <verse eid="1CH 27:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 27:3"/>Yena wayengowosendo lukaPherezi njalo eyinduna yezikhulu zonke zamabutho okwenyanga yakuqala.<verse eid="1CH 27:3"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 27:4"/>Owayephethe iviyo ngenyanga yesibili kwakunguDodayi wako-Ahohi; uMikhilothi engumkhokheli weviyo lakhe. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000) eviyweni lakhe.<verse eid="1CH 27:4"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 27:5"/>Umlawuli wamabutho wesithathu, owezopho lesithathu, kwakunguBhenaya indodana kaJehoyada umphristi. Wayeyinduna, njalo esigabeni sakhe kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000). <verse eid="1CH 27:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 27:6"/>Nguyenalo uBhenaya owayeliqhawe phakathi kwamaTshumi amaThathu njalo eyinduna yamaTshumi amaThathu. Indodana yakhe u-Amizabhadi yayiphethe iviyo lakhe.<verse eid="1CH 27:6"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 27:7"/>Owesine, owezopho lenyanga yesine, kwakungu-Asaheli umfowabo kaJowabi; indodana yakhe uZebhadiya wasala esethatha isikhundla sakhe. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000) eviyweni lakhe.<verse eid="1CH 27:7"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 27:8"/>Owesihlanu, owezopho lenyanga yesihlanu, kwakungumlawuli uShamihuthi owako-Izira. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000) eviyweni lakhe.<verse eid="1CH 27:8"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 27:9"/>Owesithupha, owezopho lenyanga yesithupha, kwakungu-Ira indodana ka-Ikheshi waseThekhowa. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000) eviyweni lakhe.<verse eid="1CH 27:9"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 27:10"/>Owesikhombisa, owezopho lenyanga yesikhombisa, kwakunguHelezi umPheloni, owako-Efrayimi. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000) eviyweni lakhe.<verse eid="1CH 27:10"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 27:11"/>Owesificaminwembili, owezopho lenyanga yesificaminwembili, kwakunguSibhekhayi umHushathi wakoZera. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000) eviyweni lakhe.<verse eid="1CH 27:11"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 27:12"/>Owesificamunwemunye, owezopho lesificamunwemunye, kwakungu-Abhiyezeri umÊ¼Anathothi owakoBhenjamini. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000) eviyweni lakhe.<verse eid="1CH 27:12"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 27:13"/>Owetshumi, owezopho lenyanga yetshumi, kwakunguMaharayi umNethofa wakoZera. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000) eviyweni lakhe.<verse eid="1CH 27:13"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 27:14"/>Owetshumi lanye, owezopho lenyanga yetshumi lanye, kwakunguBhenaya umPhirathoni wako-Efrayimi. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000) eviyweni lakhe.<verse eid="1CH 27:14"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 27:15"/>Owetshumi lambili, owezopho lenyanga yetshumi lambili, kwakunguHelidayi umNethofa, owemuli ka-Othiniyeli. Kwakulamadoda azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amabili lane (24,000) eviyweni lakhe.<verse eid="1CH 27:15"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Izikhulu Zezizwana</para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 27:16"/>Izikhulu ezizwaneni zako-Israyeli yilezi:</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 27:16"/>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:16">KwabakoRubheni: ngu-Eliyezari indodana kaZikhiri;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:16">kwabakoSimiyoni, nguShefathiya indodana kaMahakha;<verse eid="1CH 27:16"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 27:17"/>kwabakoLevi: nguHashabhiya indodana kaKhemuweli;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:17">kwabako-Aroni: nguZadokhi;<verse eid="1CH 27:17"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 27:18"/>kwabakoJuda: ngu-Elihu, umfowabo kaDavida;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:18">kwabaka-Isakhari: ngu-Omri indodana kaMikhayeli;<verse eid="1CH 27:18"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 27:19"/>kwabakoZebhuluni: ngu-Ishimaya indodana ka-Obhadaya;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:19">kwabakoNafithali: nguJerimothi indodana ka-Aziriyeli<verse eid="1CH 27:19"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 27:20"/>kwabako-Efrayimi: nguHosheya indodana ka-Azaziya;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:20">kwabayingxenye yesizwana sikaManase: nguJoweli indodana kaPhedaya;<verse eid="1CH 27:20"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 27:21"/>kwabayingxenye yesizwana sikaManase eGiliyadi: ngu-Ido indodana kaZakhariya;</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:21">kwabakoBhenjamini: nguJasiyeli indodana ka-Abhineri;<verse eid="1CH 27:21"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 27:22"/>kwabakoDani: ngu-Azareli indodana kaJerohamu.</para>
  <para style="b" vid="1CH 27:22"/>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 27:22">Laba babeyizikhulu ezizwaneni zako-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 27:22"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 27:23"/>UDavida kazange abhale phansi inani lamadoda ayeleminyaka engamatshumi amabili lababengaphansi kwaleyo, ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> wayethembise ukuthi wayezakwandisa u-Israyeli abe njengezinkanyezi emkhathini. <verse eid="1CH 27:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 27:24"/>UJowabi indodana kaZeruya waqalisa ukubala amadoda kodwa kaqedanga. Ulaka lwehlela u-Israyeli ngenxa yalokho kubalwa ngakho inani lelo alibhalwanga encwadini yezindaba zeNkosi uDavida.<verse eid="1CH 27:24"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Abacebisi BeNkosi</para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 27:25"/>U-Azimavethi indodana ka-Adiyeli wayephethe iziphala zesikhosini.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:25">UJonathani indodana ka-Uziya wayephethe iziphala emaphandleni ezabelweni, emadolobheni, emizini kanye lasezilindweni.<verse eid="1CH 27:25"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 27:26"/>U-Eziri indodana kaKhelubi wayephethe izisebenzi emaphandleni ezazilima amasimu.<verse eid="1CH 27:26"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 27:27"/>UShimeyi umÊ¼Ramathi wayephethe izivini.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:27">UZabhidi waseShefama wayephethe izithelo zezivini zokwenza iwayini.<verse eid="1CH 27:27"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 27:28"/>UBhali-Hanani umGederi wayephethe izihlahla zama-oliva lomkhiwane wesikhamore emawatheni ezintatshana zasentshonalanga.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:28">UJowashi wayephethe amafutha e-oliva.<verse eid="1CH 27:28"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 27:29"/>UShithirayi umSharoni wayephethe imihlambi eyayisemadlelweni aseSharoni.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:29">UShafathi indodana ka-Adilayi, wayephethe imihlambi ezihotsheni.<verse eid="1CH 27:29"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 27:30"/>U-Obhili owako-Ishumayeli wayephethe amakamela,</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:30">uJehideya owakoMeronothi ephethe ezabobabhemi.<verse eid="1CH 27:30"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="31" style="v" sid="1CH 27:31"/>UJazizi umHagari wayephethe ezemihlambi yezimvu.</para>
  <para style="li4" vid="1CH 27:31">Bonke laba babeyizikhulu ezaziphethe impahla zenkosi uDavida.<verse eid="1CH 27:31"/></para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="32" style="v" sid="1CH 27:32"/>UJonathani, isihlobo sikaDavida, wayengumcebisi, indoda ehlakaniphileyo njalo engumbhali.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:32">UJehiyeli indodana kaHakhimoni wayephethe amadodana enkosi.<verse eid="1CH 27:32"/></para>
  <para style="li1">
    <verse number="33" style="v" sid="1CH 27:33"/>U-Ahithofeli wayengumcebisi wenkosi.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:33">UHushayi owako-Arikhi wayengumngane wenkosi.<verse eid="1CH 27:33"/></para>
  <para style="li4">
    <verse number="34" style="v" sid="1CH 27:34"/>UJehoyada indodana kaBhenaya nguye owathatha isikhundla sika-Ahithofeli kwalandela u-Abhiyathari.</para>
  <para style="li1" vid="1CH 27:34">UJowabi wayengumlawuli webutho lenkosi.<verse eid="1CH 27:34"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 27"/>
  <chapter number="28" style="c" sid="1CH 28"/>
  <para style="s1">Amacebo KaDavida Ngokwakhiwa KweThempeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 28:1"/>UDavida wamema zonke izikhulu zako-Israyeli zabuthana eJerusalema: izikhulu zezizwana, abalawuli bamaviyo emsebenzini wenkosi, abalawuli bezinkulungwane kanye labalawuli bamakhulu, lezikhulu ezaziphethe ezezimpahla lezifuyo zenkosi lamadodana ayo, kanye lezikhulu zesigodlweni, amaqhawe labo bonke ababelezibindi empini.<verse eid="1CH 28:1"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 28:2"/>Inkosi uDavida yasukuma yathi: âLalelani, zihlobo labantu bami, bengizimisele ukwakhela ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>, indlu yokuhlala njalo kuyisenabelo sikaNkulunkulu wethu, ngaze ngenza amalungiselelo okukufeza lokho. <verse eid="1CH 28:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 28:3"/>Kodwa uNkulunkulu wathi kimi: âAwuyikulakhela indlu iBizo lami, ngoba wena ungowempi njalo usuchithe igazi.â<verse eid="1CH 28:3"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 28:4"/>Kodwa <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu ka-Israyeli, wakhetha mina kuyo yonke indlu yakwethu ukuba yinkosi yako-Israyeli kuze kube nininini. Wakhetha uJuda ukuba abe ngumkhokheli, kwathi khona endlini kaJuda wakhetha imuli yakwethu, kwazakuthi emadodaneni kababa kumthokozisile ukungibeka ngibe yinkosi kulolonke elako-Israyeli. <verse eid="1CH 28:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 28:5"/>Kuwo wonke amadodana ami njengoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> engiphe amanengi, umkhethile uSolomoni indodana yami ukuba ahlale esihlalweni sobukhosi esikhosini sombuso <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> ko-Israyeli. <verse eid="1CH 28:5"/><verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 28:6"/>Wathi kimi: âUSolomoni indodana yakho yiyo ezangakhela indlu yami ilungise lamaguma ami, ngoba ngimkhethile ukuba abe yindodana yami, lami ngizakuba nguyise. <verse eid="1CH 28:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 28:7"/>Ngizawuqinisa umbuso wakhe kuze kube nininini nxa eqina ekugcineni imilayo yami lemithetho yami njengalokhu okwenzakalayo lamuhla.â<verse eid="1CH 28:7"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 28:8"/>Ngakho-ke phambi kwakhe wonke u-Israyeli, lebandla <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu, laphambi kukaNkulunkulu wethu: gcinani linanzelele imilayo <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu, ukuze libe lelizwe elihle elizalitshiyela izizukulwane kube yilifa lazo kuze kube nininini.<verse eid="1CH 28:8"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 28:9"/>Njalo wena ndodana yami, Solomoni, mamukele uNkulunkulu kayihlo, umkhonze ngokuzinikela ngenhliziyo yakho yonke langengqondo yokuvuma, ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uyihlola yonke inhliziyo kanti uyayazi iminakano lezenzo zonke. Nxa umdinga <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uzamthola wena, kodwa nxa umfulathela, uzakufulathela yena kuze kube nininini. <verse eid="1CH 28:9"/><verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 28:10"/>Nanzelela-ke ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> ukukhethile ukuba umakhele ithempeli libe yindawo yokukhonzela. Qina wenze umsebenzi.â<verse eid="1CH 28:10"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 28:11"/>Ngakho uDavida wasenika uSolomoni indodana yakhe umdwebo wesakhiwo sethempeli, lowezindlu zalo, lowezindlu zenotho, lowezindlu zangaphezulu, lowezindlu zangaphakathi, lowendlu yesihlalo somusa. <verse eid="1CH 28:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 28:12"/>Wamnika umdwebo wakho konke ayekutshengiswe nguMoya engqondweni yakhe ngamaguma ethempeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>, lowezindlu eziwazingelezeleyo, lowendlu yenotho yethempeli, lowendlu yenotho yezinto ezingcwele. <verse eid="1CH 28:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 28:13"/>Wamtshela langesimo sezigaba zabaphristi lezabaLevi, langawo wonke umsebenzi wasethempelini <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>, langezitsha zonke zenkonzo, <verse eid="1CH 28:13"/><verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 28:14"/>langesisindo segolide lazozonke izitsha zegolide zaleyo laleyo nkonzo, langesisindo sezitsha zesiliva zaleyo laleyo nkonzo: <verse eid="1CH 28:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 28:15"/>langesisindo sezinti zezibane zegolide kanye lezibane zazo, langesisindo segolide salolo lalololuthi lwesibane lezibane zalo, lobunzima besiliva balolo lalololuthi lwesibane lezibane zalo, njengokusetshenziswa kwazo enkonzweni; <verse eid="1CH 28:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 28:16"/>langesisindo segolide saleyotafula lezinkwa ezahlukaniselwe uNkulunkulu lesisindo sesiliva esamatafula enziwe ngesiliva; <verse eid="1CH 28:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 28:17"/>isisindo segolide elicengekileyo lezinti, imiganu yokuchelisa lezinkezo zakhona, lesisindo saleso lalesositsha segolide, kanye lesaleso lalesositsha sesiliva. <verse eid="1CH 28:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 28:18"/>Wamtshela langesimo se-alithare lempepha elenziwe ngegolide elicengekileyo lesisindo salo, langomfanekiso wesihlalo esingamakherubhi egolide achaye amaphiko awo egubuzele ibhokisi lesivumelwano <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char>.<verse eid="1CH 28:18"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 28:19"/>UDavida wasesithi: âKonke lokhu ngilakho kulotshwe ngesandla <char style="nd">sikaThixo</char> phezu kwami, njalo wanginika ukuzwisisa kukho konke lokhu langokuphelela kwesimo sakhona.â<verse eid="1CH 28:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 28:20"/>Okunye okwatshiwo nguDavida kuSolomoni indodana yakhe yikuthi, âQina ube lesibindi, njalo uwenze lumsebenzi. Ungesabi njalo ungalahli ithemba ngoba <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu, uNkulunkulu wami, ulawe. Kawuyikwehluleka njalo kayikukufulathela kuze kube sekupheleni komsebenzi wethempeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char>. <verse eid="1CH 28:20"/><verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 28:21"/>Izigaba zabaphristi labaLevi sebelindele wonke umsebenzi wethempeli likaNkulunkulu, njalo kuzakuthi bonke abazinikeleyo bakuphathise ngobungcitshi babo obupheleleyo kuyo yonke imisebenzi. Izikhulu labantu bonke zizayamukela yonke imilayo yakho.â<verse eid="1CH 28:21"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 28"/>
  <chapter number="29" style="c" sid="1CH 29"/>
  <para style="s1">Izipho Zokwakha IThempeli</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="1CH 29:1"/>Inkosi uDavida yathi ebandleni lonke: âIndodana yami uSolomoni, yena kanye osekhethwe nguNkulunkulu, usesengumfana njalo usesemutsha. Umsebenzi mkhulu, ngoba lesisakhiwo sobukhosi ayisiso esomuntu kodwa <char style="nd">ngesikaThixo</char> uNkulunkulu. <verse eid="1CH 29:1"/><verse number="2" style="v" sid="1CH 29:2"/>Sengilungiselele ngayo yonke inzuzo engilayo ukwakhiwa kwethempeli likaNkulunkulu wami, igolide lokwenza izinto zegolide, isiliva sokwenza izinto zesiliva, ithusi lokwenza izinto zethusi, lensimbi yokwenza izinto zensimbi, lezigodo zokwenza izinto zezigodo, kanye lohlobo lwamatshe e-onikisi, lamatshe okubekwa, lamatshe okucecisa, lalemibala, lenhlobonhlobo zonke zamatshe amahle lamatshe alukhuni amanengi, konke lokhu ngikubuthelele ngakunengi. <verse eid="1CH 29:2"/><verse number="3" style="v" sid="1CH 29:3"/>Ngaphandle kwalokho, ngenxa yokutshisekela kwami ithempeli likaNkulunkulu wami, manje senginikela inotho yami yegolide lesiliva ethempelini likaNkulunkulu wami ngaphezu kwakho konke engikulethileyo ethempelini leli elingcwele: <verse eid="1CH 29:3"/><verse number="4" style="v" sid="1CH 29:4"/>ngamathalenta egolide azinkulungwane ezintathu egolide (igolide lase-Ofiri) lamathalenta esiliva esicengekileyo azinkulungwane eziyisikhombisa okokugudula ngalo imiduli yezindlu, <verse eid="1CH 29:4"/><verse number="5" style="v" sid="1CH 29:5"/>okomsebenzi wegolide lokomsebenzi wesiliva lokwawo wonke umsebenzi ozakwenziwa yizingcitshi. Ngakho, ngubani ofuna ukuzinikela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> lamuhla?â<verse eid="1CH 29:5"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v" sid="1CH 29:6"/>Abazinhloko zezindlu, izikhulu zezizwana zako-Israyeli, abalawuli bezinkulungwane labalawuli bamakhulu, lezikhulu ezazikhangele ngokuqhutshwa komsebenzi wenkosi bapha ngokuzinikela. <verse eid="1CH 29:6"/><verse number="7" style="v" sid="1CH 29:7"/>Banikela emsebenzini wethempeli likaNkulunkulu amathalenta azinkulungwane ezinhlanu lezinhlamvu zegolide ezizinkulungwane ezilitshumi, lamathalenta esiliva azinkulungwane ezilitshumi, amathalenta ethusi azinkulungwane ezilitshumi lasificaminwembili mibili, lamathalenta azinkulungwane ezilikhulu ensimbi. <verse eid="1CH 29:7"/><verse number="8" style="v" sid="1CH 29:8"/>Loba ngubani owayelamatshe aligugu wawanikela endlini yenotho yethempeli <char style="nd">likaThixo</char> yona eyayiphethwe nguJehiyeli umGeshoni. <verse eid="1CH 29:8"/><verse number="9" style="v" sid="1CH 29:9"/>Abantu baba lokujabula okukhulu bebona ukuzinikela kwabakhokheli babo, ngoba banikela <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> ngokukhululeka langezinhliziyo zabo zonke. UDavida inkosi laye wajabula kakhulu.<verse eid="1CH 29:9"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Umkhuleko KaDavida</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v" sid="1CH 29:10"/>UDavida wamdumisa <char style="nd">uThixo</char> phambi kwebandla lonke esithi:</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="1CH 29:10">âKawudunyiswe, Wena <char style="nd">Thixo</char>,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 29:10">Nkulunkulu ka-Israyeli ukhokho,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 29:10">kusukela nininini kuze kube nininini.<verse eid="1CH 29:10"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="1CH 29:11"/>Bungobakho, Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>, ubukhulu lamandla</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 29:11">lodumo lobukhosi lenkazimulo,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 29:11">ngoba konke okusezulwini lokusemhlabeni kungokwakho.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="1CH 29:11">Bungobakho, Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>, ubukhosi;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 29:11">uphakeme wena phezu konke.<verse eid="1CH 29:11"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CH 29:12"/>Inotho lodumo kuvela kuwe;</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 29:12">ungumbusi wazo zonke izinto.</para>
  <para style="q1" vid="1CH 29:12">Esandleni sakho kukhona ukuqina lamandla.</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 29:12">Kukuwe ukuphakamisa lokupha amandla kubo bonke.<verse eid="1CH 29:12"/></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CH 29:13"/>Siyakubonga khathesi, Nkulunkulu wethu,</para>
  <para style="q2" vid="1CH 29:13">silidumisa ibizo lakho elilodumo.<verse eid="1CH 29:13"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="1CH 29:14"/>Kodwa mina ngiyini, bayini abantu bami, ukuthi sinikele ngenhliziyo yonke na? Konke kuvela kuwe, thina sikunike kuphela lokho okuvela esandleni sakho. <verse eid="1CH 29:14"/><verse number="15" style="v" sid="1CH 29:15"/>Singabezizweni lezethekeli emehlweni akho, njengoba labokhokho bethu bonke babenjalo. Insuku zethu emhlabeni ziyafanana lesithunzi, asisilutho, kalikho ithemba. <verse eid="1CH 29:15"/><verse number="16" style="v" sid="1CH 29:16"/>Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char> Nkulunkulu wethu, lokhu esesikunikele ngobunengi bakho ekwakhiweni kwethempeli eliyindawo yeBizo lakho eliNgcwele, kuvela esandleni sakho, njalo konke kuvele kungokwakho. <verse eid="1CH 29:16"/><verse number="17" style="v" sid="1CH 29:17"/>Ngiyazi, Nkulunkulu wami, uhlola inhliziyo njalo uyabuthanda ubuqotho. Zonke lezizinto ngizinikele ngokufisa langenhliziyo yobuqotho. Khathesi ngikhangele ngentokozo abantu bakho abalapha ukuthi banikele ngesifiso kuwe. <verse eid="1CH 29:17"/><verse number="18" style="v" sid="1CH 29:18"/>Oh <char style="nd">Thixo</char>, Nkulunkulu wabobaba o-Abhrahama, lo-Isaka lo-Israyeli, yenza inhliziyo zabantu bakho zime ngalokhu kulangatha, njalo inhliziyo zabo zibe kuwe kuze kube nininini. <verse eid="1CH 29:18"/><verse number="19" style="v" sid="1CH 29:19"/>Phana uSolomoni, indodana yami, inhliziyo epheleleyo ukuze agcine imilayo yakho lemithetho yakho lezimiso zakho, lokuthi akhe lesisakhiwo esiyisigodlo mina esengisilungiselele.â<verse eid="1CH 29:19"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v" sid="1CH 29:20"/>UDavida wasesithi kulolonke ibandla, âDumisani <char style="nd">uThixo</char> uNkulunkulu wenu.â Ngakho bonke bamdumisa <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, uNkulunkulu wabokhokho babo, bathi mbo ngobuso phansi, bekhonza <char style="nd">uThixo</char>, behlonipha lenkosi.<verse eid="1CH 29:20"/></para>
  <para style="s1">USolomoni Ugcotshwa Ubukhosi</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="21" style="v" sid="1CH 29:21"/>Ngosuku olulandelayo banikela imihlatshelo <char style="nd">kuThixo</char> leminikelo yokutshiswa: inkunzi eziyinkulungwane, lenqama eziyinkulungwane lamazinyane amaduna ayinkulungwane, leminikelo yokunathwayo, layo yonke eminye imihlatshelo banikela ngokunengi benikelela bonke abako-Israyeli. <verse eid="1CH 29:21"/><verse number="22" style="v" sid="1CH 29:22"/>Badla banatha ngokujabula okukhulu ngalolosuku phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char>.</para>
  <para style="p" vid="1CH 29:22">Basebememukela okwesibili uSolomoni indodana kaDavida, bamgcoba phambi <char style="nd">kukaThixo</char> ukuthi abe ngumbusi, kuthi uZadokhi abe ngumphristi. <verse eid="1CH 29:22"/><verse number="23" style="v" sid="1CH 29:23"/>USolomoni wasebusa embusweni <char style="nd">kaThixo</char> esikhundleni sikayise uDavida. Waphumelela njalo wonke u-Israyeli wamlalela. <verse eid="1CH 29:23"/><verse number="24" style="v" sid="1CH 29:24"/>Izikhulu zonke kanye lamaqhawe, ndawonye lamadodana eNkosi uDavida bazinikela ngaphansi kombuso weNkosi uSolomoni.<verse eid="1CH 29:24"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="25" style="v" sid="1CH 29:25"/>
    <char style="nd">UThixo</char> wamphakamisa kakhulu uSolomoni wamnika isithunzi phezu kwabo bonke abako-Israyeli, njalo wamnika ubukhosi obungazange bube khona esikhosini kwabako-Israyeli.<verse eid="1CH 29:25"/></para>
  <para style="s1">Ukufa KukaDavida</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="26" style="v" sid="1CH 29:26"/>UDavida indodana kaJese wayeyinkosi yabo bonke abako-Israyeli. <verse eid="1CH 29:26"/><verse number="27" style="v" sid="1CH 29:27"/>Wabusa kwabako-Israyeli iminyaka engamatshumi amane, eyisikhombisa eHebhroni kwathi engamatshumi amathathu lantathu eJerusalema. <verse eid="1CH 29:27"/><verse number="28" style="v" sid="1CH 29:28"/>Wafa eseluphele eseleminyaka eminengi kakhulu lenotho lodumo; uSolomoni indodana yakhe waba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.<verse eid="1CH 29:28"/></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CH 29:29"/>Izehlakalo zombuso weNkosi uDavida kusukela ekuqaleni kuze kube sekupheleni, zilotshiwe egwalweni lwembali kaSamuyeli umboni, egwalweni lwembali kaNathani umphrofethi kanye lasegwalweni lwembali kaGadi umboni. <verse eid="1CH 29:29"/><verse number="30" style="v" sid="1CH 29:30"/>Kubalwa ukubusa kwakhe ngokugcweleyo, amandla lakho konke okwakusenzakala kuye lakwabako-Israyeli leminye imibuso yawo wonke amanye amazwe.<verse eid="1CH 29:30"/></para>
  <chapter eid="1CH 29"/>
</usx>
